NK062(khu)001:1639: 'og gzhi sna tshogs pa'i rin po che las grub pa yi sa gzhi mnan na nems pa /
NK062(khu)001:1641: mdzes pas bris shing spras pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:1643: mdzes par byed pa'i re'u mig rin po che'i mig mngas ris su bris shing /
NK062(khu)001:1644: rin po che'i phra mig du mas spras pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:1647: ri dang ri phran thams cad la yi ge tram
NK062(khu)001:1648: 'phros pa las yon tan kun 'byung ba nor bu
NK062(khu)001:1649: rin cen gyi phung po 'od 'bar bar byin gyis
NK062(khu)001:1650: brlabs pa dang / dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog bsil //
NK062(khu)001:1652: chu bo dang chu phran thams cad la yi ge
NK062(khu)001:1653: a 'phros pas dbyibs legs shing bang rim dang ldan
NK062(khu)001:1654: pa rin po che las grub pa'i rdzing bu chu
NK062(khu)001:1655: yan lag brgyad ldan yis gang ba /
NK062(khu)001:1656: ro bro ba'i mchog tu gyur pa bsil zhing dwangs par byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:1657: rin cen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK062(khu)001:1659: khang khyim dang sbra gur la sogs pa 'gro ba
NK062(khu)001:1660: so so'i gnas khang thams cad la yi ge b+h+rum
NK062(khu)001:1661: 'phros pas gnas khang thams cad rgyu nor bu rin
NK062(khu)001:1662: cen las grub pa'i gzhan yas khang sna tshogs par
NK062(khu)001:1664: rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal //
NK062(khu)001:1666: rtsi shing dang nags tshal thams cad la yi ge
NK062(khu)001:1667: tram 'phros pas zhing khams kyi mdzes pa'i rgyan dang
NK062(khu)001:1668: / mchod rdzas su gyur pa rin po che sna
NK062(khu)001:1669: tshogs las grub pa'i dpag bsam gyi ljon shing rgyas
NK062(khu)001:1670: pa'i tshal du byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:1671: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK062(khu)001:1673: sems kyis zin pa dang ma zin pa'i sgra skad
NK062(khu)001:1674: thams cad la yi ge h+r+aih'aphrosa pas sangs rgyas dang
NK062(khu)001:1675: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la bstod pa'i glu
NK062(khu)001:1676: dbyangs dang sems can la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK062(khu)001:1677: ba'i tshigs su bcad pa'i sgrar byin gyis brlab pa
NK062(khu)001:1678: dang / bla bre rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK062(khu)001:1680: gos dang lhab lhub thams cad la yi ge mam
NK062(khu)001:1681: 'phros pas lha rdzas las grub pa'i bla bre dang
NK062(khu)001:1686: lhab lhub la sogs par byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:1687: do shal dpung rgyan se mo do //
NK062(khu)001:1689: sems can gyi rgyan thams cad la yi ge tram 'phros pas rin po che'i do shal dang /
NK062(khu)001:1692: phyag gdub la sogs par byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:1693: bza' dang btung ba'i mchog rnams dang //
NK062(khu)001:1695: 'gro ba so so'i bza' btung gi longs spyod thams
NK062(khu)001:1696: cad la yi ge a 'phros pas bdud rtsi'i rang
NK062(khu)001:1697: bzhin gyi bza' ba dang btung ba ro bro ba'i
NK062(khu)001:1698: mchog sna tshogs pa rnams su byin gyis brlab pa
NK062(khu)001:1699: dang / rang la mdzes par brgyan pa yi //
NK062(khu)001:1701: 'gro ba thams cad kyang rang la mdzes par byed
NK062(khu)001:1702: pa'i rgyan khyad par can du mas brgyan pa'i lag
NK062(khu)001:1703: na mchod rdzas 'dod pa'i yon tan sna tshogs thogs
NK062(khu)001:1704: pa'i lha dang lha mor byin gyis brlab pa dang
NK062(khu)001:1705: / lha dang lha mo rdul snyed kyis //
NK062(khu)001:1707: lha dang lha mo de dag re re yang bsam
NK062(khu)001:1708: gyis mi khyab pa zhing gi rdul snyed du gyur
NK062(khu)001:1709: pa'i tshogs kyis / bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK062(khu)001:1711: lha dang lha mo de dag gi rkang pa'i bro dang /
NK062(khu)001:1713: ngag gi glu tshig la sogs pa bsam yas pa sna tshogs kyis mchod pa dbul ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:1714: mchod pa de dag mang nyung gi tshad ji tsam 'bul snyam na /
NK062(khu)001:1715: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK062(khu)001:1717: phyogs bcu nas nam mkha'i khams thams cad gang bar bkang nas dbul lo //
NK062(khu)001:1718: de dag gang la 'bul snyam na //
NK062(khu)001:1719: dkyil 'khor kun la rgyas par dbul //
NK062(khu)001:1721: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor gsum po thams cad kun la
NK062(khu)001:1722: rgyas par dbul ba ste mchod pa gnas su stob
NK062(khu)001:1723: bar dbul ba'o // mchod pa'i rdzas de dag gang gis dbul snyam na /
NK062(khu)001:1725: skal ba dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas dbul lo //
NK062(khu)001:1726: dbul ba'i tshul ji ltar dbul snyam na /
NK062(khu)001:1729: rnal 'byor pa blo gsal ba dang mi gsal ba'i khyad bar gyis /
NK062(khu)001:1730: rim mam yang na cig car du //
NK062(khu)001:1732: rnal 'byor pa blo mi gsal na mchod pa rnams tshig gi rim pa ltar rim gyis dbul ba'am /
NK062(khu)001:1733: yang na blo shin tu gsal bas cig car du skad cig dran rdzogs kyis dbul bar bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:1734: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK062(khu)001:1736: de ltar mchod pa rnams chos kyi dbyings skye ba
NK062(khu)001:1737: med pa rang rig pa dang mnyam par blo la
NK062(khu)001:1738: sbyor zhing chos nyid la chos nyid thim pa'i tshul
NK062(khu)001:1739: du dbul lo // mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NK062(khu)001:1741: snang srid thams cad mchod pa'i rdzas las mi 'da' bas na phyag rgya /
NK062(khu)001:1742: de lta bu'i mchod pa de ni theg pa 'og gi mchod pa las dpags pas chen po /
NK062(khu)001:1743: tshul de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par
NK062(khu)001:1744: bsgom pa ni mchod pa rnams kyi nang nas mchog
NK062(khu)001:1746: gsum pa gsang ba'i mchod pa bstan pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:1749: gsal ldan ma'am byin brlabs la //
NK062(khu)001:1751: mchod pa'i yum yang shes rab che zhing ting nge 'dzin gsal ba dang ldan ma can yin na /
NK062(khu)001:1752: yum rang gis bsgom pa'am mi ldan na gtso bo yab kyis byin gyis brlabs la /
NK062(khu)001:1753: stong gsum yungs 'brur gzhug tshul du //
NK062(khu)001:1756: byang chub sems dpa' rdzu 'phrul can gyis stong gsum
NK062(khu)001:1757: gyi stong chen po yungs 'bru gcig gi nang du
NK062(khu)001:1758: gzhug pa ste bcug kyang yungs 'bru cher ma song
NK062(khu)001:1759: stong gsum chung du ma song ba'i tshul du yum
NK062(khu)001:1760: gyi mkha'i sna rtse yungs 'bru tsam la gzhal yas
NK062(khu)001:1761: khang rdzogs par bskyed nas dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus
NK062(khu)001:1762: gsum gang rung gi lha rnams tshang bar bkod la
NK062(khu)001:1763: / dbyings nas dkyil 'khor spyan drangs mchod //
NK062(khu)001:1765: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas rang
NK062(khu)001:1766: bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ram lus kyi rtsa gnas nas
NK062(khu)001:1767: byang chub kyi sems spyan drangs shing dam tshig gi
NK062(khu)001:1768: lha la ye shes pa bstim pa'am byang chub kyi
NK062(khu)001:1769: sems nyi zla gnyis med du bstim zhing yum dang
NK062(khu)001:1770: rol pas gsang ba bde ba'i mchod pa yum gyi
NK062(khu)001:1771: mkha' la gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha de dag
NK062(khu)001:1772: la dbul lo // mnyes nas grub pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK062(khu)001:1774: de ltar yab yum gnyis phyag rgya bzhis rol pa'i
NK062(khu)001:1775: bde ba la bdag nyid kyi ji ltar myong ba
NK062(khu)001:1776: ltar bde ba'i mchod pas rgyal ba thams cad bde
NK062(khu)001:1777: bas mnyes nas de'i byin rlabs kyis srid gsum gyi
NK062(khu)001:1778: 'gro ba thams cad kyang bde bas tshim par gyur
NK062(khu)001:1779: te rgyal ba thams cad mngon sum du grub pa
NK062(khu)001:1780: las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig 'di ni mchod pa
NK062(khu)001:1781: gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas na mchog go
NK062(khu)001:1782: // bdag nyid chen po mchod pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:1784: lha kun gyi bdag nyid chen po rnal 'byor pa
NK062(khu)001:1785: yab yum gnyis yi dam gyi lhar gsal ba dang
NK062(khu)001:1786: / yum gyi mkha'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams byang chub sems kyi mchod pa yis /
NK062(khu)001:1787: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus mnyes //
NK062(khu)001:1789: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa bdag nyid
NK062(khu)001:1790: kyi rang rig pa'i ye shes las tha mi dad
NK062(khu)001:1792: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad la //
NK062(khu)001:1794: rgyal ba rnams mnyes pa de'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK062(khu)001:1795: srid gsum ni 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med kyi khams gsum yin te /
NK062(khu)001:1796: des bsdud pa'i 'gro ba rigs drug dang de dag
NK062(khu)001:1797: bskyed pa'i sa bon a n+ri su tri pre duh
NK062(khu)001:1798: thams cad la / dga' ba chen pos khyab par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:1800: byang chub kyi sems bde ba'i ro dga' ba chen pos khyab nas tshim par 'gyur ro //
NK062(khu)001:1801: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba brtan pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:1803: sgyu ma mtshon pa lha yum /
NK062(khu)001:1805: d+r+wa ba mtshon pa zung du 'brel ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:1806: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK062(khu)001:1807: kyi ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob pa'i tshad
NK062(khu)001:1808: gsal ba yul gyis mi 'phrogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK062(khu)001:1809: yis 'bras bu ji ltar 'thob ce na /
NK062(khu)001:1810: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK062(khu)001:1811: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus dang //
NK062(khu)001:1814: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhir yang dag pa'i sa'am 'gro
NK062(khu)001:1815: ba'i don la gshegs pa yi sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK062(khu)001:1816: 'khor ma lus pa dang khams gsum gyi 'gro ba
NK062(khu)001:1817: sems can rnams kyi khams dang bsam pa thams cad
NK062(khu)001:1818: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gnyis med du gsal
NK062(khu)001:1820: brgyad pa sbyin sreg bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:1821: dbyibs dang kha dog rab tu sbyin //
NK062(khu)001:1823: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan par //
NK062(khu)001:1825: thab kyi rnam pa ni zhi ba la zlum po'am 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa /
NK062(khu)001:1826: rgyas pa la gru bzhi pa'am rin po che zur brgyad pa /
NK062(khu)001:1827: dbang la zla gam mam pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa /
NK062(khu)001:1828: drag po la gru gsum dang khro zhal lam rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbyibs can dang /
NK062(khu)001:1829: kha dog ni go rim bzhin dkar po ser po dmar po drag po la mthing nag go //
NK062(khu)001:1830: mtshan ma ni zhi ba la 'khor lo dkar po +amo gyis mtshan pa /
NK062(khu)001:1831: rgyas pa la rin po che ser po tram gis mtshan pa /
NK062(khu)001:1832: dbang la pad+ma dmar po hrihs mtshan pa /
NK062(khu)001:1833: drag po la rdo rje'am kha t+wam ga mthing nag h+aum gis mtshan pa dang ldan par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:1834: zhal du gyur pa'i zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:1835: sreg lha kun gyi zhal du gyur pa'i me lha
NK062(khu)001:1836: las bzhi gang byed kyi sku mdog phyag mtshan dang
NK062(khu)001:1837: ldan pa'i dam tshig pa bskyed /
NK062(khu)001:1841: ye shes kyi me lha snyan gsan dbab /
NK062(khu)001:1842: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK062(khu)001:1843: zhes sogs kyis bos la dam tshig gi me lha
NK062(khu)001:1844: la bstim mchod bstod byas la las bzhi gang yin
NK062(khu)001:1846: de nas sreg lha dam tshig pa bskyed dbang bskur byin gyis brlab /
NK062(khu)001:1847: ye shes kyi sreg lha dbab drangs bstim kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod la /
NK062(khu)001:1848: bza' btung bro ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK062(khu)001:1850: bza' ba dang btung ba la sogs pa ro bro
NK062(khu)001:1851: ba'i tshogs kyis sreg rdzas rnams las bzhi gang byed
NK062(khu)001:1852: kyi tshig dang sngags kyis phrin las bzhi gang byed
NK062(khu)001:1853: pa'i skabs dang sbyar la mchod pa dbul zhing bden
NK062(khu)001:1854: pa dang smon lam brjod nas /
NK062(khu)001:1856: de nas khro bor bsgyur la dbab drangs bstim kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod la /
NK062(khu)001:1857: las bzhi'i mchod pa rab tu sbyin //
NK062(khu)001:1859: sngar bzhin las bzhi gang byed pa'i skabs dang sbyar
NK062(khu)001:1860: ba'i sbyin sreg gi mchod pa rab tu sbyin par
NK062(khu)001:1861: bya zhing bden pa dang smon lam brjod nas /
NK062(khu)001:1862: gtum chen gyi bstod pa bya zhing /
NK062(khu)001:1863: bro la sogs pa'i las rjes rnams rgyas par bya ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:1864: de dag ni gzhung tshig gi skabs su 'bru bsnan pa tsam du byas pa yin la /
NK062(khu)001:1865: rgyas par lung dang sbyar te bshad na /
NK062(khu)001:1867: sbyin sreg rnam pa bzhir gsungs te //
NK062(khu)001:1868: sa dang rab gnas rnam gnyis dang //
NK062(khu)001:1869: bde ba sbyin pa'i dus nyid du //
NK062(khu)001:1870: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:1871: lhag pa'i dkyil 'khor rnam bzhi ru //
NK062(khu)001:1872: zhal du gyur pa'i me bos la //
NK062(khu)001:1873: las bzhi'i mchod pa rab tu sbyin //
NK062(khu)001:1874: cho ga sogs rnams bzhis lha grangs bzhin //
NK062(khu)001:1875: skabs bzhir rgyas par mchod par bya //
NK062(khu)001:1877: sa chog gi dus su sa'i mtshan ma ngan na zhi ba'i sbyin sreg /
NK062(khu)001:1878: dkyil 'khor rab gnas kyi dus su rgyas pa'i byin sreg /
NK062(khu)001:1879: dbang bskur ba'i dus su dbang gi sbyin sreg /
NK062(khu)001:1880: slob bu rab gnas kyi dus su kun rmi ltas
NK062(khu)001:1881: log na drag po'i sbyin sreg bya bar gsungs te
NK062(khu)001:1882: / de yang sbyin sreg rtsa ba las //
NK062(khu)001:1883: gnas rdzas thab kyi rnam pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:1884: gzungs dang gtso sems bsgrub bya dang //
NK062(khu)001:1885: phur pa lha dus las rim dang //
NK062(khu)001:1886: lhag ma bcu gcig shes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:1888: de yang dang po gnas bstan pa la /
NK062(khu)001:1890: ri bo 'dus pa'i rtse dag dang //
NK062(khu)001:1891: chu rlung 'jam po'i sa phyogs su //
NK062(khu)001:1892: dang bar byed pa'i las rnams brtsam //
NK062(khu)001:1894: nags tshal sman ljongs me tog tshal //
NK062(khu)001:1895: lhun stug ri bo rgyas par bya //
NK062(khu)001:1897: sum mdo chu bo 'dus pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:1898: bzhi mdo khang stong sdud ces bya //
NK062(khu)001:1900: dur khrod ngan pa'i sa phyogs su //
NK062(khu)001:1901: lhag par brtsams na nges par 'grub //
NK062(khu)001:1903: las bzhi'i gnas de dag shin tu gal che bar bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:1904: rang bzhin nus mthu ldan pa'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:1905: shin tu dgos par bstan pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:1907: gnyis pa rdzas bstan pa la yang //
NK062(khu)001:1908: gnyis pa rnam pa lngar bshad de //
NK062(khu)001:1910: las bzhi gang byed kyi sreg shing dang /
NK062(khu)001:1916: me yi rdzas gnyis sreg shing ni //
NK062(khu)001:1918: dang po sreg shing ni shing zhig la byed na /
NK062(khu)001:1919: rtse mo zhi byed yal ga rgyas //
NK062(khu)001:1920: sdong po dbang rtsa mngon spyod do //
NK062(khu)001:1921: shing tha dad la byed na shing dkar ser 'jam po la zhi rgyas gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:1922: dmar nag tsher ma can la dbang drag gnyis kyi sreg shing bya ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:1923: kha dog las kyi sbyar bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:1926: shug pa tsan+dana dkar po dang //
NK062(khu)001:1927: u dum wa ra 'o ma'i shing //
NK062(khu)001:1928: zhi rgyas yam shing shes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:1929: dmar la dri zhim shing rnams dang //
NK062(khu)001:1930: dug shing tsher ma can dag la //
NK062(khu)001:1931: tshil byugs dbang drag me sbar ro //
NK062(khu)001:1933: gsum pa ling ga'i rgyu ni /
NK062(khu)001:1934: bsgrub bya'i dam rdzas gos sogs dang //
NK062(khu)001:1935: longs spyod de bzhin shes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:1936: dug dang tsha ba rnam gsum dang //
NK062(khu)001:1937: sha chen ra dang ba glang sha /
NK062(khu)001:1938: mchog tu gsod par byed pa yi //
NK062(khu)001:1939: skyur ba dbang ste ling ga'i rdzas //
NK062(khu)001:1943: me tog dkar po'i gtor mas zhi //
NK062(khu)001:1944: ldong ros gro chan zho rgun 'brum //
NK062(khu)001:1945: me tog gser phye rgyas pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:1946: zangs phye bu ram 'bras mar chan //
NK062(khu)001:1948: thams cad sdud pa'i gtor ma yin //
NK062(khu)001:1949: dug rnams lcags phye rdo phye dang //
NK062(khu)001:1950: ra khyi khrag dang sha chen dang //
NK062(khu)001:1951: dur sol mur ka'i chan rnams ni //
NK062(khu)001:1952: gsod par byed pa'i gtor ma yin //
NK062(khu)001:1954: lnga pa sreg rdzas la'ang zhi ba'i sreg rdzas ni /
NK062(khu)001:1955: mar dkar til dkar nas dkar can //
NK062(khu)001:1956: mngar gsum tsan+dana dkar po'i shing //
NK062(khu)001:1957: thams cad ye shes bdud rtsi ste //
NK062(khu)001:1958: tha mas ye shes me bskyed do //
NK062(khu)001:1960: zho dang ma rnying bu ram sbrang //
NK062(khu)001:1961: rgun 'brum star kha sha chen dang //
NK062(khu)001:1962: dri zhim gser phye rgyas pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:1964: tan ta li dang shang tshe dang //
NK062(khu)001:1965: ske tshe tsha ba'i mar dag dang //
NK062(khu)001:1966: dmar po'i shing dang 'bras dag gis //
NK062(khu)001:1967: thams cad 'gugs pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:1969: dug dang tshil chen ske tshe'i mar //
NK062(khu)001:1970: sran chen khrag sna tshogs tshad dang //
NK062(khu)001:1971: tsher ma ba glang sha yis gsod //
NK062(khu)001:1972: 'bras bu gdon phyir tshogs par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:1974: gsum pa thab kyi rnam pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:1975: sa gzhi legs par sbyangs byas nas //
NK062(khu)001:1977: sa gzhi rnams legs par sbyangs nas las bzhi'i thab bya ba la /
NK062(khu)001:1978: dang po zhi ba'i thab ni /
NK062(khu)001:1979: dkyil 'khor zlum po rim pa gsum //
NK062(khu)001:1980: khru gang dpangs dang zheng du yin //
NK062(khu)001:1981: zabs dang gyen ni phyed du bshad //
NK062(khu)001:1984: mda' bzhi zhags pa dkar pos dkri //
NK062(khu)001:1985: gzhan yang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la //
NK062(khu)001:1986: rigs bzhi'i phyag rgyar rab shes nas //
NK062(khu)001:1987: +amo dang seng mgo spel mar bri //
NK062(khu)001:1988: mu khyud skor ba phyi ru bshad //
NK062(khu)001:1989: thams cad zhi byed dkyil 'khor yin //
NK062(khu)001:1990: gnyis pa rgyas pa'i thab ni /
NK062(khu)001:1992: gru chad la sogs rim rjes mthun //
NK062(khu)001:1993: rdo rje rin cen zhags pas bskor //
NK062(khu)001:1994: dbus su rin chen tram snying ldan //
NK062(khu)001:1995: gzhan yang rin cen gnyis dbyibs su //
NK062(khu)001:1996: rim pa la sogs rjes su mthun //
NK062(khu)001:1997: zhags pa ser po mda' bzhis bskor //
NK062(khu)001:1999: gsum pa dbang gi thab ni /
NK062(khu)001:2000: hmo khung zla gam gdengs pa la //
NK062(khu)001:2002: lcags sgrog gtams pas mdzes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2004: gzhan yang 'dab brgyad de bzhin du //
NK062(khu)001:2005: mtha' ma ljon shing mdzes pas bskor //
NK062(khu)001:2006: mda' bzhi zhags sdud dbang gi yin //
NK062(khu)001:2007: bzhi pa drag po'i thab ni /
NK062(khu)001:2008: dkyil 'khor gru gsum gdengs pa la //
NK062(khu)001:2009: dur khrod sol bas khyab par sbyar //
NK062(khu)001:2010: rdo rje rtse gnyis gdengs pa la //
NK062(khu)001:2011: thod pa lcags kyu gtams pas bskor //
NK062(khu)001:2012: h'u bcas rdo rje snying por ldan //
NK062(khu)001:2013: mda' bzhi zhags pa nag pos bskor //
NK062(khu)001:2014: gzhan yang zhal gdangs spyan bgrad pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:2015: khro zhal shin tu 'jigs pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:2016: med dpung 'bar bas rab mdzes pa //
NK062(khu)001:2017: 'di ni gsod pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:2021: bong chung lus mdzes zla ba'i mdog /
NK062(khu)001:2022: g.yas 'khyil lus kyang de bzhin shes //
NK062(khu)001:2023: skad gsal sngags bzlas yid mi skyo //
NK062(khu)001:2024: khro spangs de bzhin zhi la sbyar //
NK062(khu)001:2026: ban glang ser mo gru bzhi pa //
NK062(khu)001:2027: rna ba 'gram slang ring sha rgyas //
NK062(khu)001:2028: yan lag zla mang las la mkhas //
NK062(khu)001:2029: dal zhing blo gros ldan pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:2030: 'phel ba'i dus su shes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2032: dmar mo zla gam mdzes pa'i zhal //
NK062(khu)001:2033: yal ga sgyu gnas ma spangs //
NK062(khu)001:2034: thabs mkhas brtson 'grus ldan pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:2035: thams cad sdug par byed pa'i mchog /
NK062(khu)001:2037: nag mo gru gsum rtsid mgo ma //
NK062(khu)001:2038: khro gnyer can la gel bag chags //
NK062(khu)001:2039: gtum shing barlanga tshig 'dzem bag med //
NK062(khu)001:2040: sngags zlos brtul zhugs ldan pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:2041: tha ma'i dus su 'di shes bya //
NK062(khu)001:2043: lnga pa gtso bo'i sems ni /
NK062(khu)001:2044: rang rigs sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK062(khu)001:2045: thams cad rang dbang bdag sgyur phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2046: bsgrub pa'i gtso bor 'di gsungs so //
NK062(khu)001:2048: don gyi sems chos nyid bden pa dbyer med kyi
NK062(khu)001:2049: don khong du chud cing byang chub kyi sems dang
NK062(khu)001:2051: stongs kyi sems zhi ba la /
NK062(khu)001:2052: ma lus sems ni mtha' bral phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2053: rang bzhin rnam dag mngon du bya //
NK062(khu)001:2055: sems gter rtog tshogs dkyil 'khor phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2056: byin rlabs bsdus 'phel mngon du bsgom //
NK062(khu)001:2058: thams cad bdag phyir tha mi dad //
NK062(khu)001:2059: shin tu zhen pa nyid kyis 'grub //
NK062(khu)001:2060: chags pa chen po nyid du bshad //
NK062(khu)001:2062: rang bzhin gcig phyir dngos med 'jig /
NK062(khu)001:2063: log rtog khros pa'i sems kyis bskul //
NK062(khu)001:2064: yang dag zhe sdang chen por gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:2068: bdag gzhan gnod pa'i sems dang ni //
NK062(khu)001:2069: sbyor ba ngan pa rig sngags las //
NK062(khu)001:2070: khams rkyen las gyur gnod mang ba //
NK062(khu)001:2071: nyon mongs bag chags sdug bsngal rnams //
NK062(khu)001:2072: thabs phyir gcig kyang dor mi bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2074: yon tan 'phel ba med nyung phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2075: tshe dang longs spyod sgo gsum gyi //
NK062(khu)001:2076: yon tan mngon par mi ldan pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:2078: yon tan bsdus te bstim pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:2079: sems ni rin cen gter gyi phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2082: mos 'dud med pa'i las rkyen can //
NK062(khu)001:2083: las gsum bdag gzhan don gyi phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2084: gsum pa'i las la sbyar bya zhing //
NK062(khu)001:2085: lha yang de bzhin shes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2087: zhing bcur gyur pa'i sems can dang //
NK062(khu)001:2088: dam pa'i chos 'jig ma rungs byed //
NK062(khu)001:2089: dpa' bos dgos pa yod pa'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2090: kun la phan phyir de bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2092: bdun pa phur bu la'ang zhi ba'i phur bu ni /
NK062(khu)001:2093: dngul lam dkar po'i shing rnams la //
NK062(khu)001:2094: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zlum po //
NK062(khu)001:2095: steng 'og logs la khro bcu bsgom //
NK062(khu)001:2097: sngags dang phyag rgyas byin brlabs pa //
NK062(khu)001:2098: mtha' bskor yan lag snying la sbyar //
NK062(khu)001:2100: gser ram ser po'i shing rnams la //
NK062(khu)001:2101: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse gru bzhi //
NK062(khu)001:2102: lha rnams de bzhin rin chen khro //
NK062(khu)001:2103: zur bzhir gnas pa lus gnas bzhir //
NK062(khu)001:2104: btab pas yon tan 'du bar gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:2106: zangs sam dmar po'i shing rnams la //
NK062(khu)001:2107: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zla gam //
NK062(khu)001:2108: de bzhin chags pa'i phur bur shes //
NK062(khu)001:2109: zla gam mtha' bskor dbang la sbyar //
NK062(khu)001:2110: de dag bsgyur te 'dus par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2112: lcags sam nag po'i shing rnams la //
NK062(khu)001:2113: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur gsum //
NK062(khu)001:2114: de bzhin rdo rje phur brlab pa //
NK062(khu)001:2115: zur gsum lus ngag sems la sbyar //
NK062(khu)001:2117: las byed nyi shu gcig tu'ang byed //
NK062(khu)001:2119: brgyad pa ni las sbyor gyi lha zhi khro'i gzhung bzhin no //
NK062(khu)001:2121: sbyin dang sreg pa'i lha gnyis te //
NK062(khu)001:2123: me lha dang sreg lha gnyis las /
NK062(khu)001:2125: las bzhi gang yin gyi sku mdog phyag mtshan te /
NK062(khu)001:2126: sangs rgya rigs kyi sprul pa'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2127: thams cad las la thogs med 'jug /
NK062(khu)001:2128: sku mdog cha lugs las bzhin shes //
NK062(khu)001:2130: rigs kyi phyag rgyas gdab par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2132: ag+ne de ba las bzhi'i sngags //
NK062(khu)001:2134: zhal phyir sbyin pa'i lhar bshad do //
NK062(khu)001:2137: gzugs brnyan lta bu'i gzhal yas ni //
NK062(khu)001:2140: rgyan rnams zhi la dkar ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:2142: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK062(khu)001:2143: kun kyang gti mug rdo rje'i tshul //
NK062(khu)001:2145: khams gnyis thams cad khyab par sbyar //
NK062(khu)001:2146: sa bon +amo dang rang sngags ldan //
NK062(khu)001:2147: gzhan la'ang de bzhin shes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2148: rin cen dga' 'phro ser skya ni //
NK062(khu)001:2150: sngags sogs gzhan ni snga ma'i tshul //
NK062(khu)001:2151: sprul pa'ang rjes su mthun pa ste //
NK062(khu)001:2153: 'dod chags rdo rje lcags sgrog dang //
NK062(khu)001:2154: mdog ni dmar smug 'od po che //
NK062(khu)001:2155: sngags ni yi ger dang h+r+aih phyogs bcur khyab cing h+r+aihl bsdu //
NK062(khu)001:2156: zhe sdang rdo rje gtum chen 'bar //
NK062(khu)001:2157: dud kha nag pa'i mdog 'dra ba //
NK062(khu)001:2159: nyi zla thod sbrul gdug pas brgyan //
NK062(khu)001:2160: seng ge glang chen stag rngam dang //
NK062(khu)001:2161: rbod stong rngam pa'i phyag rgya ldan //
NK062(khu)001:2162: sgra skad drag pos khams gsum dkrug /
NK062(khu)001:2163: bsgrub bya phyag rgya goms pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:2166: dgu pa dus ni lo gcig la byed na /
NK062(khu)001:2167: dbyar dgun ston dpyid las rim dang //
NK062(khu)001:2170: snga dro gung dgong nam phyed dus //
NK062(khu)001:2171: las rim brtsams na shis par bshad //
NK062(khu)001:2173: bcu pa sbyin sreg gi las kyi rim pa la gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:2176: dang po sngon du bya ba la gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:2180: rdzas dang yo byad ldan byas la //
NK062(khu)001:2181: sa gzhi sbyangs te gzugs brnyan sbyar //
NK062(khu)001:2182: stongs 'gyur mgo la las bcol zhing //
NK062(khu)001:2183: kun kyang tshim byas pa bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2184: shing gnyis mchod rdzas legs bkod de //
NK062(khu)001:2185: kha dog me ltar legs par gdab //
NK062(khu)001:2186: ling ga'i gnas ni gzugs brnyan tshul //
NK062(khu)001:2187: ming rus ldan pa'i phur bus bskor //
NK062(khu)001:2188: gnyis pa sngon 'gro'i cho ga dngos ni /
NK062(khu)001:2189: rdo rje gur gyis phyogs bcing zhing //
NK062(khu)001:2190: nyi ma zla ba las gnyis kyis //
NK062(khu)001:2191: gzhong ba snod kyi rdzas rnams la //
NK062(khu)001:2192: las kyi h+aum las 'bru lnga dgod //
NK062(khu)001:2194: mang zhing sna tshogs ro ldan bya //
NK062(khu)001:2196: gnyis pa las rim dngos la gsum //
NK062(khu)001:2197: las sbyor gyi phrin las zhi khro gzhung bsrang ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:2198: ling ga dgug gzhug bya ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:2199: sbyin sreg gi las rim bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2200: dang po las sbyor gyi phrin las zhi khro gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:2201: dkyil 'khor las kyi gzhung bsrang la //
NK062(khu)001:2202: sna tshogs mchod yon rgyas par dbul //
NK062(khu)001:2203: tshogs kyi 'khor lo legs par brtag /
NK062(khu)001:2204: mchod pa chen po'ang dbul bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:2206: ye shes dkyil 'khor bskul bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:2207: khams gsum byin rlabs dag bsdus te //
NK062(khu)001:2208: bsgrub bya nye bar sbyar ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:2209: srog dang ldan pa'i bzlas ba ni //
NK062(khu)001:2210: zhal gyi rang sngags khro 'bum du //
NK062(khu)001:2211: rnam gsum tshul gyi bya ba dag /
NK062(khu)001:2212: shin tu stong 'gyur rgyas par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2214: gnyis pa lid+ga dgug gzhug bya ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:2215: khams gsum gang ba'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK062(khu)001:2217: bdag nyid 'dzin pa'i phyag rgya ste //
NK062(khu)001:2218: mtshan ma bzung nas rang sngags gdon //
NK062(khu)001:2219: rol pa'i pho nya bka' nyan tshogs //
NK062(khu)001:2220: phyag rgya bzhi ldan sgra skad drag /
NK062(khu)001:2221: khams gsum skrug ste phral byas nas //
NK062(khu)001:2222: bsgrub bya mngon du sbyar bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:2224: tshogs tha ma la lid+ga byas pa brub khung du brubs la dgug gzhug bya /
NK062(khu)001:2225: gtor bskul byas la gtor thun dbab /
NK062(khu)001:2226: phur bskul byas la phur bu gdab /
NK062(khu)001:2228: gris gtubs la sreg rdzas dang bsres la bzhag go //
NK062(khu)001:2229: gsum pa sbyin sreg gi las rim la gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:2232: dang po me lha'i las rim ni /
NK062(khu)001:2233: rjes su mthun pa'i gzhal yas su //
NK062(khu)001:2234: sbyin lha so so'i gdan ltar bsgom //
NK062(khu)001:2235: me dpung 'bar ba'i tshogs chen du //
NK062(khu)001:2236: me lha ag+ne dzahs bkug nas //
NK062(khu)001:2237: phyag rgya bzhi yis nges bkug la //
NK062(khu)001:2238: ram zhes bya bas me spar nas //
NK062(khu)001:2239: gzar bu rigs kyi mtshan bcas pa //
NK062(khu)001:2240: mchod pa bdud rtsi rgyas par dbul //
NK062(khu)001:2241: gnyis pa sreg lha'i las kyi rim pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2242: de dbus 'khor lo gsal btab ste //
NK062(khu)001:2243: gnyis pa'i lha rnams spyan drangs bstim //
NK062(khu)001:2244: mar dang shing bu chan la sogs //
NK062(khu)001:2245: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgyun du dbul //
NK062(khu)001:2246: gcig min thams cad bdud rtsi ste //
NK062(khu)001:2247: yang na lan gsum brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK062(khu)001:2248: stong dang 'bum sogs ci nus dbul //
NK062(khu)001:2249: gru gsum pa de de bzhin bya //
NK062(khu)001:2250: dbang med zhal du thim par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2251: ming dang las bzhi'i sngags kyis dbul //
NK062(khu)001:2254: gzugs brnyan lu gu rgyud bskor la //
NK062(khu)001:2255: e la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK062(khu)001:2256: rjes su mthun pa'i lha bsgom la //
NK062(khu)001:2257: slas dang byi mo'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NK062(khu)001:2258: khams su gang bar sbyar bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:2259: sreg dang ldan pa'i bro stabs gar //
NK062(khu)001:2260: phyogs bcu ma lus kun nas ni //
NK062(khu)001:2261: bsgrub bya dbus su legs brgya ste //
NK062(khu)001:2262: sa bon 'od zer las bzhin du //
NK062(khu)001:2263: bstims nas bsam pa 'grub par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2264: rjes su mthun pa'i smon lam gdab //
NK062(khu)001:2267: bcu gcig pa lhag ma'i las ni /
NK062(khu)001:2268: bdag nyid 'dul ba'i dbang phyug tu //
NK062(khu)001:2269: las bzhin mnyam gzhag khro bo yi //
NK062(khu)001:2270: 'khor gyi phra men de bzhin gshegs //
NK062(khu)001:2271: phra men tshogs rnams kun bsdus te //
NK062(khu)001:2272: las bzhi'i dkyil 'khor de dag tu //
NK062(khu)001:2273: lhag ma kha chu 'dod pa sbyin //
NK062(khu)001:2277: yi ge brgya pas lhag chad kha bskangs //
NK062(khu)001:2278: sreg lha dang me lha ye shes pa gshegs /
NK062(khu)001:2279: dam tshig pa rang la bsdu /
NK062(khu)001:2280: mtshams dang dkyil 'khor bsdus la las rjes mi mngon
NK062(khu)001:2281: par bya shing bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa
NK062(khu)001:2282: brjod par bya'o // de nas lhag pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK062(khu)001:2283: 'jug pa'i cho ga bshad par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2285: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa la gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:2288: slob ma la lha sgoms shig par nan tan bya ba bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2289: dang po slob dpon 'jug pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2291: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK062(khu)001:2293: thog mar slob dpon 'jug pa'i cho ga la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:2294: dbang phyug rdo rje slob dpon dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2295: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug par bzod par gsol ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:2296: dang po dbang phyug rdo rje slob dpon dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2297: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK062(khu)001:2298: ces pas sngar bshad pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi las kun
NK062(khu)001:2299: rdzogs par byas shing phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang gis
NK062(khu)001:2300: phyug pa'i rdo rje slob dpon gyis khrus byas dbang
NK062(khu)001:2301: gos gyon nas / dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor gus pas 'dug ste me tog thogs la /
NK062(khu)001:2302: +amo badz+ra sa ma ya +amo la sogs pas rig pa'i me tog dor nas /
NK062(khu)001:2304: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK062(khu)001:2305: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig dang sngags dang ting
NK062(khu)001:2306: nge 'dzin gyis rang nyid dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i
NK062(khu)001:2307: cho ga dag gis dkyil 'khor du legs par zhugs
NK062(khu)001:2308: nas / slob ma la dbang ji tsam du bskur
NK062(khu)001:2309: bar 'dod pa rnams rang nyid dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK062(khu)001:2310: las dbang blang bar bya ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:2311: de dag ni rang gi rig pas dkyil 'khor du 'jug par bya ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:2313: rgyas pa'i mchod pa rdzogs sbyar nas //
NK062(khu)001:2314: dbang gos ldan pas dbang phyug yin //
NK062(khu)001:2315: gzhan dag gzhan gyi mdzes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2317: lha rnams mngon byas rin cen ldan //
NK062(khu)001:2318: 'bru lnga rdo rje dam tshig gis //
NK062(khu)001:2319: sngar gyi sku gsung thugs yon tan //
NK062(khu)001:2320: phrin las ye shes gnyis med sbyar //
NK062(khu)001:2322: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs +amo badz+ra sa
NK062(khu)001:2323: ma ya hoh bskul ba'i dam tshig rjes dran pa'i
NK062(khu)001:2324: // 'od zer gzi byin ldan par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2325: rang bzhin gnyis med gyur pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2327: gnyis pa slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug par bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:2328: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:2329: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK062(khu)001:2331: bdag gis slob ma gzhug par bgyi //
NK062(khu)001:2332: bzod par mdzad de dgongs su gsol //
NK062(khu)001:2333: 'dzum bcas gnang ba thob par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2334: gnyis pa slob ma gzhug bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2335: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2337: slob dpon gyis dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa de nas
NK062(khu)001:2338: slob ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa dkyil 'khor du
NK062(khu)001:2339: gzhug par bya ba la chos bcu drug gis ston
NK062(khu)001:2340: te / khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK062(khu)001:2341: bgegs bskrad lhar brlab dam tshig sbyin //
NK062(khu)001:2342: de nyid dpog dang chun na dang //
NK062(khu)001:2343: bsgrags dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:2344: lha dbab pa dang nan tan bya //
NK062(khu)001:2345: mig dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK062(khu)001:2346: tshogs mchog yon dang rnam bco brgyad //
NK062(khu)001:2356: dam tshig gi de nyid dpog pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2359: rin po che'i me tog dor ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:2365: dang po khrus bya ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:2366: shin tu bzang po'i bgo ba rnams //
NK062(khu)001:2367: dri yi chu yis dag par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2368: gnyis pa mig dar dgab pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2369: snyim par rin cen ldan pa dag /
NK062(khu)001:2370: ras sogs dmar pos gdong g.yogs la //
NK062(khu)001:2371: gsum pa dri ba bya ba ni //
NK062(khu)001:2372: bu khyod ci la dga' zhes dri //
NK062(khu)001:2373: skal bzang bdag dga' lan blan la //
NK062(khu)001:2374: 'khor lo'i drung du bkri bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:2375: bzhi pa lus dbul ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:2376: thal sbyar gus dang bcas pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:2377: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas dang //
NK062(khu)001:2378: dbang phyug sangs rgyas da ltar bdag /
NK062(khu)001:2379: ma 'ongs rin cen sems can la //
NK062(khu)001:2380: dgos pa gsum phyir lus dbul bya //
NK062(khu)001:2381: mchog gi yon phyir snod du 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2382: lnga pa bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2383: tshe bsrung sbyor ba'i khro tshogs kyis //
NK062(khu)001:2384: bar chad bgegs bskrad mtshams bcad la //
NK062(khu)001:2385: drug pa lhar brlab pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2386: sgrib sbyang rnam shes cho ga yis //
NK062(khu)001:2387: h+aum las sems dpa' gzhan yang rung //
NK062(khu)001:2388: mtshan ma rdzogs par bsam gtan bya //
NK062(khu)001:2389: bdun pa dam tshig sbyin pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:2390: dam tshig chen po bdud rtsi lnga //
NK062(khu)001:2391: rang bzhin 'bru gsum sku gsung thugs //
NK062(khu)001:2392: gzi byin ldan par byin brlabs la //
NK062(khu)001:2393: dam tshig sdom pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:2394: brgyad pa dam tshig de nyid dpog pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:2395: snying gar rdo rje bsten byas la //
NK062(khu)001:2396: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'di //
NK062(khu)001:2397: dam nyams ma 'dres med pa la //
NK062(khu)001:2398: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK062(khu)001:2399: theg pa chen po ston byed pa //
NK062(khu)001:2400: nga la brnyas dang smad mi rung //
NK062(khu)001:2401: sku gsung thugs la rtag gnas te //
NK062(khu)001:2402: ma lus sems can don gyis shig /
NK062(khu)001:2403: dgu pa chu nan bya ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:2404: tsan+dana dkar dmar sbyar ba la //
NK062(khu)001:2405: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rab gnas bya //
NK062(khu)001:2406: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK062(khu)001:2407: dam tshig 'das na sreg par byed //
NK062(khu)001:2408: rdo rje khro bo chen por 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2409: rdo rje'i chu 'di btung bar gyis //
NK062(khu)001:2411: de lta bas na bu khyod kyis //
NK062(khu)001:2412: dam tshig 'di dag bsrung bar gyis //
NK062(khu)001:2413: de bzhin byas na dngos grub 'thob //
NK062(khu)001:2414: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i chu 'thungs shig /
NK062(khu)001:2415: +amo badz+ra ud da ka h+aum th+aa /
NK062(khu)001:2416: bcu pa dam tshig bsgrags pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:2417: lan gsum byin nas rab bsgrags pa //
NK062(khu)001:2418: thabs dang shes rab sems nyid kyis //
NK062(khu)001:2419: rtag tu dgos pa med gyis la //
NK062(khu)001:2420: 'dod pa lnga yi yon tan spyod //
NK062(khu)001:2421: gzhan yang stong khams thams cad na //
NK062(khu)001:2422: shes rab dbyings dang 'dod yon gzhan //
NK062(khu)001:2423: rab 'bring tha ma thams cad spyad //
NK062(khu)001:2424: gzhan yang dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:2425: skye bo gang zhig dam la gnod //
NK062(khu)001:2426: brtul zhugs can gyis de grongs la //
NK062(khu)001:2427: snying la khrag chen btung bar gyis //
NK062(khu)001:2428: sems nyid theg pa rab nges na //
NK062(khu)001:2429: nyon mongs 'dod lnga kun spyad kyang //
NK062(khu)001:2431: byas la mi sogs sdom pa'am rdzogs //
NK062(khu)001:2432: bya dang mi bya cung zad med //
NK062(khu)001:2433: bcu gcig pa me tog dor ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:2434: dkyil 'khor yid la mngon sbyar nas //
NK062(khu)001:2435: 'dod pa'ang yang na gzhan yang rung //
NK062(khu)001:2436: dor te 'brel pa legs par brtag /
NK062(khu)001:2437: bcu gnyis pa lha dbab pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2438: rang ming dam tshig h+aum dang bcas //
NK062(khu)001:2439: dam tshig phyag rgya lan gsum bstan //
NK062(khu)001:2440: lcags kyu ha his bkug byas la //
NK062(khu)001:2441: nyes legs phrin las gsal byas la //
NK062(khu)001:2442: phyag rgyas bstims la brtan par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2443: bcu gsum pa mig dbye ba ni //
NK062(khu)001:2444: 'od zer thur mas dbye bya ba //
NK062(khu)001:2445: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha phata /
NK062(khu)001:2446: 'khor lo mngon pa'i nga rgyal bya //
NK062(khu)001:2447: bcu bzhi pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:2448: dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags bshad pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2450: dang po dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags bshad pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2451: gser sogs mtshon byed nges blangs la //
NK062(khu)001:2452: chos rnams thams cad gnyis med pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:2453: dbyings su thim pa'i 'od zer gsal //
NK062(khu)001:2454: gcig dang spros pa thams cad med //
NK062(khu)001:2455: dkyil 'khor spros med zlum po'i tshul //
NK062(khu)001:2456: rang rig ye nas mya ngan 'da' //
NK062(khu)001:2457: ye shes rgyu dang 'bras bur ldan //
NK062(khu)001:2458: chos kyi 'khor lo yongs kyis bskor //
NK062(khu)001:2459: thugs rje'i byin rlabs spros pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:2460: ye shes bzhi yi dkyil 'khor spro //
NK062(khu)001:2461: sku gsung thugs dang ye shes lnga //
NK062(khu)001:2462: byin rlab ya mtshan bsam mi khyab //
NK062(khu)001:2463: rang snang ba yi thabs las byung //
NK062(khu)001:2464: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2465: mtha' dbus med par rgyas par gnas //
NK062(khu)001:2467: de phyir ye shes sgo bzhir shar //
NK062(khu)001:2468: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2469: der 'gro lam stegs brgyad dang ldan //
NK062(khu)001:2470: rang bzhin ye nas 'od gsal phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2471: nyi zla brtsegs pa'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK062(khu)001:2472: ye nas rnam par dag pa'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2474: zad med ye shes gter gyur pas //
NK062(khu)001:2475: yid bzhin rin cen 'bar ba'i gdan //
NK062(khu)001:2476: 'bras bu'i chos rnams yongs rdzogs phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2477: seng ge la sogs bstan pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:2478: ye nas mnyam nyid mi 'ad'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2479: ta la'i ljon shing rang bzhin gnas //
NK062(khu)001:2480: thams cad la ni dbang sgyur phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2481: 'jig rten lha chen rnams kyis bskor //
NK062(khu)001:2482: gnyis pa lha ngo bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2483: thams cad rang bzhin dag pa'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2484: sgyu 'phrul bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis //
NK062(khu)001:2485: thams cad lha nyid rtag tu sbyor //
NK062(khu)001:2486: thams cad ma lus dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK062(khu)001:2487: mtshan nyid legs par shes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2488: bco lnga pa nan tan bya ba ni //
NK062(khu)001:2489: rang gi lha nyid 'bras bu yi //
NK062(khu)001:2490: gzhi phyir mchog tu'ang nan tan bya //
NK062(khu)001:2491: bcu drug pa yon dbul ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:2492: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK062(khu)001:2493: nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2494: dbang dang dngos grub 'dod pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:2495: 'di la shin tu nan tan bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2496: gsum pa slob ma la lha sgoms shig par nan tan bya ba bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2497: skal ba mnyam pa'i phung bar 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2499: skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes de //
NK062(khu)001:2500: zhes pas bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum gyi rang
NK062(khu)001:2501: bzhin yang rgyal ba yi dam gyi lha'i sku gsung
NK062(khu)001:2502: thugs rdo rjer ye nas lhun gyis grub pa la
NK062(khu)001:2503: ni / bdag dang lha khyad par med pa skal
NK062(khu)001:2504: pa mnyam pa'i ye shes zhes bya ba kho na'o
NK062(khu)001:2505: ni / // de ltar yin mod kyi tha mal
NK062(khu)001:2506: pa'i sgo gsum du brtag pas sgrib pa de bsal
NK062(khu)001:2507: ni / // ba'i thabs ni / gnyen na nye bar 'byung ba yi //
NK062(khu)001:2509: le'u lnga pa ltar ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis gnyen
NK062(khu)001:2510: zhing bsgrubs na dus nye bar 'byung ba yi 'bras
NK062(khu)001:2512: ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges //
NK062(khu)001:2513: zhes pas mchog gi dngos grub ya mtshan chen po
NK062(khu)001:2514: myur ba nyid du grub nas 'byung bar nges pas
NK062(khu)001:2515: yi dam gyi lha sgom pa dang mi 'bral bar
NK062(khu)001:2518: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK062(khu)001:2520: gcig dang du mar yongs bral bas //
NK062(khu)001:2523: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2524: zhes pas rtsa ba'i dam tshig bla med mi spang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:2525: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcod pa gnyis car
NK062(khu)001:2526: lha'i sgom bzlas yin pas de ltar lha sgom pa
NK062(khu)001:2527: dang / bzlas pa byed pa la dad pa med
NK062(khu)001:2528: na yi dam lha'i dam tshig nyams par 'gyur ro
NK062(khu)001:2529: dang / // dam tshig nyams na skyon ci yod ce na /
NK062(khu)001:2530: rdo rje gnod sbyin gyis snying khrag zho bzhin 'jibs
NK062(khu)001:2531: nas 'dir yang tshe thung zhing phyi ma ngan 'gro'i
NK062(khu)001:2532: gnas su ltung ba'i phyir na phung bar 'gyur bas
NK062(khu)001:2533: sgrub pa la nan tan che bar bya'o zhes gsung
NK062(khu)001:2535: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2536: gang zhig phyag rgya 'di spangs na //
NK062(khu)001:2537: nyon mongs ngan song gnas su skye //
NK062(khu)001:2539: bla med 'gro ba'i rgyun yang bcad //
NK062(khu)001:2540: rigs chad nyid du gnas par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2542: bcu pa dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK062(khu)001:2543: bde ba chen po'i yid 'ong mnyam par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2545: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK062(khu)001:2547: rigs lnga yab yum thabs dang shes rab zung du
NK062(khu)001:2548: 'brel ba ni bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor kho
NK062(khu)001:2549: na'o // de dag lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi skabs su dkyil 'khor bsdus pa la ni /
NK062(khu)001:2550: stangs dpyal gnyis sam yang na lnga //
NK062(khu)001:2553: dpyal ni yum ste gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gnyis sam /
NK062(khu)001:2554: yang na dkyil 'khor rgyas pa dang 'bring po gnyis la gtso bo rigasalnga yab yum gyis byas pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2555: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs na //
NK062(khu)001:2557: de ltar dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams rab gnas dang ldan par byas te /
NK062(khu)001:2558: dkyil 'khor gsum po de dag tu sngar bshad pa
NK062(khu)001:2559: bzhin slob bu dad pa dang ldan pas rab tu
NK062(khu)001:2560: zhugs par gyur na yon tan ji lta bu 'byung
NK062(khu)001:2561: snyam pa la / 'dod pa yid 'ong mnyam par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2563: 'dod pa'i don dbang dngos grub yid du 'ong ba thams cad thob pas na /
NK062(khu)001:2564: sngon 'og min du mthar lam bzhugs pa dang skal ba mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK062(khu)001:2566: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bar legs zhugs pas //
NK062(khu)001:2567: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK062(khu)001:2568: dkyil 'khor kun tu zhugs pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:2569: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:2570: 'khor lo mngon du mthong zhugs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:2571: bsod nams rtag pa gang yin pa //
NK062(khu)001:2572: phyis byas de bzhin lung bstan phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2574: stangs dpyal nyis sam yang na lnga //
NK062(khu)001:2575: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs na //
NK062(khu)001:2577: mngon byas pa dang mnyam par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2578: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK062(khu)001:2579: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2580: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rigs nges shing //
NK062(khu)001:2581: gdon rnams bzlog cing ngan song sbyong //
NK062(khu)001:2582: longs spyod 'du ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK062(khu)001:2583: ye shes spyan gyis rang bzhin nges //
NK062(khu)001:2584: de la sogs pa bsam yas mchog /
NK062(khu)001:2586: gnyis pa khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2587: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de bzhin te //
NK062(khu)001:2589: 'dir sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la yang sa
NK062(khu)001:2590: gzhi mnyam pa la sogs pa spyi don bcus ston
NK062(khu)001:2591: kyang spyir zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su bshad
NK062(khu)001:2592: pa de bzhin du bya bas te 'on kyang dang
NK062(khu)001:2593: po sa gzhi mnyam pa la brgyad yod pa'i sa
NK062(khu)001:2595: gnas ma mo 'du ba'i dur khrod du bya bar shis so //
NK062(khu)001:2596: drug pa sa byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2597: brgyad pa sa gzung ba khro bos bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2599: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi tshad mthun no //
NK062(khu)001:2600: gsum pa thig la ye shes kyi thig skud rgyus chen la bya /
NK062(khu)001:2602: thig gdab pa'i thabs kyang khro bo'i lugs su gdab bo //
NK062(khu)001:2603: bzhi pa tshon la thal chen bsres la rab gnas khro bos bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2604: lnga pa bri thabs la khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bar khyams gnyis pa bya /
NK062(khu)001:2605: drug pa rnam pa dgod pa khro bo'i sku gsung thugs dgod /
NK062(khu)001:2606: bdun pa rab gnas la las sbyor khro bo'i gzhung bsrang /
NK062(khu)001:2607: mnga' gsol gyi skabs su tho mar bum pa /
NK062(khu)001:2608: de nas rol pa nyi shu /
NK062(khu)001:2612: mnga' gsol brgyad cus mnga' gsol lo //
NK062(khu)001:2617: tshig kyang zhi ba dang mi mthun no //
NK062(khu)001:2618: khrus ras kyis sku phyi ba yang dur khrod ras chen gyis bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2619: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa khro bo ltar ro //
NK062(khu)001:2620: bdun pa bden pas brtan par bzhugs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2621: brgyad pa bskor ba dang smon lam yang khro bo'i rab gnas nas bshad pa ltar ro //
NK062(khu)001:2622: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga gzhan rnams 'dra ba la /
NK062(khu)001:2623: lhar brlab pa dang lha dbab pa khro bos bya /
NK062(khu)001:2624: bcu pa zhugs pa'i yon tan zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhin no //
NK062(khu)001:2625: gsum pa mchog gi dkyil 'khor zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor ltar shes par gdams pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2626: bsam yas dag la'ang de bzhin bya //
NK062(khu)001:2627: rig pas dpag pa tsam du'o //
NK062(khu)001:2629: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa mchog gi dkyil 'khor
NK062(khu)001:2630: dag la'ang zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su bshad
NK062(khu)001:2631: pa de bzhin du spyi don bcur shes par bya
NK062(khu)001:2632: ste / dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2633: chos thams cad mnyam par rtogs shing de'i ngang du 'jog pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2635: rang gi rig pas dpag cing blos ji tsam lcogs pa'i tshad tsam du bsgom par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2637: rang rig pa nyid dkyil 'khor du gsal ba las mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:2639: sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar mtshon pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2641: sems nyid mnyam pa nyid la sku dang ye shes
NK062(khu)001:2642: kyi dkyil 'khor ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su gsal ba'o
NK062(khu)001:2643: // drug pa rnam pa dgod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2646: dran rig thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du ma 'gags par dgod pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2652: mchod pa'i rim pa rnams bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2654: bde ba chen po don rgyud la sbyin zhing rnam rtog rang rgyud pa sreg pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2655: dgu pa dkyil du 'jug pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2656: rgyun bshags kyis gsal btab la rgyun chad med par nyams su len pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2657: bcu pa zhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK062(khu)001:2658: sngon 'og min du mthar lam pa zhugs pa dang
NK062(khu)001:2659: skal pa mnyam pa sngar dang rjes su mthun no
NK062(khu)001:2660: // spyi don gnyis pa dbang ye shes rdo rje la gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:2661: dbang gi sngon du rgyu yon dbul ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:2662: snod dang sbyar la bskur ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:2663: gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2664: dang po dbang gi sngon rgyu yon dbul ba bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2665: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK062(khu)001:2666: rgyal srid dang ni dag par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2668: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK062(khu)001:2670: dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa la de dbang bskur bston pas na nas zhes pa'am /
NK062(khu)001:2671: dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba rdzogs pa de nas dkyil
NK062(khu)001:2672: 'khor du zhugs pa'i gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i
NK062(khu)001:2673: rigs kyi bu mchog dbang thob par 'dod pa des
NK062(khu)001:2674: dbang zhu ba'i sngon du dbang thob par bya ba'i
NK062(khu)001:2675: rgyu tshogs mchog yon dbul bar bya ste /
NK062(khu)001:2676: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK062(khu)001:2678: rang gi yi dam gyi lha de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK062(khu)001:2679: rigs la me tog phog pa yin na rang gi
NK062(khu)001:2681: rdo rje'i rigs yin na ni rang gi lus dbul lo //
NK062(khu)001:2682: 'o na rgyal srid med pa rnams yon mi dbul lam zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:2683: rang dbang ba'i dngos po ci yin pa thams cad dbul gsung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:2684: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK062(khu)001:2686: yi dam pad+ma'i rigs la me tog phog pa yin na /
NK062(khu)001:2688: rin po che'i rigs la rin po che dngos sam
NK062(khu)001:2689: nor gyi dbyig ste rang gi nor gyi drag shos
NK062(khu)001:2690: dbul lo // rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK062(khu)001:2692: las kyi rigs la rang la gang rab tu gces pa de dbul pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2693: yi dam gyi lha rigs thams cad kyi bdag po
NK062(khu)001:2694: drug pa kun tu bzang po yin na bla ma'i
NK062(khu)001:2695: yin la ci 'thad pa dbul ba yin te /
NK062(khu)001:2696: thugs la 'thad na rang gi las kyi phyag rgya ste gzungs ma yang dbul lo //
NK062(khu)001:2698: de ltar bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la yon
NK062(khu)001:2699: phul ba de'i yon tan la dgos pa ci zhig
NK062(khu)001:2701: dbang phyug longs spyod lngas mchod na //
NK062(khu)001:2702: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:2704: dbang phyug bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la dbul
NK062(khu)001:2705: bar bya ba gong du bshad pa'i yon rnams dang
NK062(khu)001:2706: / gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya la sogs pa
NK062(khu)001:2707: 'dod yon lnga'i longs spyod kyis mnyes par mchod na
NK062(khu)001:2708: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod par 'gyur ba
NK062(khu)001:2709: / yin te / dbang phyug bla ma nyid rgyal
NK062(khu)001:2710: ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi bdag nyid dam ngo
NK062(khu)001:2712: dgongs pa tha mi dad pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:2713: bla ma la mchod pa phul bas dus gsum gyi
NK062(khu)001:2714: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad la mchod pa phul
NK062(khu)001:2716: de yang mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa las /
NK062(khu)001:2717: bskal pa 'bum gyi sangs rgyas pas //
NK062(khu)001:2718: bla ma gnyan par shes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2719: ci phyir bskal pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK062(khu)001:2720: bla ma dag la brten nas byung //
NK062(khu)001:2722: bla ma lnga bcu pa las /
NK062(khu)001:2723: de sbyin sangs rgyas thams cad la //
NK062(khu)001:2724: rtag tu byin pa nyid du 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2726: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor smos ci dgos //
NK062(khu)001:2728: dbang phyug bla ma rdo rje slob dpon nyid mchod
NK062(khu)001:2729: pas nye ba yi dam lha'i dkyil 'khor thams cad
NK062(khu)001:2730: mnyes pa dang 'grub pa la lta smos kyang ci
NK062(khu)001:2731: dgos te / nyes pa thams cad 'dag par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:2733: thun mong gi nyes pa mi dge bcu mtshams med
NK062(khu)001:2734: pa lnga de dang nye ba lnga lci ba bzhi
NK062(khu)001:2735: log pa brgyad la sogs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2736: thun mong ma yin pa'i nyes pa gsang sngags kyi
NK062(khu)001:2737: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa'i
NK062(khu)001:2738: sdig pa dang sgrib pa thams cad byang zhing dag
NK062(khu)001:2739: par 'gyur bas de'i phyir yon la ser sna spang
NK062(khu)001:2740: ngo zhes bya'o // gnyis pa snod dang sbyar la bskur ba'i rim pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2743: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK062(khu)001:2744: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK062(khu)001:2746: slob bu'i mtshan nyid rtog pa la mkhas pa'i slob dpon gyis /
NK062(khu)001:2747: 'og nas rab rtogs na zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:2748: slob bu snod dang ldan mi ldan phyi mtshan nyid
NK062(khu)001:2749: rab tu rtogs nas snod dang mi ldan pa'i slob
NK062(khu)001:2750: ma spang la / snod ldan gyi slob bu gsang
NK062(khu)001:2751: sngags kyi theg pa 'di la dad pa dang ldan
NK062(khu)001:2752: pa rnams la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu sbyin zhing
NK062(khu)001:2753: ma spang la / / brtson 'grus can la nang nus pa'i dbang lnga sbyin par bya ste /
NK062(khu)001:2755: bdag don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nyan pa dang sgom pa'i dbang gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:2756: gzhan don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la 'di steng du 'chad pa dang phrin las kyi dbang gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:2757: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la /
NK062(khu)001:2758: de'i steng du rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang sbyin no //
NK062(khu)001:2759: brtul zhugs can la gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum sbyin te /
NK062(khu)001:2761: spyod pa'i brtul zhugs can la gsang ba'i dbang //
NK062(khu)001:2762: rig pa'i brtul zhugs can la shes rab ye shes
NK062(khu)001:2763: kyi dbang mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la dbyer med
NK062(khu)001:2764: bde ba chen po'i dbang sbyin par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2765: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2767: de ltar snod kyi rim pa bzhin du phan nus
NK062(khu)001:2768: zab mo'i dbang rnams rang rang gi blo dang 'tshams
NK062(khu)001:2769: tshod du sbyin par bya zhing /
NK062(khu)001:2770: snying rjes chud ma zos par gzung //
NK062(khu)001:2772: rdo rje slob dpon gyis slob bu la don du
NK062(khu)001:2773: mi 'gyur ba'i dbang byin na rdza snod du seng
NK062(khu)001:2774: zho blugs pa dang mtshungs pas /
NK062(khu)001:2775: slob dpon gyi snying rje'i kun nas blangs pa'i sems kyis snod dang 'tshams par byin la /
NK062(khu)001:2776: slob bu chud ma zos par rjes su gzung bar bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2777: gsum pa gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:2779: de la gdan dang sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma dgod pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2780: dang po tshad dngos la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:2781: pad+ma'i tshad sor bzhi pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2782: rdo rje'i tshad mdzub gang ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:2783: dang po pad+ma'i tshad sor bzhi pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:2784: shin tu phra ba'i bzhi yi tshad du bya //
NK062(khu)001:2786: de yang spyir gsang ba sgyu 'phrul gyi lugs kyi
NK062(khu)001:2787: dkyil 'khor bzhi ru dbang lnga skur bar byed pa
NK062(khu)001:2788: yin te / phyi rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor du phan dbang /
NK062(khu)001:2789: nang lus kyi dkyil 'khor du nus dbang /
NK062(khu)001:2790: gsang ba b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor du gsang dbang dang shes rab ye shes kyi dbang /
NK062(khu)001:2791: de kho na nyid sems kyi dkyil 'khor du /
NK062(khu)001:2792: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ba yin pa la /
NK062(khu)001:2793: skabs 'dir gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor ston par byed de /
NK062(khu)001:2794: de yang yab yum gyi mkha' gsang mtshon par byed
NK062(khu)001:2795: pa yin pas gser dngul zangs lcags la sogs pa
NK062(khu)001:2797: ras sam gro shog la sogs pa la ris su bris pa'am /
NK062(khu)001:2798: tsan+dana gor+shi sha la sogs pa la rkos su brkos pa'ang rung ste /
NK062(khu)001:2799: shin tu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK062(khu)001:2801: sngar gyi dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gyi tshad
NK062(khu)001:2802: khru gang ba la sogs pa la ltos na sor
NK062(khu)001:2803: bzhi pa 'di las chung tshad gzhan med pas /
NK062(khu)001:2804: shin tu phra ba'i dkyil 'khor te spyod pa'i brtul
NK062(khu)001:2805: zhugs can gyi slob bu la bde ba'i ye shes
NK062(khu)001:2806: mtshon cing sbyor ba las mi 'da' bas na dam
NK062(khu)001:2808: dkyil 'khor de gang du dgod na /
NK062(khu)001:2809: phyag rgya chen po'i phyag mthil du //
NK062(khu)001:2811: rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku phyag rgya chen por
NK062(khu)001:2812: bsgom pa'i phyag mnyam gzhag gi mthil du dgod pa'o
NK062(khu)001:2814: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa de //
NK062(khu)001:2816: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa bde ba'i ye shes skye ba'i yul gsang ba'i pad+ma yin pas /
NK062(khu)001:2817: de mtshon byed pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma bzhi pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2818: dkyil 'khor de'i tshad ji tsam zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:2819: sor ni bzhi yi tshad du bya //
NK062(khu)001:2821: yum gyi gsang gnas mtshon pa yin pas sor ni bzhi pa'i tshad du bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2823: phyag rgya chen po nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK062(khu)001:2824: sor bzhi'i tshad du ra bzhin gnas //
NK062(khu)001:2825: bde ba'i ye shes thugs dkyil 'khor //
NK062(khu)001:2826: kha dog dbyibs dang ldan par bya //
NK062(khu)001:2827: thabs kyi rab gnas cho gar ldan //
NK062(khu)001:2828: 'jug pa pos kyang gsol ba gdab //
NK062(khu)001:2830: gnyis pa rdo rje'i tshad mdzub gang ba bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2831: yang na thal mo bzhin du bya //
NK062(khu)001:2834: pad+ma'i tshad las yang na rdo rje'i tshad bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2837: thal mo ni slob dpon yab yum gnyis sku phyag rgya chen por bsgom pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:2838: yab yum gnyis kyi dbang po rab tu bsnol nas /
NK062(khu)001:2839: phyag rgya chen po'i pang du ni //
NK062(khu)001:2841: slob dpon yab yum sku phyag rgya chen por bsgom pa'i bang du ni'o //
NK062(khu)001:2843: bde ba'i ye shes skye ba'i rten gsang ba'i rdo
NK062(khu)001:2844: rje de mtshon par byed pa'i rdo rje sngon po
NK062(khu)001:2845: rtse lnga pa'o // dkyil 'khor de'i tshad ji tsam snyam na /
NK062(khu)001:2846: dkyil 'khor mdzub gang tshad du yang //
NK062(khu)001:2848: yab kyi gsang gnas mtshon pa yin pas dkyil 'khor mdzub gang ba'i tshad du yang bya ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:2849: mkhas pas cho ga bzhin du bya //
NK062(khu)001:2851: lag len la bzo bo mkhas pas gong gi rgyu
NK062(khu)001:2852: rnams la rdo rje rtse lnga pa cho ga ji
NK062(khu)001:2853: lta ba bzhin du bzo bar bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2855: mkhas pas cho ga bzhin du bya //
NK062(khu)001:2857: gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor la mkhas pas zhi ba'i
NK062(khu)001:2858: dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga bzhin du sa'i cho ga
NK062(khu)001:2859: la sogs pa don bcur bya ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:2860: mtshon byed rtags kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2863: thal mo zhes bya sdebs pa'i sgra //
NK062(khu)001:2864: dbang po'i yul du rab sbyor bas //
NK062(khu)001:2865: phyag rgya chen po nam mkha'i dbyibs //
NK062(khu)001:2866: brtul zhugs gnyis kyis pang du blang //
NK062(khu)001:2867: rdo rje mdzub mo'i rtse dag tu //
NK062(khu)001:2868: til 'bru nam mkha'i gzhal yas su //
NK062(khu)001:2869: ri rab tsam gyi phyag rgya dgod //
NK062(khu)001:2870: thabs kyi cho ga rab gnas dang //
NK062(khu)001:2871: gsang ba'i sbyin sreg lugs su dbul //
NK062(khu)001:2873: rdo rje las rim las kyang /
NK062(khu)001:2874: shin tu phra ba gzhan dkyil 'khor //
NK062(khu)001:2875: gtso bo thugs te rigs ldan pa //
NK062(khu)001:2876: rnam pa'ang rim pa'i skabs su bshad //
NK062(khu)001:2878: gnyis pa de la gdan dang sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma dgod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2881: de yang sor bzhi pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi pad+ma'i dbus kyi lte ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:2882: phyogs kyi 'dab ma rnams la nyi ma dang /
NK062(khu)001:2883: mdzub gang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi rdo rje'i rwa dbus
NK062(khu)001:2884: ma dag phyogs kyi rwa rnams la zla ba 'god
NK062(khu)001:2885: de / de dag che chung gi tshad ni /
NK062(khu)001:2886: sen zlum tsam gyi nyi zla la //
NK062(khu)001:2888: sen mo zlum po tsam gyi nyi ma dang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK062(khu)001:2891: sran ma tsan ka'i 'bru slebs pa tsam gyi pad+ma'i gdan gyi thog tu /
NK062(khu)001:2892: yungs 'bru tsam gyi yi ge las //
NK062(khu)001:2894: yungs kar gyi 'bru tsam gyi yi ge 'god de /
NK062(khu)001:2895: de yang sor bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi nyi ma la
NK062(khu)001:2896: gnas pa'i pad+ma rnams kyi steng du yum gyi 'bru
NK062(khu)001:2897: lnga dang / mdzub gang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi zla
NK062(khu)001:2898: ba la gnas pa'i pad+ma rnams la yab kyi 'bru
NK062(khu)001:2900: yab yum gyi yig 'bru bcu po rnams yongs su gyur pa las /
NK062(khu)001:2901: phyag rgya til 'bru tsam du bri //
NK062(khu)001:2902: zhes pas rigs lnga yab yum gyi sku phyag rgya chen po til 'bru tsam du bri zhes pa'am /
NK062(khu)001:2904: yi ge yungs 'bru tsam la sku nas 'bru tsam 'god pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2905: yi ge til 'bru tsam la sku yungs 'bru tsam 'god pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2907: de ltar mtshon byed rtags kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis la
NK062(khu)001:2908: gdan dang sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma ji ltar
NK062(khu)001:2910: yab yum gnyis snyoms par 'jug pa'i sngon du yang
NK062(khu)001:2911: mkha' gsang gnyis la gdan dang sku gsung thugs kyi
NK062(khu)001:2912: mtshan ma yab kyis yum dang yum gyis yab la
NK062(khu)001:2913: 'god par bya'o // spyi don gsum pa sgrub pa ye shes rdo rje la gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:2914: tshogs kyi sgrub pa po'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK062(khu)001:2915: 'bras bu rig 'dzin bsgrub pa'i dus dang /
NK062(khu)001:2916: de ltar bsgrubs pa'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas 'thob tshul bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:2917: dang po tshogs kyi sgrub pa po'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK062(khu)001:2918: cho ga lnga ni rab brtson na //
NK062(khu)001:2920: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing //
NK062(khu)001:2922: de bzhin nyid kyi cho ga dang kun tu snang
NK062(khu)001:2923: gi cho ga dang phyag rgya gcig pa la phra
NK062(khu)001:2924: ba yig 'bru la bslab pa'i cho ga dang rags
NK062(khu)001:2925: pa lha sku la bslab pa'i cho ga dang phyag
NK062(khu)001:2926: rgya spros pa dang bcas pa'i cho ga ste /
NK062(khu)001:2927: cho ga lnga ni sngon du rdzogs par byas shing zhes bla ma gong ma rnas gsung la /
NK062(khu)001:2929: de ting dang kun ting dang phyag rgya gcig pa
NK062(khu)001:2930: la sku gsung thugs kyi cho ga gsum dang ldan
NK062(khu)001:2931: gsungs te / de dang mthun par 'grel chung las kyang /
NK062(khu)001:2932: dang po stong pa'i byang chub gnyis pa snying rje yin //
NK062(khu)001:2933: gsum pa yi ge bzhi pa dam tshig phyag rgya'o //
NK062(khu)001:2934: lnga pa la ni gzugs rdzogs lha skur ldan pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:2936: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK062(khu)001:2940: rgyan dang bgo ba'i yo byad /
NK062(khu)001:2941: bza' ba dang btung ba'i yo byad //
NK062(khu)001:2942: +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad dang lnga ni tshogs sgrub pa'i sngon du rdzogs par byas nas /
NK062(khu)001:2943: gnas 'khor khang phyi nang bar gsum dang ldan par /
NK062(khu)001:2944: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pas //
NK062(khu)001:2949: byin gyis brlab kyi phyir sngags te lha'o //
NK062(khu)001:2950: zhes pas sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum ye shes
NK062(khu)001:2951: sems dpa' dang bzhi dbu rgyan rigs lnga'i lha gcig
NK062(khu)001:2952: tu byas pas / sngags kyi yan lag lnga lnga
NK062(khu)001:2953: dang ldan pa'o zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsungs
NK062(khu)001:2954: tu byas pas / la / 'grel pa spar khab las /
NK062(khu)001:2955: de nyid kyi lus kyi yan lag mgo bo la
NK062(khu)001:2956: sogs pa la phyag rgya lnga bcu tham pa rgyas
NK062(khu)001:2957: pa'i rgyud bzhin du bkod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2958: rtog pa'i yan lag phung po la sogs pa dkyil
NK062(khu)001:2959: 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis gnyis su snang ba rnam
NK062(khu)001:2961: de nyid kyi yan lag gcig la yang de dag tshang bar dgod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:2962: de dag la yang rdo rje gsum bsgom pa dang dbang bskur ba'i yan lag dang lnga rdzogs te /
NK062(khu)001:2963: snang ba rnam par 'byed pa la dbang thob nas zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:2964: gong dang cung mi mthun par gsung la /
NK062(khu)001:2966: snying gar ye shes sems bsgom snying gar nyi zla'i dkyil //
NK062(khu)001:2967: dam tshig phyag rgya bzhag ste de steng yig 'bru bzhag /
NK062(khu)001:2968: zlos tshe spros bsdus bzlas pa yan lag yin //
NK062(khu)001:2970: de ltar yan lag lnga po de dag rdzogs par gsal ba'i rnal 'byor bas /
NK062(khu)001:2971: ma nyams 'jug la rab brtson na //
NK062(khu)001:2973: de ltar gong gi lnga tshan gsum po'i lta ba
NK062(khu)001:2974: dang rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga yan lag gi bcu
NK062(khu)001:2975: la sogs pa ma nyams par tshogs sgrub pa'i ting
NK062(khu)001:2976: nge 'dzin dang spyod pa la 'jug cing /
NK062(khu)001:2977: sgrub pa nyams su len pa la rab tu brtson
NK062(khu)001:2978: par byas na sgrub pa pos tshogs 'grub par gsungs
NK062(khu)001:2979: so // gnyis pa 'bras bu rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:2980: zhag ni sum cu dam pa 'grub //
NK062(khu)001:2982: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK062(khu)001:2984: lta ba dang dam tshig ma nyams par brtson pa
NK062(khu)001:2985: la gnas na blo dang brtson 'grus rab kyis zhag
NK062(khu)001:2986: ni sum cu phrag drug ste zla ba drug gam
NK062(khu)001:2987: / bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK062(khu)001:2989: 'bring gis zla ba bcu gnyis te lo gcig gam /
NK062(khu)001:2990: yang na zla ba bcu bzhi ste lo gcig zla ba gnyis sam /
NK062(khu)001:2991: tha mas kyang zla ba bcu drug gis te lo gcig zla ba bzhi yis /
NK062(khu)001:2992: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK062(khu)001:2994: dbang po rtul na rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin nam /
NK062(khu)001:2995: dbang po rno na tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rig
NK062(khu)001:2996: 'dzin rnams kyi nang nas dam pa ste mchog tu
NK062(khu)001:2997: gyur pa lus mi 'dor bar lam mchog yongs su
NK062(khu)001:2998: rdzogs pa'i tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin nyid 'grub
NK062(khu)001:2999: par 'gyur ro // 'di la gsang sngags kyi bstan
NK062(khu)001:3000: pa'i mnga' bdag 'jam pa'i dbyangs chen po'i gsung gis
NK062(khu)001:3001: par 'gyur ro // / 'bras bu 'grub pa'i dus la gnyis su 'dod de /
NK062(khu)001:3002: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus dang mthar thug sku lnga 'grub pa'i dus so //
NK062(khu)001:3003: dang po ni gong du smos pa'i dus rab 'bring tha gsum yin la /
NK062(khu)001:3005: de tshe bcu drug tshul chad kyis //
NK062(khu)001:3006: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:3008: mthong lam tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob pa de'i tshe /
NK062(khu)001:3009: lo brgya tshan pa bcu drug ste stong drug brgya tshun chad kyis bsnur zhing bsgrub pas /
NK062(khu)001:3010: mthar lam chags pa'i dbang du sgom lam phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK062(khu)001:3011: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin gnyis bgrod nas mthar thug la sbyor la /
NK062(khu)001:3012: lam thod rgal gyi dbang du tshe dbang de nyid
NK062(khu)001:3013: kyis mthar thug gi 'bras bu sku lnga lhun gyis
NK062(khu)001:3014: grub pa mngon du rdzogs par gyur pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:3016: tshe ni bcu dang drug pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:3017: brgya brgya dag tu bsnur zhing gnas //
NK062(khu)001:3018: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas sa //
NK062(khu)001:3020: gsum pa de ltar bsgrubs pa'i mthar thug gi 'bras
NK062(khu)001:3021: bu sangs rgyas thob pa'i tshul bstan pa la gnyis
NK062(khu)001:3022: te / 'bras bu thob pa'i tshul dang /
NK062(khu)001:3024: dang po 'bras bu thob pa'i tshul la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:3025: 'grub tshul rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:3026: de ltar 'grub pa'i dus dpe'i sgo nas rang snang du bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:3027: dang po 'grub tshul rang snang du bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:3028: ye shes thig le rang snang ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:3030: ye shes thig le de nyid la //
NK062(khu)001:3032: mthar lam chags pa'i dbang du lhun grub rig 'dzin dang /
NK062(khu)001:3033: thod rgal gyi dbang du tshe la dbang ba'i rig
NK062(khu)001:3034: 'dzin gyi dgongs pa rang rig pa'i ye shes spros
NK062(khu)001:3035: pa dang bral ba'i thig le de nyid kyi ngo
NK062(khu)001:3036: la / ye shes thig le nyid snang ba //
NK062(khu)001:3038: mnyam gzhag gi dus su rgyal ba'i dgongs pa spros
NK062(khu)001:3039: pa dang bral ba'i ye shes kyi thig le de
NK062(khu)001:3042: bde 'dus ye shes thig le las //
NK062(khu)001:3043: mtha' yas ye shes rang snang ba //
NK062(khu)001:3044: ma btsal lhun grub rig 'dzin mchog /
NK062(khu)001:3046: tshe dbang thod rgal ba lhun grub rig 'dzin la
NK062(khu)001:3047: sbyor ba'am de bas kyang blo chen mthar thug sangs
NK062(khu)001:3048: rgyas kyi sa la sbyor ba'ang yod de /
NK062(khu)001:3050: tshe ni bcu dang drug pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:3051: brgya brgya dag tu bsnur zhing gnas //
NK062(khu)001:3052: lus ma bor bar sangs rgya sa sa //
NK062(khu)001:3054: bsam gyis mi khyab mtha' yas mchog /
NK062(khu)001:3056: de yang tshe dbang thod rgal ba'am lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK062(khu)001:3057: bsam gyis mi khyab pa yi ge 'khor lo'i sa'i
NK062(khu)001:3058: yon tan brjod pa las 'das pas mtha' yas pa'i
NK062(khu)001:3059: ye shes rang la snang bas ma btsal bar lhun
NK062(khu)001:3060: gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin ni rig 'dzin kun gyi
NK062(khu)001:3061: mchog ces bya'o // phyogs bcu dus bzhi mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:3063: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi'i rgyal ba yang dag pa
NK062(khu)001:3064: mngon par rdzogs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsum
NK062(khu)001:3066: zhing khams rnams dag bsam yas dang //
NK062(khu)001:3068: zhing khams rnam par dag pa dang ma dag pa dang bar ma dang gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:3069: zhing khams de dag kyang mnyen pa dang 'jam pa la sogs pa'i yon tan bsam yas pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:3070: rgya dang bral ba'i gzhal yang khang //
NK062(khu)001:3072: rig pa nyid rang byung gi ye shes shar bas
NK062(khu)001:3073: rgya dang bral ba'i phyir blo sa gzhal ba las
NK062(khu)001:3075: 'khor lo rgyan dang rol mo'i tshogs //
NK062(khu)001:3077: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang lnga'i rgyan gdan
NK062(khu)001:3078: khri dang bcas pa rol mo'i bye brag 'dod yon
NK062(khu)001:3079: gyi lha mo la sogs pa gzhal yas khang gi
NK062(khu)001:3081: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsam yas kun //
NK062(khu)001:3083: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa'i sku gsung thugs
NK062(khu)001:3084: yon tan phrin las lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga la
NK062(khu)001:3085: sogs pa bsam yas pa kun kyang /
NK062(khu)001:3086: mthong nas nye bar brnyes pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:3088: skad cig ma dang po mnyam gzhag la mthong nas
NK062(khu)001:3089: skad cig gnyis pa rjes thob la nye bar brnyes
NK062(khu)001:3090: pa ste dus gcig tu gsal bar snang nas thob
NK062(khu)001:3091: pa dang / rgya chen gsung las don 'byung ba'ang //
NK062(khu)001:3093: rgyal ba de dag gi rig pa'i gsung lnga lhun
NK062(khu)001:3094: gyis grub pas na rgya chen po'i gsung las basngagasa
NK062(khu)001:3097: dbang bskur ba thob pa la sogs pa'i don 'byung ba'ang /
NK062(khu)001:3098: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:3100: de las mi slob pa'i bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin mngon du byas pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:3101: gzhi rang byung gi ye shes rang la gnas pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:3102: lam rig pa'i ye shes kyis rtogs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:3103: 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes mngon du byas pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:3104: ye shes de gsum tshul gcig tu gyur pas mthun pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:3107: gnyis pa de ltar 'grub pa'i dus dpe'i sgo nas rang snang du bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:3108: dpag bsam shing dang ngang du byung //
NK062(khu)001:3110: gong du bstan pa'i 'bras bu de dag rang la snang ba'i tshul ji lta bu snyam pa la /
NK062(khu)001:3111: dpag bsam shing dang yid bzhin gyi //
NK062(khu)001:3112: rin po che dang 'byung ba kun //
NK062(khu)001:3114: dper na byang sgra mi snyan na dpag bsam gyi shing la dgos 'dod 'byung ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:3115: lho 'dzam bu gling gi yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che la dgos 'dod 'byung ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:3116: lha'i yul na lha'i bum pa bzang po la dgos
NK062(khu)001:3117: 'dod 'byung ba dang gsum po de dag la rang
NK062(khu)001:3119: de dag rdzas yod ma yin te //
NK062(khu)001:3121: dpe gsum po de dag snang tshul la dngos po
NK062(khu)001:3122: rdzas grub ltar snang yang don la de dag rdzas
NK062(khu)001:3123: su grub pa rdul tsam yang yod pa ma yin
NK062(khu)001:3124: te / 'o na gang las byung zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:3125: rang sems bsod nams brtan pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:3127: 'gro ba rang gi sems kyi snang ba bsod nams
NK062(khu)001:3128: cha mthun gyis mthus brtan par snang nas dgos 'dod
NK062(khu)001:3131: 'khor lo sgyur rgyal dpag bsam shing dang bum pa bzang //
NK062(khu)001:3132: longs spyod de dag rang sems snang las gzhan ma yin //
NK062(khu)001:3134: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK062(khu)001:3136: dpe gsum po ltar snang ba de bzhin du /
NK062(khu)001:3137: gzhi sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes ci yang
NK062(khu)001:3138: ma yin pa la cir yang snang bas na ngo
NK062(khu)001:3139: mtshar zhing / sems kyi cho 'phrul sku gsung thugs
NK062(khu)001:3140: yon tan phrin las lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga la
NK062(khu)001:3141: sogs pa mtha' yas pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK062(khu)001:3142: rang las byung ba ni rmad kyi chos so //
NK062(khu)001:3143: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK062(khu)001:3145: de dag rang rig pa nyid yin pa la gzhan
NK062(khu)001:3146: yod pa cig bkug pa dang bgrod pa ste gzhan
NK062(khu)001:3147: nas 'ong ba cig ma yin te /
NK062(khu)001:3148: rgyu rkyen gyis ma byas pa'i phyir ro //
NK062(khu)001:3149: 'o na de dag gang las byung zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:3150: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK062(khu)001:3152: thabs snang la 'gag pa med pa la blos brtan
NK062(khu)001:3153: pa thob pa'i shes rab rang bzhin med pa nyid
NK062(khu)001:3154: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK062(khu)001:3156: yang na phung po la sogs pa sku gsung thugs
NK062(khu)001:3157: kyi phyag rgyar gsal ba'i thabs de la shes rab
NK062(khu)001:3158: rang rig par rgyun du bsgoms pa brtan pa las
NK062(khu)001:3159: / de lta bu yi ngang du byung //
NK062(khu)001:3161: 'bras bu de lta bu rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa'i ngang du rang byung ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:3162: gnyis pa 'bras bu'i ngo bo bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:3163: rgyu rkyen las ma bskyed cing don byed nus par bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:3164: gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i don rang byung gi ye shes rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:3165: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gdul bya la gzigs tshul bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:3166: dang po rgyu rkyen las ma bskyed cing don byed nus par bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:3167: shes rab dbyings kyi btsan po'i mchog /
NK062(khu)001:3169: shes rab dbyings kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK062(khu)001:3171: chos thams cad bdag gi sems nyid kho na yin
NK062(khu)001:3172: pa'i phyir de nyid dngos po gang du yang mi
NK062(khu)001:3173: dmig par rang gsal ba'i don ni ngo bo nyid
NK062(khu)001:3175: de ka la ming gi rnam grangs su mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings kyi zhes bya ste /
NK062(khu)001:3176: de dag theg pa chen po'i chos nyid ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid do //
NK062(khu)001:3177: thabs kyi phyag rgyar gyur pa'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:3179: don dam de nyid gdod nas 'bras bu dkor bdun
NK062(khu)001:3180: thams cad lhun gyis grub pa nyid thabs kun rdzob
NK062(khu)001:3181: sku dang ye shes kyi phyag rgyar rang snang ba
NK062(khu)001:3182: ste / gyur ba ni gdul bya'i don lam gyi
NK062(khu)001:3183: zhen pa dag pa'i stobs kyis 'bras bu sku dang
NK062(khu)001:3184: ye shes su snang bar gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK062(khu)001:3185: ye shes la ni ye shes rol //
NK062(khu)001:3187: de ltar gzhi don dam lhun gyi grub pa'i ye
NK062(khu)001:3188: shes de nyid la ni 'bras bu kun rdzob grangs
NK062(khu)001:3189: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sku dang ye shes su
NK062(khu)001:3190: rang snang ba de la rol zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:3191: 'o na 'bras bu snang ba de dag yod pa'i mtshan mar 'gyur ro snyam na /
NK062(khu)001:3192: ye shes rol pa nyid kyang gsog /
NK062(khu)001:3194: gzhi'i ye shes la 'bras bu'i ye shes rol pa
NK062(khu)001:3195: de'i ngo bo nyid kyang yang dag par na bden
NK062(khu)001:3196: pa'i dngos po rang rgyud pa 'di 'dra ba ci
NK062(khu)001:3197: yang gzung du med pas na gsog gsob ya ma
NK062(khu)001:3198: barla snying po med pa chu shing rul ba lta
NK062(khu)001:3199: bu ste rang rgyud pas stongs pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:3200: 'o na snying po med pa des 'gro ba'i don brtan par byed mi nus so snyam pa la /
NK062(khu)001:3201: rgyal ba mngon byung skyob pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:3203: rgyal ba sprul pa'i sku 'gro ba rigs drug gi
NK062(khu)001:3204: mngon du byung zhing 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las skyob
NK062(khu)001:3205: pa dang / byin rlabs ston pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK062(khu)001:3207: sprul sku de dag byin rlabs kyis ston pa'i longs
NK062(khu)001:3208: sku'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyang ma grub pa'i dpe
NK062(khu)001:3209: don gong du bshad pa de bzhin te /
NK062(khu)001:3210: don chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes rang snang ba yin pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:3211: bya byed nus pa'i gzi byin gyis //
NK062(khu)001:3213: gdul bya sems can la 'dul byed rgyal ba rnams
NK062(khu)001:3214: kyi sku gsung thugs kyi nus pa'i gzi byin gyis
NK062(khu)001:3216: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po'i mchog /
NK062(khu)001:3218: dper na sgyu mas sprul pa'i rta dang glang po
NK062(khu)001:3219: la sogs pa bden par grub pa med kyang gzhan
NK062(khu)001:3220: snang 'brid pa'i don byed nus pa bzhin du ye
NK062(khu)001:3221: shes sgyu ma lta bu'i rol pas /
NK062(khu)001:3222: gzugs sku gnyis su snang nas don byed tsam na
NK062(khu)001:3223: rang gi ngo bo nyid ni chos nyid 'dus ma
NK062(khu)001:3224: byas pa dang gnyis su mi phyed pa'i phyir skye
NK062(khu)001:3225: 'jigs med pas rdo rje'i sku la btsan po zhes
NK062(khu)001:3226: bya ste / 'dus byas las khyad par du 'phags pas mchog kho na'o //
NK062(khu)001:3227: gnyis pa gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i don
NK062(khu)001:3228: rang byung gi ye shes rang snang du bstan pa
NK062(khu)001:3229: ni / gcig dang du mar gnas med snang //
NK062(khu)001:3231: gcig dang du mar bral ba yi //
NK062(khu)001:3232: mtha' dang dbus med ces pas /
NK062(khu)001:3233: 'khor 'das kun gyi bdag nyid rang rig pa rang
NK062(khu)001:3234: byung gi ye shes dngos po thams cad du rang
NK062(khu)001:3235: snang ba'i phyir gcig gi mtha' dang /
NK062(khu)001:3236: ji ltar snang ba thams cad bdag nyid kyi rang
NK062(khu)001:3237: bzhin las ma 'das pa'i phyir du ma'i mtha' dang
NK062(khu)001:3239: yod med rtag chad 'gro 'ong skye 'gag dran rtog
NK062(khu)001:3240: gi mtha' kun las 'das pa dang der ltos kyi
NK062(khu)001:3241: dbus kyang grub pa med de /
NK062(khu)001:3242: ngo bo nyid 'di 'drar bstan du med pa ni
NK062(khu)001:3243: 'khor 'das thams cad kyi ngo bor lhun gyis grub
NK062(khu)001:3245: sangs rgyas kyi kyang mi gzigs te //
NK062(khu)001:3247: de la bu'i ngo bo nyid mngon du byas pa
NK062(khu)001:3248: ni de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa yang dag par
NK062(khu)001:3250: de nyid kyi kyang dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i
NK062(khu)001:3251: chos thams cad yul dang yul can du'am rten dang
NK062(khu)001:3252: brten can du mi gzigs te /
NK062(khu)001:3253: gzigs par byar med pa'i phyir ro //
NK062(khu)001:3254: 'on kyang dbu ma pa ye shes rgyud chad pa lta bur 'dod pa de ni ma yin te /
NK062(khu)001:3255: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK062(khu)001:3257: rang byung gi ye shes la gnas bya'i yul dang
NK062(khu)001:3258: gnas byed kyi shes pa gnyis med par chos thams
NK062(khu)001:3260: de'i phyir sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa ni chu
NK062(khu)001:3261: la chu thim pa ltar ro gcig tu gyur pa'am
NK062(khu)001:3262: shing du ma spungs pa'i me dpung ltar /
NK062(khu)001:3263: rgyud tha dad pa yang ma yin la gnyis med
NK062(khu)001:3264: kyi mtha' las 'das pas na brjod du med pa
NK062(khu)001:3265: zhes bya'o // de yang man ngag lam rim las /
NK062(khu)001:3266: mtha' kun phyogs su ma chad phyir //
NK062(khu)001:3267: mtha' dang bral phyir ma bral ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:3268: gang yang ma spangs mi ldan pas //
NK062(khu)001:3269: ma bral phyir na bral zhes bya //
NK062(khu)001:3271: gsum pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gdul bya la gzigs tshul bstan pa ni /
