NK062(khu)001:9325: de nas bcom ldan 'das bkod do //
NK062(khu)001:9327: bstan pa yun ring du gnas par bya ba'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:9328: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal he ru kas /
NK062(khu)001:9329: dregs pa can de dag gi 'khor rnams kyi lag
NK062(khu)001:9330: tu dbang rtags lags kyi rdo rje rtse gsum pa
NK062(khu)001:9331: de byin nas / rdo rje mi srin mo la sogs par ming gi dbang bskur te /
NK062(khu)001:9332: dkyil 'khor gyi khyams nang ma'i phyi rim du khyams phyi ma la bkod do //
NK062(khu)001:9333: 'o na le'u'i bco lnga pa 'dir gsungs pa'i ru dra 'di /
NK062(khu)001:9334: rang rgyud pa yin nam sprul pa ba yin /
NK062(khu)001:9336: lung man ngag rig pa gsum dang 'gal ba'i skyon yod de /
NK062(khu)001:9339: khro bo'i tshogs chen po de dag kyang /
NK062(khu)001:9343: sku 'bar ba chen po'i klong na bzhugs pa mthong ngo //
NK062(khu)001:9345: man ngag ni 'grel pa lung bstan las /
NK062(khu)001:9346: mthu 'di dag rang rgyud pa la yod pa ma yin te /
NK062(khu)001:9347: sprul pa ba yin pa la som nyi mi bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:9350: sdig pa gang che che bas 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur /
NK062(khu)001:9352: ru dra rang rgyud par 'dug pas so //
NK062(khu)001:9353: yang ru dra sprul pa yin na lung man ngag rig pa gsum dang 'gal te /
NK062(khu)001:9356: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:9357: brtags pa la mngon par zhen pas /
NK062(khu)001:9362: nyon mongs pa rang kha ma'i bag chags rnams so //
NK062(khu)001:9365: sprul pa ba de rang la dgos ched med par 'gyur te /
NK062(khu)001:9366: ci ste na gdul bya rang rgyud pa med pas so //
NK062(khu)001:9367: yang phyis 'byung bar dogs nas sdig ri skur ba yin no zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:9368: de la'ang dgos ched med de /
NK062(khu)001:9369: sngar dngos su ma byung na phyis kyang 'byung bar mi 'gyur te /
NK062(khu)001:9370: rgyu rkyen la khyad par med pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:9371: 'di la bla ma rgya gab gong pa na re /
NK062(khu)001:9372: 'dir dngos su byung ba ni sprul pa yin la /
NK062(khu)001:9373: 'di dang cha lugs mthun pa'i rang rgyud pa mthu
NK062(khu)001:9374: 'di tsam med pa yang yod pas gnyis ka ltar
NK062(khu)001:9375: shes par bya'o // zhes gsung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:9376: gtsang ba byi ston na re dngos su byung ba
NK062(khu)001:9377: 'di rang sprul pa rang rgyud gnyis ka yin te
NK062(khu)001:9378: / mthar lam nas mdzad pa bcu gnyis ston pas sprul pa yang yin la /
NK062(khu)001:9379: bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa yod pas rang rgyud pa yang yin gsung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:9380: gnyis pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9383: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:9384: gsang ba'i zhes rtogs dka' ba /
NK062(khu)001:9386: de kho na nyid gzhan sel ba /
NK062(khu)001:9387: nges pa the tshom dang bral ba /
NK062(khu)001:9388: las zhes pa de mtshan gyi gzhir gda' /
NK062(khu)001:9389: khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi sprin rnam par spros pa'i le'u ste bco lnga pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9391: khro bo rang bzhin gyi 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i
NK062(khu)001:9392: dkyil 'khor mang nyung gi tshad sprin tsam du gdul
NK062(khu)001:9393: bya ru dra 'khor dang bcas pa'i ngo la rnam
NK062(khu)001:9394: par spros pa ston pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams
NK062(khu)001:9395: tshoms dang ris su gcod cing /
NK062(khu)001:9396: mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis na le'u ste /
NK062(khu)001:9397: de'i grangs nyi shu yod pa las /
NK062(khu)001:9398: yas bgrangs bco lnga pa'i don du gada'o //
NK062(khu)001:9399: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK062(khu)001:9400: rgyud kyi 'brel bshad rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i
NK062(khu)001:9401: sgron me yid bzhin gyi nor bu zhes bya ba
NK062(khu)001:9402: las le'u bco lnga pa'i gzhung don rnam par bshad
NK062(khu)001:9404: da ni le'u bcu drug pa 'di 'chad par byed pa 'di la /
NK062(khu)001:9405: chos tshoms ngos bzung ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK062(khu)001:9406: blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam ston /
NK062(khu)001:9407: lam la thabs lam grol lam gnyis las grol lam ston /
NK062(khu)001:9408: mtshan nyid gsum las rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ston /
NK062(khu)001:9409: rim cig gcar gnyis las rim gyis bston /
NK062(khu)001:9410: snang ba bzhi las lam snang ston /
NK062(khu)001:9411: blo 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don ston /
NK062(khu)001:9412: de la dngos po bcu yod pa las khro bo gsung gi dkyil 'khor ston /
NK062(khu)001:9413: bcu yang brgya'i bdag nyid du byas na dkyil 'khor gyi zhor la ting nge 'dzin ston /
NK062(khu)001:9416: blo tha ma'i chos tshoms bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu yod pa las bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud ston /
NK062(khu)001:9417: gzhan yang spyi 'gro rnams kyis ston par byed do //
NK062(khu)001:9418: 'di nas ma yig brgya dang brgyad cu pa dang
NK062(khu)001:9419: brgya dang gya gcig pa ldeb gnyis tshang mi 'dug
NK062(khu)001:9422: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags kyis bskyed do //
NK062(khu)001:9423: de yang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9424: +amo zhes pa ye shes lnga dang ldan pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9426: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ni /
NK062(khu)001:9427: dpal rdo rje khrag 'thung chen po //
NK062(khu)001:9431: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK062(khu)001:9433: gtum po chen po sngang pa thams cad rtogs shig /
NK062(khu)001:9437: sku gsung thugs su bsdus la gnyis su med par sgrol cig /
NK062(khu)001:9439: bzlas pa las kyi sngags te /
NK062(khu)001:9441: +amo ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK062(khu)001:9444: nyams len gyi skabs su yab yum gyi sngags sdeb pa yin no //
NK062(khu)001:9445: de bzhin du bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9446: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he
NK062(khu)001:9447: ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha
NK062(khu)001:9448: na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK062(khu)001:9449: +amo sarbata th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai sarba dush+tana h+aum phata /
NK062(khu)001:9450: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9451: +amo rat+na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa
NK062(khu)001:9452: tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK062(khu)001:9454: +amo ma h+aa sur+ya rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai bi d+ha ma h+aum phata /
NK062(khu)001:9455: pad+ma he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9456: +amo pad+ma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa
NK062(khu)001:9457: tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK062(khu)001:9459: +amo hri shwa ta sa man+ta pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai kh+aa hi h+aum phata /
NK062(khu)001:9460: karma he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9461: +amo karma ma h+aa sh+ai he ru ka ma h+aa
NK062(khu)001:9462: tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK062(khu)001:9464: +amo sarba a mo g+ha kar+m+aa d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai bi shwa h+aum phata /
NK062(khu)001:9466: gnyis pa gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags la gsum /
NK062(khu)001:9467: gnas ma brgyad bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:9468: yul ma brgyad bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:9469: sgo ma bzhi bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags so //
NK062(khu)001:9470: dang po la gnas ma brgyad bskyed pa rkyeen gyi sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9471: +amo badz+ra koo r+ai ha badz+ra tsan+da l+ai ha /
NK062(khu)001:9475: +amo ni ye shes lnga ldan sngags kyi 'go 'dren /
NK062(khu)001:9476: badz+ra ni rdo rje ste dbang rtags rdo rje rtse lnga pas dbu brgyan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9478: ha rtsa ba'i sa bon no //
NK062(khu)001:9479: de bzhin du badz+ra tsoo r+ai ha /
NK062(khu)001:9494: gnyis pa yul ma brgyad bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9495: +amo badz+ra sid+ha mu kh+ai he badz+ra u lu ka mu kh+ai he /
NK062(khu)001:9499: +amo ni ye shes lnga ldan sngags kyi 'go 'dren /
NK062(khu)001:9500: badz+ra ni rdo rje ste dbang rtags rdo rje rtse lnga pas dbu brgyan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9503: he rtsa ba'i sa bon no //
NK062(khu)001:9505: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai he /
NK062(khu)001:9506: badz+ra sh+ri g+aa la mu kh+ai he /
NK062(khu)001:9507: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK062(khu)001:9508: badz+ra g+h+ri d+ha mu kh+aa he /
NK062(khu)001:9509: badz+ra kam ka mu kh+ai he /
NK062(khu)001:9510: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+ai he /
NK062(khu)001:9511: badz+ra u lu ka mu kh+ai he /
NK062(khu)001:9520: gsum pa sgo ma bzhi bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9523: dbang rtags rdo rje rtse lngas dbu brgyan pa'i sgo skyong ma bzhi bskyed pa'i sngag ni /
NK062(khu)001:9524: badz+ra +aa r+ya te dza te nga dzah badz+ra a mu ka h+aum /
NK062(khu)001:9526: badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya wa tu hoh zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:9530: rdo rje ro langs ma ste /
NK062(khu)001:9531: dzahh+aum bam hohbazhi ni rtsa ba'i sa bon no //
NK062(khu)001:9532: gsum pa dbang mo rnams kyi rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9536: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i thugs ka nas dbang mo
NK062(khu)001:9537: rnams kyi rtsa ba'i sngags sam sa bon phyi khams
NK062(khu)001:9538: dmar po la dgod pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9539: de yang shar gyi ma drug gi rtsa sngags b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK062(khu)001:9540: lho'i ma drug gi rtsa sngags b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK062(khu)001:9541: nub kyi ma drug gi rtsa sngags b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK062(khu)001:9542: byang gi ma drug gi rtsa sngags b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK062(khu)001:9543: sgo ma bzhi'i rtsa sngags b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK062(khu)001:9544: 'di dag la ma nu rag sha s+ai b+h+yo /
NK062(khu)001:9545: zhes pa la sogs bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags kyis /
NK062(khu)001:9546: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK062(khu)001:9547: zhes pa la sogs pa'i sku mdog phyag mtshan rgyan chas dang ldan pa'i skur bskyed pa yin no //
NK062(khu)001:9548: spyi don gnyis pa spyan drang ba la sogs pa las kyi rim pa'i sngags la drug ste /
NK062(khu)001:9549: snyan gsan dbab pa'i sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:9551: rig pa'i me tog dor ba'i sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:9552: dngos grub bskul ba'i tshig sngags dang drin lan gyi tshul du mchod pa'i sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:9553: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la bstim pa'i sngags so //
NK062(khu)001:9554: dang po snyan gsan dbab pa'i sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9555: ru lu ru lu h+aum zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:9556: chos sku skye ba med pa'i ngang las gzugs sku
NK062(khu)001:9557: lha tshogs lnga bcu rtsa brgyad du rongs kyi bzhengs
NK062(khu)001:9558: nas byon ma rag par mos pas /
NK062(khu)001:9559: se gol bsnol mar gdab cing ru lu ru lu
NK062(khu)001:9560: ru lu h+aum zhes pa'i sngags kyis sku gsung thugs
NK062(khu)001:9562: gnyis pa spyan drang ba'i sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9563: e h+ye hi a na ya /
NK062(khu)001:9565: e h+ye hi ni kye kye /
NK062(khu)001:9566: a na ya ni gshegs shig pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9567: de ltar skye ba med pa'i dbyings rnam par dag pa rang bzhin gyi gnas nas /
NK062(khu)001:9568: chos sku las gzugs skur bzhengs pa de rnams /
NK062(khu)001:9569: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis mdun gyi nam
NK062(khu)001:9570: mkha' la rim par spyan drangs nas bzhugs pa la
NK062(khu)001:9572: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor dang me ri 'dab 'byor du gnas par bsgom mo //
NK062(khu)001:9573: gsum pa rig pa'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:9574: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK062(khu)001:9576: ye shes rdo rje khro bo'i dam tshig gis bsdus shig ces pa'i sngags /
NK062(khu)001:9577: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK062(khu)001:9579: ye shes pa dang dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor sku
NK062(khu)001:9580: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las dbyer mi phyed pa
NK062(khu)001:9581: gcig gi ngo bor gsal la rtog pa med par
NK062(khu)001:9582: bsgom pa ni / rig pa'i me tog dor ba zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:9583: bzhi pa dngos grub bskul ba'i sngags ni //
NK062(khu)001:9584: khro la sa ma ya phata /
NK062(khu)001:9586: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK062(khu)001:9588: +amo ni yi ge cha lnga pa ye shes lnga ldan glu'i 'go 'dren pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9589: rang bzhin gyis khro la mdzad pa las kyi phyag rgya'i skur snang nas /
NK062(khu)001:9590: thugs rjes khros pa'i tshul bstan pas dregs pa can
NK062(khu)001:9591: gdug pa'i tshogs kyi gdul bya rnams zhi bar mdzad
NK062(khu)001:9592: pa ni / thugs rje chen po gzhan gyi dpal zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:9593: thugs rje khro dpal rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK062(khu)001:9595: de ltar thugs rje chen po'i khros pa'i tshul gyis
NK062(khu)001:9596: bdag gzhan gyi dpal du gyur pas na chen po
NK062(khu)001:9597: ste / de yang phrin las la phyi bshol med par mdzad pas na rngam pa'i tshogs chen po'o //
NK062(khu)001:9598: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK062(khu)001:9600: khro bo khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi byin rlabs /
NK062(khu)001:9601: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las gzhan las khyad
NK062(khu)001:9602: par du gyur pas ngo mtshar rmad po che de
NK062(khu)001:9603: nyid / de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK062(khu)001:9605: dus da lta nyid du ni bdag la stsal du gsol cig ces gsol ba btab nas /
NK062(khu)001:9606: slar yang thugs dam gnad nas bskul ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:9607: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK062(khu)001:9608: +amo badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya hoh +amo badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya phata /
NK062(khu)001:9609: ces pa'i sngags brjod pa'i don ni ye shes rdo rje khro bo'i dam tshig gis /
NK062(khu)001:9610: bdag dang gnyis su med par mdzod cig /
NK062(khu)001:9611: bdag la mnyes par mdzod cig /
NK062(khu)001:9612: bdag gi gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa sgrol cig pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9613: sngags de thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul bas dgyes nas lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs ka nas /
NK062(khu)001:9614: yig 'bru phata nag po grangs med pa 'phros nas
NK062(khu)001:9615: bdag la phog pa gnyis 'dzin gyi sgrib pa bral
NK062(khu)001:9616: nas / lha rtog gnyis med kyi dngos grub thob par bsam mo //
NK062(khu)001:9617: lnga pa drin lan gyi tshul du mchod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9618: +aa li kha hi hoh zhes pa der gda' zhing /
NK062(khu)001:9619: de yang mchod bar 'bul ba'i rdzas gang zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:9620: a li u li zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9624: ta p+aa li ni bca' ba sna tshogs pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9625: de dag mang por spros la dbul ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:9626: dbul ba'i gnas gang la dbul zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:9629: rgyal ba rigs lnga'i khro bo yab yum gyi tshogs dang /
NK062(khu)001:9630: go na roo tri zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:9631: yon tan drag mo'i tshogs khro mo nyi shu dang /
NK062(khu)001:9632: kha ram yo gi n+ai zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:9633: zhal 'bar ba'i tshogs kyi rnal 'byor ma ste /
NK062(khu)001:9634: ma mo nyer brgyad la sogs pa la dbul lo //
NK062(khu)001:9635: tshul ji ltar dbul zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:9639: des mnyes par mdzod cig pa'i tshul gyi dbul ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:9640: drug pa rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la bstim pa'i sngags ni /
NK062(khu)001:9643: h'u gis rigs lnga yab yum bcu /
NK062(khu)001:9646: phata kyi sgo ma bzhi rnams rim pa bzhin bstim mo //
NK062(khu)001:9647: 'di na med kyang b+h+yo dang ram gnyis 'jug pas /
NK062(khu)001:9648: b+h+yos dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK062(khu)001:9649: ram gyis gzhal yas khang me ri me dpung dang bcas pa rnams bstim mo //
NK062(khu)001:9650: de yang lha la lha thim /
NK062(khu)001:9651: gzhal yas khang la gzhal yas khang thim ste /
NK062(khu)001:9653: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gnyis chu dang 'o ma
NK062(khu)001:9654: 'dres pa bzhin dbyer med du gyur pas bsam mo
NK062(khu)001:9655: // gnyis pa de'i yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9659: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad tshig /
NK062(khu)001:9663: zhes gsung sngags kyi dkyil 'khor gyi don de dag brjod pas /
NK062(khu)001:9664: bzlas pa las kyi sngags kyi mthu 'am byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK062(khu)001:9665: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu kun tu btags pa'i
NK062(khu)001:9666: rnam par rtog pa thams cad mi gnas par byas
NK062(khu)001:9667: pas na tshig / tshabs che bas na rab tu
NK062(khu)001:9668: tshig khyab cing tshabs che bas kun tu tshig go
NK062(khu)001:9673: skyed pa rkyen gyi sngags kyi mathu'am byin gyis brlabs
NK062(khu)001:9674: kyi rtog tshogs thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK062(khu)001:9675: zhing 'bar / tshabs che bas rab tu 'bar /
NK062(khu)001:9676: khyab cing tshabs che bas kun tu 'bar ro //
NK062(khu)001:9677: thams cad du 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs kyis gang /
NK062(khu)001:9679: kun tu gang bar gyur to //
NK062(khu)001:9681: spyan drangs pa la sogs pa las kyi rim pa'i
NK062(khu)001:9682: sngags kyi mathu'am byin gyis brlabs kyi dam tshig gi
NK062(khu)001:9684: 'bar ba khro bo'i lha ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs kyis gang /
NK062(khu)001:9685: tshabs che bas na rab tu gang /
NK062(khu)001:9686: khyab cing tshabs che bas na kun tu gang bar gyur to //
NK062(khu)001:9687: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9690: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:9691: gsang ba'i zhes rtogs dka' ba /
NK062(khu)001:9693: de kho na gzhan sel ba /
NK062(khu)001:9694: nges pa the tshom dang bral ba /
NK062(khu)001:9695: las zhes pa mtshan gyi gzhir gda' /
NK062(khu)001:9696: khro tshogs chen po gsum gyi dkyil 'khor spros pa'i le'u ste bcu drug pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9698: gong du le'u bco lnga pa'i skabs su bshad pa'i
NK062(khu)001:9699: 'bar ba khro bo'i tshogs chen po'i gsung lhag pa
NK062(khu)001:9700: ting nge 'dzin sngags kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rtsa ba'i
NK062(khu)001:9701: sngags dang / bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:9702: las kyi rim pa'i sngags la sogs pa mang po spros nas /
NK062(khu)001:9703: ston pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams tshoms dang ris
NK062(khu)001:9704: su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis
NK062(khu)001:9705: na le'u ste / de'i grangs nyi shu rtsa gnyis
NK062(khu)001:9706: su yod pa las yas bgrangs bcu drug pa'i don
NK062(khu)001:9707: na le'u ste / du gada'o // gsang ba'i snying
NK062(khu)001:9708: po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud kyi 'brel
NK062(khu)001:9709: bshad rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i sgron me yid
NK062(khu)001:9710: bzhin gyi nor bu zhes bya ba las le'u bcu
NK062(khu)001:9711: drug pa'i gzhung don rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9713: // da ni le'u bcu bdun pa 'chad par byed pa 'di la /
NK062(khu)001:9714: chos tshoms ngos bzung pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK062(khu)001:9715: blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam ston /
NK062(khu)001:9716: lam la thabs lam grol lam gnyis las grol lam ston /
NK062(khu)001:9717: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston /
NK062(khu)001:9718: mtshan nyid gsum las rkyen 'jug pa ston /
NK062(khu)001:9719: snang ba bzhi las lam snang ston /
NK062(khu)001:9720: blo 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don ston /
NK062(khu)001:9721: de la bcu yod pa las /
NK062(khu)001:9722: khro bo'i sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ston /
NK062(khu)001:9724: lha bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin ston /
NK062(khu)001:9726: blo tha ma'i chos tshoms bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig
NK062(khu)001:9727: bcu las spyi don bsdu ba dang spyi 'gro gsum
NK062(khu)001:9728: ston no // de ltar ston par byed pa'i le'u bcu bdun pa 'di la don gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:9729: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:9732: dang po gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9735: de nas zhes pas le'u bcu drug par lhag pa
NK062(khu)001:9736: ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor sngags kyi rim
NK062(khu)001:9737: pa rnams bstan pa la de /
NK062(khu)001:9738: le'u bcu bdun pa 'dir lhag pa ting nge 'dzin
NK062(khu)001:9739: sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ston pas na nas
NK062(khu)001:9740: / bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos zhes pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9742: de dag gis dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:9743: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK062(khu)001:9745: gsung sngags kyi dkyil 'khor de dag gis sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:9747: 'khor rnams kyis ched du brjod pa 'di dag brjod do //
NK062(khu)001:9748: gnyis pa le'u'i gzhung bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:9751: dang po sku'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:9752: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:9753: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9754: dang po rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa la yang gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:9755: gzhal yas khang ngo bo rgyan dang bcas pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:9757: dang po gzhal yas khang ngo bo rgyan dang bcas pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9762: me ri me klong du 'bar ba chen po'i khro
NK062(khu)001:9763: bo'i gzhal yas khang ni ye shes lnga dang ldan
NK062(khu)001:9765: rtags 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dbus kyi lte ba dang lnga ldan ba yin /
NK062(khu)001:9766: gru chad bzhi yis rnam par brgyan //
NK062(khu)001:9768: bden pa bzhi dang ldan pa don yin la /
NK062(khu)001:9769: rtags gru chad bzhi'i rnam pas mdzes par brgyan pa /
NK062(khu)001:9770: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK062(khu)001:9772: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa don yin la /
NK062(khu)001:9773: rtags gzhal yas khang gi phyi'i dbyibs gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK062(khu)001:9774: rnam par thar pa'i ting nge 'dzin bzhi dang ldan pa don yin la /
NK062(khu)001:9775: rtags sgo khyud can bzhi dang ldan dang /
NK062(khu)001:9776: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes //
NK062(khu)001:9778: bden pa gnyis dang ldan pa don yin la /
NK062(khu)001:9779: rtags phra men dang dbang phyug ma'i 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes pa /
NK062(khu)001:9780: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi mas brjid //
NK062(khu)001:9782: thod pa sna tshogs kyi rtsig pa'i kha bad las /
NK062(khu)001:9783: sbrul chen gyi zhags pas mgul nas drangs bas /
NK062(khu)001:9784: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed kyi tshul du byas pa /
NK062(khu)001:9785: sna tshogs thod pa'i bar nas nyi ma'i 'od zer 'phro bas brjid pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9788: me'i 'od rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i dbyibs su 'bar
NK062(khu)001:9789: ba'i sprul ba'i khro chung phyi nang du 'phro ba
NK062(khu)001:9790: mang po 'khrug pa'i gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK062(khu)001:9791: gnyis pa gdan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9794: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK062(khu)001:9796: gti mug ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags shar
NK062(khu)001:9797: phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du stobs ldan khyu mchog
NK062(khu)001:9799: nga rgyal ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags lho
NK062(khu)001:9800: phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du brjid pa ma he
NK062(khu)001:9801: dang / 'dod chags ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i
NK062(khu)001:9802: rtags nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du gdug pa
NK062(khu)001:9803: dang / gzig dang / phrag dog ma spangs gnas
NK062(khu)001:9804: su dag pa'i rtags byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng
NK062(khu)001:9806: gtum pa dom gyi spar bas ni //
NK062(khu)001:9808: zhe sdang ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags /
NK062(khu)001:9809: dbus kyi lte ba la gtum pa dom rnams kyi spar bas ni /
NK062(khu)001:9810: dbang phyug lha chen la sogs bzung //
NK062(khu)001:9812: phrin las nan tan du brtan par bya ba'i phyir
NK062(khu)001:9813: 'khor lo'i dbus su 'jig rten gyi dbang phyug lha
NK062(khu)001:9814: chen po dregs pa ru dra pho mo byi chings
NK062(khu)001:9816: la sogs pa'i sogs khong nas /
NK062(khu)001:9817: shar du dri za pho mo /
NK062(khu)001:9819: nub tu srin po pho mo /
NK062(khu)001:9820: byang du gnod sbyin pho mo /
NK062(khu)001:9821: de rnams kyang pho kha bub dang mo gan rkyal
NK062(khu)001:9822: du bsgyel ba'i pho rnams kyi sog phrag dang mo
NK062(khu)001:9823: rnams kyi nu phrag nas bzung ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:9824: de dag ni dregs pa can zil gyis gnon pa'i gdan zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:9825: yon tan gyi che ba rang snang ba'i gdan ni /
NK062(khu)001:9826: nyi zla pad+ma gsum rtseg go //
NK062(khu)001:9827: gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu'i gnas su ro dang nyi ma'i gdan no //
NK062(khu)001:9828: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad la zhing skam po re'i gdan no //
NK062(khu)001:9829: gnyis pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:9830: sku mdog zhal phyag gi don bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:9831: rgyan gyi don bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:9832: phyag mtshan gyi don bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9833: dang po sku mdog zhal phyag gi don bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9836: smug nag sngo nag ser nag dang //
NK062(khu)001:9838: drag po'i phrin las kyi nang nas zhi ba'i las
NK062(khu)001:9839: mdzad pa'i rtags su bud+d+ha he ru ka'i sku mdog
NK062(khu)001:9840: smug nag / drag po'i phrin las kho na mdzad
NK062(khu)001:9841: pa'i rtags su badz+ra he ru ka'i sku mdog sngo
NK062(khu)001:9842: smug nag / nag / drag po'i phrin las kyi
NK062(khu)001:9843: cha la rgyas pa'i las mdzad pa'i rtags su rat+na
NK062(khu)001:9844: he ru ka'i sku mdog ser nag dang /
NK062(khu)001:9845: dmar nag ljang nag 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK062(khu)001:9847: drag po'i phrin las kyi cha las dbang gi phrin
NK062(khu)001:9848: las mdzad pa'i rtags su pad+ma he ru ka'i sku
NK062(khu)001:9849: mdog dmar nag / drag po'i phrin las kyi cha
NK062(khu)001:9850: las las sna tshogs mdzad pa'i rtags su karma he
NK062(khu)001:9851: ru ka'i sku mdog ljang nag ste /
NK062(khu)001:9852: khro bo de dag thams cad kyang sku che zhing yan lag rags pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:9853: shin tu 'jigs shing rngam pa'i sku dang ldan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9854: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir bgrad //
NK062(khu)001:9856: rnam par thar pa gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags su dbu gsum /
NK062(khu)001:9857: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug /
NK062(khu)001:9858: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags
NK062(khu)001:9859: su zhabs bzhi gyad kyi dor stabs su bgrad pa
NK062(khu)001:9860: / gzhan yang nyi zla bye ba'i 'od zer dus gcig la 'phro ba lta bus brjid pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9861: rngam pa'i sgra chen 'jigs par sgrogs //
NK062(khu)001:9863: gsung rngam pa'i sgra chen gshe zhing myur bar bzhad pas 'jigs pa'i nga ro //
NK062(khu)001:9867: ru lu ru lu la sogs pa'i sgra sna tshogs par sgrogs pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9868: gnyis pa rgyan gyi don bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9871: de yang 'bar ba chen po khro bo'i lha tshogs de dag kyang dur khrod kyi rgyan brgyad dang /
NK062(khu)001:9872: dpal gyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9873: dang po dur khrod kyi rgyan brgyad ni /
NK062(khu)001:9877: dang po bgo ba'i gos gsum ni /
NK062(khu)001:9878: ko rlon gos ni sna tshogs gyon //
NK062(khu)001:9880: ko rlon gyi gos ni sna tshogs pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9881: thabs mkhas phrin las kyi gos zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi /
NK062(khu)001:9882: khyab pa thugs rje'i gos glang chen gyi ko rlon /
NK062(khu)001:9883: phyii nang gsang ba sdud pa'i gos stag lpags kyi sham thabs rnams gyon pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9884: sbrul dang thod phreng nyi zla'i chas //
NK062(khu)001:9889: de la sbrul gyi rgyan chas brgyad ni /
NK062(khu)001:9899: thod pa'i phreng ba'i rgyan ni /
NK062(khu)001:9902: thod rlon gyi ser ral kha'o //
NK062(khu)001:9904: dpral ba'i dbyes su thal chen gyi tshom bu //
NK062(khu)001:9905: smin phrag tu rak+ta'i thig le /
NK062(khu)001:9906: ol ko la zhag gi zo ris so //
NK062(khu)001:9907: de lta bu'i rgyan dang ldan pa'i khro bo rnams
NK062(khu)001:9908: kyi dbu skra ral pa'i gseb nas nyi ma'i dkyil
NK062(khu)001:9909: 'khor 'od zer bye ba dang bcas par 'gyed pa'o
NK062(khu)001:9914: snyan gong g.yas g.yon nyi ma dang zla ba'i dkyil
NK062(khu)001:9915: 'khor 'od zer bye ba 'gyed pa dang bcas pas
NK062(khu)001:9916: brgyan pa'o // de dag ni rgyal byed dpa' rtags kyi rgyan zhes bya ba /
NK062(khu)001:9917: sngon ru dra btul ba'i tshe /
NK062(khu)001:9918: ru dra'i rgyan rnams dpal chen po'i rgyan du mdzad pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9919: dper na dpa' bos dgra bsad nas de'i gos rgyan rang gis gyon pa bzhin no //
NK062(khu)001:9920: gnyis pa dpal gyi chas brgyad ni /
NK062(khu)001:9921: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du bardzesa par 'khor ba ru bzlog pa'i chas //
NK062(khu)001:9922: g.yas g.yon gyi rdo rje khyung gi gshog pa thabs dang shes rab kyi chas //
NK062(khu)001:9923: snyan gong g.yas g.yon gyi dar mthing dmar gyis cod pan rtag chad zil gyis gnon pa'i chas //
NK062(khu)001:9924: spyi bo'i gtsug na rtse lnga yod pa rdo rje lhag pa rig pa'i chas //
NK062(khu)001:9925: dbang gi bse khrab gzi brjid 'bar bgrod pa'i chas //
NK062(khu)001:9926: yum dang gnyis su med par sbyor ba shes rab yum gyi chas //
NK062(khu)001:9927: gnod gdug zlog byed rgya gram lcags kyi chas //
NK062(khu)001:9928: nyon mongs pa sreg par byed pa rdo rje me yi chas //
NK062(khu)001:9930: de rnams dpa' gyi sku la ye nas gnas pas dpal gyi chas brgyad ces bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:9931: de dag ni thugs rig pa rang snang gi rgyan zhes kyang bya ste /
NK062(khu)001:9932: don dang rtags su mi 'gal ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:9933: mdor na dur khrod kyi rgyan brgyad /
NK062(khu)001:9936: rgyan chas bco brgyad dang ldan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9937: gsum pa phyag mtshan gyi don bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:9940: stong gi 'jig rten khor yug bcas //
NK062(khu)001:9942: badz+ra he ru ka'i phyag g.yon gyi tha ma na /
NK062(khu)001:9943: stong gi 'jig rten khor yug dang bcas pa bsnams pa yin la /
NK062(khu)001:9944: rdo rje dung chen gang ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:9946: khrag 'thung rigs lnga char gyi phyag bar pa rnams g.yas rdo rje lnga pa 'dzin pa /
NK062(khu)001:9947: g.yon pa dung chen khrag gis gang ba 'khrug pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:9948: ral gri dgra s+t+wa gshol la sogs //
NK062(khu)001:9950: karma he ru ka'i phyag g.yas kyi dang po na ral gri /
NK062(khu)001:9951: rat+na he ru ka'i phyag g.yon gyi tha ma na dgra s+t+wa /
NK062(khu)001:9952: karma he ru ka'i phyag g.yon gyi tha ma na thong gshol dang /
NK062(khu)001:9953: la sogs pa'i sogs khong nas /
NK062(khu)001:9954: rang gi lag cha sna tshogs bsnams //
NK062(khu)001:9956: rigs lnga rang rang gi lag cha mi mthun pa sna tshogs pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9957: rigs lnga'i phyag g.yas kyi dang po rnams na rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan bsnams pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9958: badz+ra he ru ka'i rdo rje rtse dgu /
NK062(khu)001:9960: rat+na he ru ka'i rin po che /
NK062(khu)001:9963: bung+ng+ha he ru ka'i g.yon gyi tha ma na /
NK062(khu)001:9965: pad+ma he ru ka'i g.yon gyi tha ma na rnga chung sgra dang bcas pa bsnams pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:9968: rang rang gi rigs kyi btsun mo badz+ra kro d+h+ai
NK062(khu)001:9969: shwa r+ai la sogs 'jigs pa'i tshogs rnams rigs kyi
NK062(khu)001:9971: yum gyi phyag g.yas pa shes rab kyi rtags dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK062(khu)001:9972: g.yon pa dung khrag zhal du stob pa /
NK062(khu)001:9973: sku mdog yab dang mthun pa khro mo'i cha lugs can /
NK062(khu)001:9974: gzig gi sham thabs dang ldan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:9975: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya dang //
NK062(khu)001:9977: gnas ma goo r+ai ma brgyad dang /
NK062(khu)001:9978: yul ma seng+ha ma brgyad ni /
NK062(khu)001:9979: rgyu ming 'bras bu la btags pa'am /
NK062(khu)001:9980: gdul bya'i ming 'dul byed la btags pa yin la /
NK062(khu)001:9982: goo r+ai b+han dmar byis dbyug sngo //
NK062(khu)001:9983: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:9984: sid+ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK062(khu)001:9986: sgo bzhi'i phyag rgyas rab mdzes shing //
NK062(khu)001:9989: rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK062(khu)001:9990: zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:9991: de ltar khro mo nyi shu'i 'khor gyis rab tu mdzes shing /
NK062(khu)001:9992: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK062(khu)001:9993: bcu gnyis dang ni brgyad kyis mdzes //
NK062(khu)001:9995: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs ni dbang phyug ma ste /
NK062(khu)001:9996: de yang bcu tshan gnyis dang /
NK062(khu)001:9998: nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis mdzes pa /
NK062(khu)001:9999: mdza' mo'i 'khor rnams rang gi stan dang lag cha dang /
NK062(khu)001:10000: ci bgyi zhes ni chas te gnas //
NK062(khu)001:10002: rang rang gi gdan zhing skam po re dang /
NK062(khu)001:10003: sku mdog dang lag cha ni /
NK062(khu)001:10004: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK062(khu)001:10005: zhes pa la sogs pa dang mthun pa'i cha lugs can rnams /
NK062(khu)001:10006: bdag cag rnams kyis las ci bgyi zhes zer bas ni las la chas te gnas so //
NK062(khu)001:10007: 'di ni sgrub thabs dam pa rgyan dang mthun pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:10009: rdo rje khros pa khrag 'thung mthing //
NK062(khu)001:10011: dkar dmar zhal du nyon mongs 'dren //
NK062(khu)001:10012: rtse dgu rtse lnga ti ra dang //
NK062(khu)001:10014: shes rab 'khyud bas chags pa stob //
NK062(khu)001:10016: dkar ser smug nag gti mug 'dren //
NK062(khu)001:10017: 'khor lo rdo rje ti ra dang //
NK062(khu)001:10018: dril bu mdung dmar tri shul 'chang //
NK062(khu)001:10020: sngo dmar ser nag nga rgyal gsol //
NK062(khu)001:10021: rin cen rdo rje ti ra dang //
NK062(khu)001:10022: dril bu mdung dmar dgra s+t+wa rol //
NK062(khu)001:10024: dkar ser dmar nag brjid pa la //
NK062(khu)001:10025: pad+ma rdo rje ti ra dang //
NK062(khu)001:10026: dril bu mdung dmar rnga chung 'chang //
NK062(khu)001:10027: las rab khrag 'thung yum dang rol //
NK062(khu)001:10028: dkar dmar ljang nag 'bar ba la //
NK062(khu)001:10029: rgya gram rdo rje ti ra dang //
NK062(khu)001:10030: dril bu mdung dmar thong gshol rol //
NK062(khu)001:10032: gzhan yang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK062(khu)001:10033: rdo rje rdo rje dril bu dang //
NK062(khu)001:10035: de bzhin 'khor lo dgra s+t+wa dang //
NK062(khu)001:10037: nor bu rin cen rgyu zhags dang //
NK062(khu)001:10038: rdo rje dgra s+t+wa rab tu sdeb //
NK062(khu)001:10039: chags mchog pad+ma chen po dang //
NK062(khu)001:10040: dril bu rnga'i sgra sgrogs ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:10041: las ni ral gri gshol chen dang //
NK062(khu)001:10043: rigs lnga char gyi bar ma rdo rje dang dung dmar 'khrug /
NK062(khu)001:10044: g.yas tha ma kun ti ra chen po rab sdeb pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10046: de ltar lha'i sku mdog phyag mtshan la nges pa med pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10047: thugs rje la phyogs ris med pas gdul bya la ji ltar mos pa ltar snang ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:10048: 'o na sku mdog dang phyag mtshan la sogs pa
NK062(khu)001:10049: la nges pa med na nyams su ji ltar len
NK062(khu)001:10050: zhe na / rgyud gzhung re re'i dbang du byas
NK062(khu)001:10051: nas nges pa can du nyams su len zhes bla
NK062(khu)001:10052: ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:10053: gnyis pa sku'i dkyil 'khor gyi yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10056: zhes gzhung gi don de dag brjod pas /
NK062(khu)001:10057: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa thams
NK062(khu)001:10058: cad du dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK062(khu)001:10059: cad khro bo khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK062(khu)001:10060: / gdul bya'i ngo la kun tu gsal bar gyur to //
NK062(khu)001:10061: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10064: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK062(khu)001:10066: gsang ba'i zhes rtogs dka' ba /
NK062(khu)001:10068: de kho na nyid gzhan sel ba /
NK062(khu)001:10069: nges pa the tshom dang bral ba /
NK062(khu)001:10070: las zhes pa de mtshan gyi gzhir gda' /
NK062(khu)001:10071: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10073: 'bar ba khro bo'i lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku
NK062(khu)001:10074: dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar bstan pa'i gzhung
NK062(khu)001:10076: tshoms dang ris su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis na le'u ste /
NK062(khu)001:10077: de'i grangs nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las yas bgrangs bcu bdun pa'i don du gada'o //
NK062(khu)001:10078: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK062(khu)001:10079: rgyud kyi 'grel bshad rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i
NK062(khu)001:10080: sgron me yid bzhin gyi nor bu zhes bya ba
NK062(khu)001:10081: las le'u bcu bdun pa'i gzhung don rnam par bshad
NK062(khu)001:10083: da ni le'u bco brgyad pa 'chad par bya ba
NK062(khu)001:10084: 'di la chos tshoms ngos bzung ba'i dbang du byas
NK062(khu)001:10085: na / blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras
NK062(khu)001:10086: bu gsum las gzhi dang 'bras bu zur tsam ston
NK062(khu)001:10088: lam la thabs lam grol lam gnyis las gnyis ka ston /
NK062(khu)001:10089: mtshan nyid gsum las gsum ka ston /
NK062(khu)001:10090: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston /
NK062(khu)001:10091: snang ba bzhi las bzhi ka ston /
NK062(khu)001:10092: blo 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don ston /
NK062(khu)001:10093: de la bcu yod pa las /
NK062(khu)001:10095: bcu yang brgya'i bdag nyid du byas na /
NK062(khu)001:10096: de'i shugs la lta ba dang spyod pa dang ting nge 'dzin ston /
NK062(khu)001:10098: blo tha ma'i tshos tshoms bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu las /
NK062(khu)001:10101: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK062(khu)001:10102: de ltar ston par byed pa'i le'u bco brgyad pa 'di la don gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:10103: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10106: dang po gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10110: gong du lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku gsung thugs
NK062(khu)001:10111: kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa la de le'u bco brgyad
NK062(khu)001:10112: pa 'dir khyad par gyi mchod pa ston pas na
NK062(khu)001:10113: nas / bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos /
NK062(khu)001:10115: mnyes pa'i mchod pa chen po 'di ched du brjod do //
NK062(khu)001:10117: rgyal ba rnams mnyes par byed pa'am gnas su stobs pas na mnyes pa'i mchod pa /
NK062(khu)001:10118: phyi rgyud man chad kyi yul ma yin zhing rmad du byung bas na chen po /
NK062(khu)001:10119: rnam grangs kyi dbang du bzhi po 'di dag /
NK062(khu)001:10120: 'khor rnams kyi ched du brjod do //
NK062(khu)001:10121: gnyis pa le'u'i gzhung bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:10125: dang po mchod pa dngos la bzhi ste /
NK062(khu)001:10126: zhe sdang sgrol ba'i mchod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10127: 'dod chags sbyor ba'i mchod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10128: gti mug rdzas kyi mchod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10130: dang po zhe sdang sgrol ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10133: de la zhes pas sngar bstan pa'i lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor de la /
NK062(khu)001:10136: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mchod cing ma mo dang
NK062(khu)001:10137: mkha' 'gro la sbyin pa'i dug gsum gyi mchod pas
NK062(khu)001:10138: bsgral bya'i sems can gyi skyabs chen po thob pa'i
NK062(khu)001:10139: phyir / mchod sbyin gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas na dam pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10140: de ni tshul ji lta bu zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:10141: 'chad bzhin pa'i sbyor sgrol gnyis ka la /
NK062(khu)001:10143: dbang po yul dus kyi sbyor sgrol /
NK062(khu)001:10145: mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor sgrol /
NK062(khu)001:10146: thabs chen po'i sbyor sgrol dang lnga lngas ston te /
NK062(khu)001:10147: thog mar sgrol ba'i tshul lnga las /
NK062(khu)001:10148: 'dir tha ma gnyis gtso bor bzung ste /
NK062(khu)001:10149: de yang sgrol ba'i mchod pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK062(khu)001:10150: thog mar rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:10151: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK062(khu)001:10153: gzhan sgrol ba'i thog mar rnal 'byor ba bdag nyid kyis rtogs pa bzhi dang /
NK062(khu)001:10155: mnyam pa gnyis kyi gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas /
NK062(khu)001:10156: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba rtogs shing nyams su lon pa /
NK062(khu)001:10157: cho ga lnga'i sgo nas ting nge 'dzin bsgoms shing
NK062(khu)001:10158: stobs su byas nas gzung 'dzin gyi rnam rtog chos
NK062(khu)001:10159: nyid kyi klong du bsgral lo //
NK062(khu)001:10160: thugs rjes gzhan bsgral ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:10162: sngon du lta sgom stobs su byas pas bdag bsgral
NK062(khu)001:10163: ba la de thugs rjes gzhan sgrol ba ston pas
NK062(khu)001:10164: na nas / gnyis med blo yis ni /
NK062(khu)001:10166: sems nyid kyi gshis la bsgral bya sgrol byed gnyis su med par rtogs pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:10167: bdag gzhan gnyis su med par shes pa yis lta
NK062(khu)001:10168: sgom blo gdengs dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa de
NK062(khu)001:10169: yis ni / blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK062(khu)001:10171: zhing bcu dag gi las rgyu 'bras mi shes pa'i phyir blo ngan pa kho na ste /
NK062(khu)001:10172: de dag las kyi dbang gis yun du 'jig rten du 'khor ba'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:10173: bsgral ba'i zhing bcur gyur pa de dag la bsgral
NK062(khu)001:10174: na snying re rje bas snying rjes zin bar bya
NK062(khu)001:10175: ba'i zhing dag / thugs rjes gzung ba'i don du bsgral bar bya ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:10177: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:10179: bsgral bya de nyid le'u bcu gcig pa nas bshad pa'i thabs dang ldan pas bsgral te /
NK062(khu)001:10180: bsgral bya'i shes pa rdo rje sems dpar bskyed pa de 'og min du 'phangs nas /
NK062(khu)001:10181: rdo rje 'dzin pa yab yum thabs shes rab gnyis
NK062(khu)001:10182: su med pa'i byang chub sems kyis dbang bskur nas
NK062(khu)001:10183: / rgyal ba'i sras su rigs nges par byas pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10184: chos kyi dbyings su bsgral bar bya ba'i thabs dam pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10185: sgrol ba'i thabs 'di dag gi tshul rgyas par le'u
NK062(khu)001:10186: bcu gcig par bshad zin pas 'dir ma spros so
NK062(khu)001:10187: // gnyis pa 'dod chags sbyor ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10190: de yang gong du sgrol ba'i skabs su bshad pa ltar /
NK062(khu)001:10191: 'dir sbyor ba'i tshul la yang lnga las /
NK062(khu)001:10193: de yang thabs lam steng sgo las su rung zhing log pa'i chags yid spangs pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK062(khu)001:10194: pad+ma can la sogs pa'i gzungs ma mtshan nyid dang
NK062(khu)001:10195: ldan pa yongs su sbyangs pa dang gnyis pos mkha'
NK062(khu)001:10197: sbyor ba'i brda bsnol mar bskul nas /
NK062(khu)001:10198: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK062(khu)001:10200: thabs shes rab phan tshun 'khril ba'i tshul gyis bsrub
NK062(khu)001:10201: pa dang bsrubs pa'i sbyor bas bde ba nyams su
NK062(khu)001:10203: bdag gi don dang gzhan gyi don dang gnyis ka'i
NK062(khu)001:10204: don dang chos kyi don te don bzhi 'grub par
NK062(khu)001:10206: yab yum gnyis kyi byang sems dkar dmar dus mnyam du sbyor bas /
NK062(khu)001:10207: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:10209: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kun gyi bdag nyid rnal
NK062(khu)001:10210: 'byor pa yab yum yi dam gyi lhar gsal ba
NK062(khu)001:10211: bde ba chen pos mnyes pas rgyal ba thams cad
NK062(khu)001:10212: kyang mchod pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:10213: gsum pa gti mug dam rdzas kyi mchod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10218: rang bzhin gyi mnyam pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10219: spyad pa las kyi mnyam pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10220: dang po rang bzhin gyi mnyam pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10221: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga dang /
NK062(khu)001:10223: shes bya'i gshis kyi steng na snang na snang mnyam /
NK062(khu)001:10225: rang bzhin bzang ngan tha dad med par mnyam pa ni rang bzhin gyi mnyam pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10226: gnyis pa spyad pa las kyi mnyam pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10228: sems can rtog pa bzlog phyir sman //
NK062(khu)001:10229: gtso ru dang du blang bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:10231: gtsang rme'i rtog pa bzlos nas mnyam pa nyid du
NK062(khu)001:10232: longs spyod pa ni spyad pa las kyi mnyam pa'o
NK062(khu)001:10235: de ltar mnyam pa gnyis dang ldan pa'i dam rdzas
NK062(khu)001:10236: grub pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rdzas chen po bdud
NK062(khu)001:10237: rtsi lnga po 'di dag grub tshul ni bzhi ste
NK062(khu)001:10238: / chos nyid rang bzhin gyis grub pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10239: chos can rang gi ngo bos grub pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10241: byin gyi rlabs kyis grub pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10242: dang po chos nyid rang bzhin gyis grub pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10244: dngos po ma lus sems nyid phyir //
NK062(khu)001:10245: mtshan nyid bral ba chos kyi dbyings //
NK062(khu)001:10247: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga'i rang bzhin sems nyid las
NK062(khu)001:10248: mi gzhan pa'i phyir sems nyid stong zhing spros pa
NK062(khu)001:10249: thams cad dang bral ba chos kyi dbyings su /
NK062(khu)001:10250: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin las ma g.yos par chos
NK062(khu)001:10251: kyi dbyings su grub pa ni chos nyid rang bzhin
NK062(khu)001:10252: gyis grub pa'o // gnyis pa chos can rang gi ngo bos grub pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10253: rang bzhin bde ba'i ye shes lnga //
NK062(khu)001:10254: byed pa med par rang snang ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:10256: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga po de byed pa pos
NK062(khu)001:10257: ma byas bar ye shes lnga'i ngo bor rang snang
NK062(khu)001:10258: ba ni chos can rang gi ngo bos grub pa'o
NK062(khu)001:10259: // gsum pa mthus grub pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10260: shes rab ting 'dzin thabs dag gi //
NK062(khu)001:10261: nus mthu nges par 'byung ba yin //
NK062(khu)001:10263: rtogs pa'i lta ba dang bsgoms pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pas /
NK062(khu)001:10264: dam rdzas lnga la longs spyod pa'i thabs kyis spyad
NK062(khu)001:10265: pas mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus
NK062(khu)001:10266: pa 'grub pa ni mthus grub pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10267: bzhi pa byin gyis brlabs kyis grub pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10268: 'di lta'i lam la gang gnas pa //
NK062(khu)001:10269: phyogs dus kun nas byin gyis rlob //
NK062(khu)001:10271: dam rdzas lnga la longs spyod pa'i rnal 'byor pa de la /
NK062(khu)001:10272: phyogs bcu na dus gsum du bzhugs pa'i bde bar gshegs pa sras dang /
NK062(khu)001:10277: mkha' 'gros ming por dgongs nas byin gyis rlob pa ni byin gyis brlabs kyis grub pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10278: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la dbul //
NK062(khu)001:10280: 'bul byed kyi mkhan po rnal 'byor pa bdag dang /
NK062(khu)001:10281: dbul bya'i yul bde bar gshegs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10282: dbul bya'i rdzas gsum po rang rig pa'i steng nas
NK062(khu)001:10283: tha dad med par mnyam pa'i phyir de ni tshogs
NK062(khu)001:10285: mchod pa de dag la 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i mchod pa zhes kyang bya la /
NK062(khu)001:10286: de gnas su stobs bas na dbul ba zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:10287: de yang 'khor gsum yongs dag ni /
NK062(khu)001:10288: phyi khang zhing nang nor rdzas bran khol la sogs pa la chags shing zhen pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10289: nang rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad yul gyi rjes su 'jug shing zhen pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10290: gsang ba lta sgom spyod gsum la mchog tu 'dzin
NK062(khu)001:10291: pa'i zhen pa las grol nas ye shes chen po
NK062(khu)001:10292: 'byed pa med pa'i ngang du gnas par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:10293: bzhi pa 'dod yon rgyan gyi mchod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10296: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo /
NK062(khu)001:10298: bza' ba dang bca' ba dang btung ba ste ro bro ba'i mchog tu gyur pa rnams dang /
NK062(khu)001:10299: bgo ba ni reg bya'i bye brag rnams te /
NK062(khu)001:10300: 'jam zhing yang la bde ba rnams dang /
NK062(khu)001:10301: de la sogs pa'i gzugs sdug pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10303: dri zhim po'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:10304: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK062(khu)001:10306: de ltar 'dod pa'i longs spyod lnga po rnams ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK062(khu)001:10307: thams cad 'dod yon gyi lha mor byin gyis brlabs pa rnams ni /
NK062(khu)001:10310: bdag dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa gnyis su
NK062(khu)001:10311: med par gsal ba lha'i dkyil 'khor de la ni
NK062(khu)001:10312: / mchod pa'i lha mor byin gyis brlabs pa'i 'dod
NK062(khu)001:10313: yon gyi dkyil 'khor de nyid dper na chu la
NK062(khu)001:10314: chu thim pa'i tshul du gnyis su med par thim
NK062(khu)001:10316: gnyis pa mchod pa'i 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:10319: dang po thun mong gi 'bras bu ni /
NK062(khu)001:10322: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi /
NK062(khu)001:10323: bde gshegs yon tan rmad po che //
NK062(khu)001:10325: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhir bdag don du yang dag pa'i sa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10326: gzhan don du sems can gyi don la gshegs pa'i
NK062(khu)001:10327: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK062(khu)001:10328: yon tan phrin las theg pa gzhan gyi 'bras bu
NK062(khu)001:10329: las khyad du gyur pa'i rmad po che de nyid
NK062(khu)001:10330: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te /
NK062(khu)001:10331: lha srin la sogs smos ci dgos //
NK062(khu)001:10333: rang sems sgrib pa dang bral ba las gzhan nas
NK062(khu)001:10334: btsal du yod pa zhig bkug pa'am gzhan nas 'ong
NK062(khu)001:10336: lha dang srin po la sogs pa'i mthu las byung
NK062(khu)001:10337: ba ni smos ci dgos te 'dir sems nyid las
NK062(khu)001:10338: su rung ba'i yon tan las de rnams /
NK062(khu)001:10339: thams cad zil gyis gnon no //
NK062(khu)001:10340: gnyis pa mchog gi 'bras bu ni /
NK062(khu)001:10343: rnal 'byor las su rung rnams kyis //
NK062(khu)001:10344: phyag rgya chen po rdzogs 'gyur zhing //
NK062(khu)001:10346: rnal 'byor pa ting 'dzin las su rung ba rnams
NK062(khu)001:10347: kyis yi dam lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po rang
NK062(khu)001:10348: rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal bar rdzogs par 'gyur
NK062(khu)001:10349: zhing / gsal la yid gnyis med pas na //
NK062(khu)001:10352: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal ba'i tshad yul
NK062(khu)001:10353: gyis mi 'phrogs pa la brtan pa thob nas yid
NK062(khu)001:10354: gnyis dang the tshom med pas bsgrubs par byas na
NK062(khu)001:10355: / rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK062(khu)001:10356: dngos grub chen po 'bar ba 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK062(khu)001:10357: / // gsum pa mchod pa'i yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10362: zhes mchod pa 'bras bu dang bcas pa'i don de dag brjod pas /
NK062(khu)001:10363: mnyes pa'i mchod pa chen pos /
NK062(khu)001:10364: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad khyab par gyur to //
NK062(khu)001:10366: gnas su stob cing mnyes par byed pa'i mchod pa /
NK062(khu)001:10367: bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis 'grub pas na chen po 'dis ni /
NK062(khu)001:10368: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad du mchod pa'i sprin gyis khyab par gyur to //
NK062(khu)001:10369: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10372: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:10373: gsang ba'i zhes rtogs dka' ba /
NK062(khu)001:10375: de kho na nyid gzhan sel ba /
NK062(khu)001:10376: nges pa the tshom dang bral ba /
NK062(khu)001:10377: las zhes pa mtshan gyi gzhir gda' /
NK062(khu)001:10378: mchod sbyin dam pa bstan pa'i le'u ste bco brgyad pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10380: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud man chad kyi mchod sbyin las khyad par du gyur pas na dam pa /
NK062(khu)001:10381: dug gsum gyi mchod pa bstan pa'i gzhung gi tshig
NK062(khu)001:10382: don rnams tshoms dang ris su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin
NK062(khu)001:10383: par byed pa'i don gyis na le'u'i ste de'i grangs
NK062(khu)001:10384: nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK062(khu)001:10385: yas bgrangs bco brgyad pa'i don du gada'o //
NK062(khu)001:10386: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK062(khu)001:10387: rgyud kyi 'grel bshad rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i
NK062(khu)001:10388: sgron me yid bzhin gyi nor bu zhes bya ba
NK062(khu)001:10389: las le'u bco brgyad pa'i gzhung don rnam par bshad
NK062(khu)001:10391: da ni le'u bcu dgu pa 'chad par byed pa 'di la /
NK062(khu)001:10392: chos tshoms ngos zung ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK062(khu)001:10393: blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las gsum ka ston /
NK062(khu)001:10394: lam la thabs lam grol lam gnyis las gnyis ka ston /
NK062(khu)001:10395: mtshan nyid gsum las gsum ka ston /
NK062(khu)001:10396: rim gcig car gnyis las gnyis ka ston /
NK062(khu)001:10397: snang ba bzhi las bzhi ka ston cing /
NK062(khu)001:10399: blo 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don ston /
NK062(khu)001:10400: de la dngos po bcu yod pa las dam tshig ston /
NK062(khu)001:10401: de'i zhor la lta ba dang spyod pa ston /
NK062(khu)001:10402: blo tha ma'i chos tshoms bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu las /
NK062(khu)001:10406: gtar kha gegs sel rnams ston cing /
NK062(khu)001:10407: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK062(khu)001:10408: de ltar ston par byed pa 'i le'u bcu dgu pa 'di la don gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:10409: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10412: dang po gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10416: le'u bco brgyad par khyad par gyi mchod pa bstan
NK062(khu)001:10417: pa la de le'u bcu dgu pa 'dir dam tshig
NK062(khu)001:10418: bsrung mtshams ston pas na nas /
NK062(khu)001:10419: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos /
NK062(khu)001:10422: sngags 'chang rnams don yod par bya ba'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:10423: dam tshig chen po 'di chen du brjod do //
NK062(khu)001:10425: gsang sngags 'chang ba'i rnal 'byor pa rnams lam la
NK062(khu)001:10426: 'bad cing bsgrubs pa don yod par bya ba'i phyir
NK062(khu)001:10427: / gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i bsrung ba'i dam
NK062(khu)001:10428: tshig gzhan theg pa 'og ma'i 'dul sdom la sogs
NK062(khu)001:10429: pa las khyad par du gyur pas na chen po
NK062(khu)001:10430: 'og nas 'byung ba 'di dag 'khor gyi ched du
NK062(khu)001:10431: / brjod do // gnyis pa le'u'i gzhung bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:10433: gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK062(khu)001:10434: dang po gzhung dngos la bdun te /
NK062(khu)001:10435: dam tshig gi che ba 'dus pa rnam par dag pa bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10436: dam tshig gi rnam grangs mdor bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10437: mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig skyon yon dang bcas pa bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10438: dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10439: dam tshig gi rang bzhin bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10440: dam tshig gi rnam grangs rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10441: dam tshig gi yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10442: dang po dam tshig gi che ba 'dus pa rnam par dag pa bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:10445: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10446: bla med theg par rnam par dag /
NK062(khu)001:10448: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK062(khu)001:10450: lam dang 'bras bu gnyis ka theg pa 'di'i gong
NK062(khu)001:10451: na gzhan med pa'i phyir bla na med pa gsang
NK062(khu)001:10452: sngags rdo rje'i theg par rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga
NK062(khu)001:10453: dang yan lag gi dam tshig bcu ste /
NK062(khu)001:10454: dam tshig bco lnga nyams su lon cing don rab tu nges pa ste rtogs na /
NK062(khu)001:10455: nyon mongs las rnams kun spyod kyang //
NK062(khu)001:10457: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug nga rgyal phrag dog
NK062(khu)001:10458: ste nyon mongs pa dug lnga'i las mi dge ba
NK062(khu)001:10459: bcu dang / mtshams med pa lnga dang /
NK062(khu)001:10460: de dang nye ba lnga dang /
NK062(khu)001:10462: log pa brgyad la sogs pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10463: de la mi dge ba bcu ni /
NK062(khu)001:10464: lus kyi sgo nas srog gcod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10465: ma byin pa len pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10466: 'dod pa la log par g.yem pa dang gsum las /
NK062(khu)001:10469: srog gcod pa ni bsam bzhin du //
NK062(khu)001:10470: ma nor ba ni gzhan bsad pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10472: ma byin len pa gzhan gyi nor //
NK062(khu)001:10473: mthu dang 'jab bus bdag gir byed //
NK062(khu)001:10474: 'dod pa la log par g.yem pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10476: log par g.yem pa rnam pa bzhi //
NK062(khu)001:10482: rdzun tshig 'du shes gzhan bsgyur ba'i //
NK062(khu)001:10483: tshig don mngon par go ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:10485: phra ma pha rol dbye ba yi //
NK062(khu)001:10486: nyon mongs can gyi sems kyi tshig /
NK062(khu)001:10488: tshig rtsub po ni mi snyan pa //
NK062(khu)001:10489: nyon mongs can kun kyal pa nyid //
NK062(khu)001:10491: gzhan ni de las gzhan nyon mongs //
NK062(khu)001:10492: kha gsag glu dang zlos gar bzhin //
NK062(khu)001:10493: yid kyi sgo nas brnab sems /
NK062(khu)001:10497: bstan bcos ngan zhing brnab sems ni //
NK062(khu)001:10498: log pas gzhan gyi nor la chags //
NK062(khu)001:10500: gnod sems sems can la sdang ba //
NK062(khu)001:10502: dge dang mi dge med lta ba //
NK062(khu)001:10503: log par lta ba yin 'di la //
NK062(khu)001:10506: dpung bzang gis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK062(khu)001:10507: gang zhig dgra bcom pha ma gsod pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:10508: mthun pa'i dge 'dun dbyen ni byed pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10509: de bzhin gshegs la sdang ba'i sems kyi su //
NK062(khu)001:10510: gang zhig mi dag sku mtshal 'byin byed pa //
NK062(khu)001:10511: shin tu mi bzad sdig pa'i las 'di rnams //
NK062(khu)001:10512: rgyal bas mtshams med lnga po yin par bshad //
NK062(khu)001:10513: gti mug can gyi sdig pa gcig byas na //
NK062(khu)001:10514: phung po 'di la grub pa thob mi 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:10516: de dang nye ba lnga ni /
NK062(khu)001:10518: mchod rten 'jig cing byang chub sems dpa' gsod //
NK062(khu)001:10519: nyon mongs zad pa'i ma ni sun 'byin dang //
NK062(khu)001:10520: slob pa gsod cing dge 'dun mnga' ba la //
NK062(khu)001:10521: gang zhig 'dod pas mang nyung rku 'phrog pa //
NK062(khu)001:10522: mtshams med nye lngar de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:10523: tshul bsdams mi ni gang zhig 'di byed pa //
NK062(khu)001:10524: bskal ba'i bar du mnar med sdug bsngal myong //
NK062(khu)001:10530: sngags pa dam tshig can gyi nor lci /
NK062(khu)001:10531: zhes gong ma rnams gsungs ngo //
NK062(khu)001:10533: dkar nag phyogs la smad dang bstod //
NK062(khu)001:10534: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs dang //
NK062(khu)001:10535: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag dang //
NK062(khu)001:10536: bla ma lha dang mched lcam spangs //
NK062(khu)001:10537: dkyil 'khor gnyan po dral dang brgyad //
NK062(khu)001:10538: 'di dag log pa brgyad du gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:10540: de ltar nyon mongs pa lnga'i lam ngan pa rnams ma lus pa kun dang /
NK062(khu)001:10541: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga po kun la spyod pa ltar snang yang /
NK062(khu)001:10542: byas la mi rtsogs tshogs 'gyur te //
NK062(khu)001:10544: bsam pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK062(khu)001:10545: thabs khyad par can gyi gnad dang /
NK062(khu)001:10546: rtogs pa lta ba'i gdengs gsum gyis zin pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:10547: las ngan pa byas pa la 'bras bu ngan song
NK062(khu)001:10548: gsum gyi sdug bsngal mi rtsogs pa ste mi gsog
NK062(khu)001:10550: de rnams lam 'gag par spyad par byas pas bsod
NK062(khu)001:10551: nams kyi tshogs dang de la bdag tu 'dzin pas
NK062(khu)001:10552: ye shes kyi tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs par 'gyur
NK062(khu)001:10553: te / tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK062(khu)001:10555: nyan thos kyi tshul khrims dang /
NK062(khu)001:10556: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10557: sngags phyi rgyud kyi dam tshig rnams ched du ma bsrungs kyang /
NK062(khu)001:10558: 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin yon tan yar ldan du
NK062(khu)001:10559: rdzogs pas na phun sum tshogs pa'i sdom pa zhes
NK062(khu)001:10560: bya'o // bla med mchog gi dam tshig tu //
NK062(khu)001:10562: de'i phyir lam dang 'bras bu gong na med pa
NK062(khu)001:10563: gsang sngags bla med mchog gi dam tshig 'di dag
NK062(khu)001:10564: tu / 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshul khrims dang //
NK062(khu)001:10566: gdul bya 'dul ba'i dbang gis so sor thar ba
NK062(khu)001:10567: nyan thos kyi tshul khrims rtsa ba bzhi yan lag
NK062(khu)001:10568: dang bcas pa'i bsrung bya kun dang /
NK062(khu)001:10569: sdom pa ji snyed bsam yas pa //
NK062(khu)001:10572: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa ji snyed pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10573: sngags phyi rgyud pa'i bsrung sdom bsam yas pa /
NK062(khu)001:10574: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK062(khu)001:10576: lhag ma ma lus pa kun gyi yon tan thams
NK062(khu)001:10577: cad kyang bla na med pa gsang sngags ma h+aa
NK062(khu)001:10578: yo ga'i theg pa 'dir 'dus shing rnam par dag
NK062(khu)001:10579: pa ste / de yang theg pa 'og ma pa'i
NK062(khu)001:10580: 'dul sdom thams cad kyang mdor bsdu na gsum du
NK062(khu)001:10581: pa ste / 'dus te / gang zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:10582: nyes spyod mi dge ba spong ba sdom pa'i tshul khrims dang /
NK062(khu)001:10583: legs spyod gnyen po dge ba'i tshogs sgrub pa dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims dang /
NK062(khu)001:10584: rang brtan pa thob nas dngos sam brgyud pa'i sgo
NK062(khu)001:10585: nas sems can la phan pa sgrub pa sems can
NK062(khu)001:10586: don byed kyi tshul khrims so //
NK062(khu)001:10588: skabs 'dir gsang sngags kyi dam tshig chen po dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK062(khu)001:10589: las dang nyon mongs pa lnga la sogs pa spyod
NK062(khu)001:10590: pa ltar snang yang 'dzin pa med pas ltung bar
NK062(khu)001:10591: mi 'gyur ba ni mi dge sdom pa'i tshul khrims
NK062(khu)001:10592: / gang ltar spyod kyang sgo gsum lha'i sku phyag
NK062(khu)001:10593: rgya chen po las mi 'da' ba ni dge ba
NK062(khu)001:10595: gzhan don du 'gyur na srog gcod pa la sogs
NK062(khu)001:10596: pa'i tshul mi 'dor ba ni sems can don byed
NK062(khu)001:10598: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK062(khu)001:10599: srog gcod pa la srog gcod pa spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag dang /
NK062(khu)001:10600: ma byin par len pa la ma byin par len
NK062(khu)001:10601: pa spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag dang
NK062(khu)001:10602: / rdzun du smra ba la rdzun du smra ba spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag dang /
NK062(khu)001:10603: mi tshangs par spyod pa la mi tshangs par spyod
NK062(khu)001:10604: pa spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag go
NK062(khu)001:10605: // dang po srog gcod pa la srog gcod pa spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag ni /
NK062(khu)001:10606: yod med dbu ma log rtog tsam //
NK062(khu)001:10608: yod med dbu ma mi dmigs shing //
NK062(khu)001:10610: bdag gzhan gnyis ka sems nyid kyi ngang du gsal ba'i dus na yod pa ste snang ba /
NK062(khu)001:10612: dbu ma ste gnyis med kyi mtha' gang du yang
NK062(khu)001:10613: mi dmigs shing blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa ni
NK062(khu)001:10615: 'o na bdag dang gzhan du snang ba 'di ci zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:10616: sgyu ma mig yor lta bu'i tshul //
NK062(khu)001:10618: kun rdzob tu rgyu rkyen 'dus pa log rtog gi ngo bo tsam du snang yang /
NK062(khu)001:10619: bden dngos kyis stong pa dper na sgyu ma'am mig
NK062(khu)001:10620: shes 'khrul pas tho yor la mir 'dzin pa lta
NK062(khu)001:10622: srog med srog kyang gcad du med //
NK062(khu)001:10624: srog gcod bya gcod byed gnyis ka nas dag pa'i
NK062(khu)001:10625: phyir gcad bya'i srog dmigs su med pas srog gcod
NK062(khu)001:10627: gcod do ba'i 'du shes kyang dmigs su med pas na /
NK062(khu)001:10628: don dam par srog gcad du med kyang /
NK062(khu)001:10629: srog dang skyes bu log rtog tsam //
NK062(khu)001:10631: 'o na srog dang sems can du snang ba 'di ci zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:10632: kun rdzob tu gcad bya'i srog dang gcod byed kyi skyes bur snang ba 'di ni /
NK062(khu)001:10633: log rtog rten 'brel gyi snang ba tsam du rtogs shing /
NK062(khu)001:10634: de ltar bden pa gnyis kyang de nyid dang gzhan nyid du brjod du med par rtogs nas /
NK062(khu)001:10635: thugs rjes zhing bcu'i srog bcad kyang bdag la sgrib
NK062(khu)001:10636: pa mi gsog cing gzhan la sdug bsngal mi bskyed
NK062(khu)001:10637: pas na / de la theg pa 'og ma pas
NK062(khu)001:10638: srog gcod pa spangs pa'i yon tan zhor la rdzogs
NK062(khu)001:10639: pas na / pa'o // gnyis pa ma byin par
NK062(khu)001:10640: len pa la ma byin par len pa spong ba
NK062(khu)001:10641: yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag ni /
NK062(khu)001:10642: bden pa gnyis ka nyid kyi dbyings //
NK062(khu)001:10644: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med pas //
NK062(khu)001:10646: don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyi bden pa gnyis ka sems nyid kyi ngo bor dbyer med pas /
NK062(khu)001:10647: bdag dang gzhan du mi dmigs shing //
NK062(khu)001:10648: 'phrul dag'i tshul te tha dad min //
NK062(khu)001:10650: dper na lha 'phrul dag'i longs spyod rang las sprul nas rang gis spyod pa'i tshul te /
NK062(khu)001:10651: blang bya'i rdzas dang len byed kyi mkhan po dang
NK062(khu)001:10652: len pa po'i 'du shes gsum ka bdag las mi
NK062(khu)001:10653: gzhan pa'i phyir / sems nyid kyi ngo bor tha dad min pas /
NK062(khu)001:10654: gzhan dang ma byin med pa'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:10656: blang bya rdzas dang gzhan bdag po dang ma byin
NK062(khu)001:10657: par len pa po bdag rnams dmigs su med pa'i
NK062(khu)001:10658: phyir / kun rdzob tu ma byin par len pa ltar snang yang /
NK062(khu)001:10659: blang med thams cad nyid kyi dbyings //
NK062(khu)001:10661: don dam par blang bya blang byed med de /
NK062(khu)001:10662: thams cad bdag nyid chen po mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings las ma 'das par rtogs nas /
NK062(khu)001:10663: gzhan don bsgrub pa'i phyir ma byin par len pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10664: theg pa 'og ma pas ma byin par len pa spong ba'i yon tan zhor la rdzogs pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10665: gsum pa rdzun du smra ba la rdzun du smra
NK062(khu)001:10666: ba spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag ni
NK062(khu)001:10667: / chos rnams sgyu ma yod ma yin //
NK062(khu)001:10669: chos rnams sgyu ma lta bu dang //
NK062(khu)001:10671: phyi nang gi dngos pos bsdus pa'i chos rnams snang
NK062(khu)001:10672: yang bden dngos kyis stong pa sgyu ma lta bu
NK062(khu)001:10673: la bdag tu lta ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:10674: ngo bo nyid med bzhin du btags pas /
NK062(khu)001:10675: ngo bo nyid kyi rdzun dang /
NK062(khu)001:10676: ming dang tshig tu btags pa rdzun //
NK062(khu)001:10678: dngos po med bzhin zhe na pas ming dang tshig tu btags pa 'di la /
NK062(khu)001:10679: ming tshig gi rjes su spyod cing bden par 'dzin
NK062(khu)001:10680: pas mngon par zhen pas rjes su spyod pa'i rdzun
NK062(khu)001:10681: no // de dag las kyang 'gal bar smra ba ni log pa'i rdzun no //
NK062(khu)001:10682: rdzun nyid la ni rdzun spyod pas //
NK062(khu)001:10684: de ltar rdzun gsum po re re nyid la ni
NK062(khu)001:10685: bden pa'i gzhi ma grub pa'i phyir na rdzun spyod
NK062(khu)001:10686: pa ste / rdzun zhes btags tsam yod ma yin //
NK062(khu)001:10688: des na rdzun zhes btags pa tsam las don dam
NK062(khu)001:10689: par na bden par grub cing dmigs su yod pa
NK062(khu)001:10690: ma yin no // de ltar rtogs nas bdag gzhan
NK062(khu)001:10691: chos gsum gyi don du rdzun du smras pa ni
NK062(khu)001:10692: ma yin no // / theg pa 'og ma pas
NK062(khu)001:10693: rdzun du smra ba spangs pa'i yon tan zhor la
NK062(khu)001:10694: ma yin no // / rdzogs pa'o // bzhi pa
NK062(khu)001:10695: mi tshangs par spyod pa la mi tshangs par spyod
NK062(khu)001:10696: pa spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag ni
NK062(khu)001:10697: ma yin no // / rdzogs pa'o // / ma chags pa la chen po yin //
NK062(khu)001:10699: ma chags pa la chags pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:10701: dngos po thams cad sems nyid du rang snang bas
NK062(khu)001:10702: yul sems gnyis med du gsal ba ni ma chags
NK062(khu)001:10704: de la pho mo gnyis su zhen cing chags pa ni log pa'i 'dod chags so //
NK062(khu)001:10705: de ltar log pa'i 'dod chags rang kha ma dang tshul mthun par spyod kyang /
NK062(khu)001:10706: de dag sems nyid du shes pa'i lta ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:10707: 'du shes gsum ldan gyi sgom pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10708: thabs kyis zin pa'i spyod pa dang gsum ldan gyi sgo nas /
NK062(khu)001:10709: chags pa nyid na chags med pa //
NK062(khu)001:10711: chags pa ma 'gags par spyod pa'i dus nyid na chags pa'i ngo nyid ye shes su gsal bas /
NK062(khu)001:10712: chags pa tha mal pa'i nyes skyon gyi dri mas gos pa med pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10713: de ni tshangs mchog rgyal po ste //
NK062(khu)001:10715: de ltar chags pa'i nyes skyon gyis ma gos pa
NK062(khu)001:10716: de ni tshangs par spyod pa'i mchog bde ba'i ye
NK062(khu)001:10717: shes la dbang sgyur ba'i rgyal po yin te /
NK062(khu)001:10718: shin tu chags pa chen po yin //
NK062(khu)001:10720: de ni shin tu yang dag pa'i chags pa chen po spangs gnyen ro gcig tu gyur pa /
NK062(khu)001:10721: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid yin no //
NK062(khu)001:10722: de ltar shes nas 'dzag med kyi ye shes bsgrub pa'i don du chags pa spyad pas /
NK062(khu)001:10723: theg pa 'og ma pas mi tshangs par spyod pa spangs pa'i yon tan zhor la rdzogs pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10725: bla ma gong ma 'ga' zhig gi bzhed kyis /
NK062(khu)001:10726: srog gcod pa la srog gcod pa spong ba rdzogs pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10727: don dam pa la srog gcad bya gcod byed gnyis med du rtogs /
NK062(khu)001:10728: kun rdzob rang rig ye shes sgyu mar rtogs /
NK062(khu)001:10729: de dag kyang bden pa dbyer med du rtogs pa'i
NK062(khu)001:10730: rnal 'byor pas srog gcad kyang bdag la sgrib pa
NK062(khu)001:10731: mi gsog / gzhan la sdug bsngal mi skyed /
NK062(khu)001:10732: yang na sgrol ba'i tshad rab thams cad mkhyen pa'i go shar ba /
NK062(khu)001:10733: 'bring yi dam lha'i zhal mthong ba /
NK062(khu)001:10734: tha ma gong ltar rtogs dgos pa yin zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:10736: rab gong gi lta ba rtogs pa /
NK062(khu)001:10737: 'bring bsgral ba de gnas spor nus pa /
NK062(khu)001:10738: tha ma rang gi snying la mtshon btsugs kyang mi
NK062(khu)001:10739: dga' ba med pa zhig gis srog gcod pa'i sdom
NK062(khu)001:10740: pa blang ngo // de la theg pa 'og ma pa'i srog gcod spangs pa'i yon tan rdzogs so //
NK062(khu)001:10741: ma byin par len pa spong ba rdzogs pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10742: rab bdag gzhan dbyer med rtogs pa'i lta ba dang ldan pa /
NK062(khu)001:10743: 'bring bslangs pa'i yo byad gnas su stob pa /
NK062(khu)001:10744: tha ma rang gi yo byad thams cad gzhan gyis
NK062(khu)001:10745: khyer yang sems la mi dga' ba med pa zhig
NK062(khu)001:10746: gis ma byin bar len pa'i sdom pa blang ngo
NK062(khu)001:10747: // de la theg pa 'og ma pa'i ma byin par len pa spong ba'i yon tan rdzogs pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10748: rdzun du smra ba spong ba rdzogs pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10749: rab chos thams cad sgyu ma'am rdzun gyi snang ba tsam du shes pa /
NK062(khu)001:10750: 'bring rdzun gyi sgo nas blo phyin ci log tu
NK062(khu)001:10751: zhen pa'i gdul bya yang dag pa'i lam la 'dren
NK062(khu)001:10752: nus pa / tha mar rang la gzhan gyis ngan ci smras kyang /
NK062(khu)001:10753: mi dga' ba med pa cig gis rdzun smra ba'i sdom pa blang ngo //
NK062(khu)001:10754: de la theg pa 'og ma pas rdzun spangs pa'i yon tan rdzogs so //
NK062(khu)001:10755: mi tshangs par spyod pa spong ba rdzogs pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10756: rab tshangs mchog rgyal por rtogs pa /
NK062(khu)001:10757: 'bring thig le dbab pa dang bzung ba dang bzlog
NK062(khu)001:10758: pa gsum gyi thabs dang ldan pas bde stong gnyis
NK062(khu)001:10760: tha ma rang gi gzungs ma la gzhan gyis rang
NK062(khu)001:10761: gi mngon du spyad kyang mi dga' ba med pa
NK062(khu)001:10762: zhig gis mi tshangs par spyod pa'i sdom pa blang
NK062(khu)001:10763: ngo // de la theg pa 'og ma pas mi
NK062(khu)001:10764: tshangs par spyod pa spong pa'i yon tan rdzogs pa'o
NK062(khu)001:10765: ngo // // gnyis pa dam tshig gi rnam grangs mdor bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:10766: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga dang /
NK062(khu)001:10767: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu dang /
NK062(khu)001:10768: nyams na skyon yod pas 'da' bar dka' ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:10769: dang po rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga ni /
NK062(khu)001:10770: bla med mi spang dam tshig mchog /
NK062(khu)001:10772: bla med mi spang zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:10773: ngo bo nyid dang lam 'bras gong na gzhan med
NK062(khu)001:10774: pa'i phyir bla na med pa byang chub sems kyi
NK062(khu)001:10775: dam tshig ste / yang na don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10776: kun rdzob tu sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK062(khu)001:10777: du mnyam par rdzogs pa gnyis snang stong gnyis su
NK062(khu)001:10778: med par rtogs nas sgo gsum yi dam lha'i sku
NK062(khu)001:10779: gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya las mi 'da' zhing mi
NK062(khu)001:10780: spang ba ni byang chub sems kyi dam tshig go
NK062(khu)001:10781: // 'di la lta spyod lhas ma khrel ba zhig dgos gsung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:10783: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK062(khu)001:10784: sems can khams kyang der shes shing //
NK062(khu)001:10785: snang stong dbyer med rdo rje'i sku //
NK062(khu)001:10786: byang mthong zos pa thams cad la //
NK062(khu)001:10787: sems phyir gang yang byas snang med //
NK062(khu)001:10788: dran dang shes bzhin mngon btang la //
NK062(khu)001:10789: dus gsum rgyun du ma dran na //
NK062(khu)001:10790: theg mchog sngags par ci yis chud //
NK062(khu)001:10794: bla ma ni rdo rje slob dpon te /
NK062(khu)001:10795: de la spar khab ltar rnam pa lnga ste /
NK062(khu)001:10797: dam tshig 'bogs shing dbang bskur ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:10802: lta spyod dam tshig 'brel ba yis //
NK062(khu)001:10803: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang //
NK062(khu)001:10804: nyams chag skong dang shes rgyud 'grol //
NK062(khu)001:10805: man ngag lung gi slob dpon rnams //
NK062(khu)001:10808: sgo gsum zol zog med pas mnyes par bya ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:10809: 'di la sri zhu slob dpon gyis mkhrel ba zhig dgos gsung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:10812: lus la dbang ba'i rgyal po dang //
NK062(khu)001:10813: khu bo pha dang ma dang mig /
NK062(khu)001:10814: snying bas lhag pa'i tshul lta ste //
NK062(khu)001:10815: sgo gsum zol sgyu med pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:10816: yi dam lha ltar rgyun du bsam //
NK062(khu)001:10818: 'dir gong 'og brtsegs sdeb cung zad tsam zhig byed pas /
NK062(khu)001:10819: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK062(khu)001:10821: yang dag pa'i bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gnyis zung 'jug
NK062(khu)001:10822: gi lam du zhugs pa rnams ni rdo rje'i spun
NK062(khu)001:10823: no // de la spar khab ltar gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:10828: spyi yi mched dang nye ba'i mched //
NK062(khu)001:10829: ring ba'i mched dang 'dres pa'i mched //
NK062(khu)001:10831: de dag la sgo gsum gyis phan pa'i rtsal byin pa ni byams pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10832: 'di lag rtse gdung mched lcam gyis ma khrel ba zhig dgos gsung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:10835: mtha' yas sems can rang rig phyir //
NK062(khu)001:10836: gang yang bdag las gzhan min dang //
NK062(khu)001:10837: bde gshegs snying po'i spun yin phyir //
NK062(khu)001:10838: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas rang bzhin ni //
NK062(khu)001:10839: spyi yi mched de pha tshan bzhin //
NK062(khu)001:10840: sangs rgyas chos zhugs ring ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:10841: lta spyod mthun pa nye bar bshad //
NK062(khu)001:10842: pha gcig dam tshig nang 'dres pa //
NK062(khu)001:10843: nang tshan phas spun spun bas kyang //
NK062(khu)001:10844: lhag par bltas te bsrung ba ni //
NK062(khu)001:10845: lus kyi zas nor mnyes byas la //
NK062(khu)001:10846: sbur ma lta bur 'phangs bya min //
NK062(khu)001:10847: gdan bting khud sogs las bya ba //
NK062(khu)001:10848: bran bzhin nges par dang du blang //
NK062(khu)001:10850: de ltar bla ma bkur ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:10851: mched la byams pa gnyis ni sku'i dam tshig go //
NK062(khu)001:10852: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK062(khu)001:10854: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:10855: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:10856: bzlas pa las kyi sngags te sngags gsum dang /
NK062(khu)001:10857: dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK062(khu)001:10860: sku phyag rgya chen po ste phyag rgya bzhi po
NK062(khu)001:10861: de dag brtson pa rab kyis skad cig ma'i rgyun
NK062(khu)001:10862: du bar mi gcad par chu bo'i rgyun bzhin nam
NK062(khu)001:10863: / nyin zhag gcig la thun drug gam /
NK062(khu)001:10864: thun bzhi'i rnal 'byor du bya ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:10865: 'bring gis zla ba gcig la dus tshigs drug gam /
NK062(khu)001:10867: nya stong gnyis la rnal 'byor dang ldan par bya ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:10868: tha mas kyang zla dus sam /
NK062(khu)001:10869: ra ba bzhi 'am lo dus su yi dam gyi sgom bzlas dang /
NK062(khu)001:10870: tshogs gtor rnams ma chag par bya ba ni gsung gi dam tshig go //
NK062(khu)001:10873: rtsa ba bskyed dang las sngags dang //
NK062(khu)001:10874: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK062(khu)001:10875: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK062(khu)001:10876: rang gi sgo gsum yi dam gyi //
NK062(khu)001:10877: sku gsung thugs su mngon sbyar la //
NK062(khu)001:10878: rtag tu bzlas pa byed pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:10879: byang chub gzungs la zhugs pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:10880: rab kyis chu bo'i gzhung bzhin nam //
NK062(khu)001:10881: nyin gsum mtshan gsum nyag gcig tu'ang //
NK062(khu)001:10882: ma yengs tsam du ngang gis bzlas //
NK062(khu)001:10883: 'bring gis zla gcig dus drug dang //
NK062(khu)001:10884: dus bzhi bar du mi gcad cing //
NK062(khu)001:10885: tha ma bya ba'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK062(khu)001:10886: zla re'am ra ba'i dus dag tu //
NK062(khu)001:10887: brtson par 'bad de mi byed pa //
NK062(khu)001:10888: byang chub sa bon brlag pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:10889: tshogs dang gtor ma'ang de bzhin du //
NK062(khu)001:10892: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK062(khu)001:10896: gsal bkra gnyis ka mthun par bcu ste /
NK062(khu)001:10901: de la spyir gsang bzhi ni /
NK062(khu)001:10903: lta zab spyod pa barlanga po dang /
NK062(khu)001:10904: lha ming gzungs dang grub rtags rnams //
NK062(khu)001:10905: spyir gsang rnam pa bzhir bshad do //
NK062(khu)001:10907: sgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas //
NK062(khu)001:10908: bar du gsang ba bsgrub par bya //
NK062(khu)001:10910: mchod rdzas dang gsang spyod la sogs pa gsang bar 'os pa rnams gsang ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:10912: gsang bar 'os pa mdor bsdu na //
NK062(khu)001:10913: phud dang gtor ma tshogs dag dang //
NK062(khu)001:10914: b+han+d+ha phur pa mar me'i snod //
NK062(khu)001:10915: rdzas dang lag cha dkyil 'khor rnams //
NK062(khu)001:10916: skye bos mthong bar yongs mi bya //
NK062(khu)001:10917: dril bu rnga chung la sogs sgra //
NK062(khu)001:10918: skye bos thos sar yongs mi brdung //
NK062(khu)001:10919: grogs po'i spyod dang mtshang rnams dang //
NK062(khu)001:10920: sems can kun gyi ngan spyod dang //
NK062(khu)001:10921: kun la gnod pa'i spyod pa rnams //
NK062(khu)001:10922: shin tu gsang ba byang chub rgyud //
NK062(khu)001:10924: gsang bar gnyen gtad pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10925: slob dpon dang mched kyis gsang bar gnyer gtad pa rnams te /
NK062(khu)001:10927: gnyen gtad pa ni gdams pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:10928: sngar bshad dpon mched rnams kyis so //
NK062(khu)001:10930: de ltar gsang bcu de dag bdag gi don dang /
NK062(khu)001:10934: don bzhi po kho nar 'gyur bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:10937: ma 'dres pa rnams la lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK062(khu)001:10938: dam 'dres pa dag la yang gnas skabs dang sbyar la gsang ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:10939: tshig dang spyod lam yan chad kyi spa zhing smra
NK062(khu)001:10940: bar mi bya ba ni thugs kyi dam tshig go
NK062(khu)001:10941: // de dag ni chos la skyon yod pas gsang ba ma yin te /
NK062(khu)001:10943: gsang sngags gsang zhes bya ba ni //
NK062(khu)001:10944: gsang sngags skyon yod ma yin te //
NK062(khu)001:10945: sems can don phyir rab tu gsang //
NK062(khu)001:10946: gsang thub dngos grub mi yal bas //
NK062(khu)001:10947: gsang phyir gdams ngag sna tshogs gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:10949: 'di rnams la g.yo sgyu rang sems kyis ma khrel ba zhig dgos gsung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:10950: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams te //
NK062(khu)001:10952: de ltar dam tshig lnga po 'di dag ni lam
NK062(khu)001:10953: dang 'bras bu'i yon tan mtha' dag gi gzhi rten
NK062(khu)001:10954: yin pa'i phyir rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga rnams zhes
NK062(khu)001:10957: byang sems rnam gnyis slob dpon drug /
NK062(khu)001:10958: mched bzhi sngags gsum phyag rgya bzhi //
NK062(khu)001:10959: gsang bcu rtsa bar shes par bya //
NK062(khu)001:10961: sgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK062(khu)001:10963: de yang bla med mi spang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:10964: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad pa gnyis ni /
NK062(khu)001:10965: sgrub pa'i dam tshig yin pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10966: bla ma bkur ba dang mched la byams pa gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:10967: gsang ba gzhan la mi spel ba dang gsum ni /
NK062(khu)001:10968: bsrung ba'i dam tshig yin la /
NK062(khu)001:10969: de ltar rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po de dag
NK062(khu)001:10970: yan lag gi dam tshig las khyad par du gyur
NK062(khu)001:10972: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig bcu bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:10973: mi spang ba'i dam tshig lnga bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10974: mi dor ba'i dam tshig lnga bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:10975: mjug bsdu ba yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:10976: dang po mi spang ba'i dam tshig lnga bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:10977: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK062(khu)001:10978: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK062(khu)001:10980: 'di la spyir yang dag pa'i dug lnga dang /
NK062(khu)001:10981: log pa'i dus lnga gnyis su rgyas pa'i le'u bdun cu don gcig pa nas gsungs shing /
NK062(khu)001:10983: mi spang dam tshig bshad bya ba //
NK062(khu)001:10984: yang dag dug lnga log dug lnga //
NK062(khu)001:10986: de la dang po yang dag pa'i dug lnga ni /
NK062(khu)001:10987: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gnyis med mnyam nyid du rtogs tsam na /
NK062(khu)001:10988: rtogs med kyi shes pa la chos thams cad bzang ngan du mi 'byed pa ni gti mug dang /
