NK062(khu)001:10989: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can la thugs rjes chags pa'am /
NK062(khu)001:10990: rtogs pa'i lta ba dang 'du 'bral med pas 'dod chags dang /
NK062(khu)001:10991: rang byung gi ye shes su gsal tsa na log lta 'joms pa'i zhe sdang dang /
NK062(khu)001:10992: rang byung gi ye shes las ma gtogs pa'i chos gzhan med par shes pas sam /
NK062(khu)001:10993: mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba shong mi 'bebs pa'i nga rgyal dang /
NK062(khu)001:10994: gnyis 'dzin can gyi lta spyod mnyam pa nyid kyi klong du mi shong ba'i phrag dog ste /
NK062(khu)001:10995: de ltar yang dag pa'i dug lnga la gnas pas
NK062(khu)001:10996: ni theg pa chen po'i lta spyod dam tshig thams
NK062(khu)001:10997: cad rdzogs par 'gyur ba yin pas de dag spangs
NK062(khu)001:10998: na bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis mi 'grub ste /
NK062(khu)001:10999: byin gyis rlabs med par 'gyur ba'i phyir mi spang ngo //
NK062(khu)001:11002: lta bas phyogs ris mi phyed dang //
NK062(khu)001:11003: spyod pas blang dor mi bya ba //
NK062(khu)001:11004: theg pa chen po'i gti mug go //
NK062(khu)001:11005: bshad pa'i thabs mkhas 'dod chags dang //
NK062(khu)001:11006: longs spyod sems kyi rgyan shes nas //
NK062(khu)001:11007: shin tu zhen pa lam du gsung //
NK062(khu)001:11008: zhing bcu rlag byed zhe sdang mchog /
NK062(khu)001:11009: lta ngan 'joms pa de bzhin te //
NK062(khu)001:11010: thabs la mkhas pas spyod pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:11011: mngon par mtho ba'i lta ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:11012: ting 'dzin nges pa'i bran tshugs pa //
NK062(khu)001:11013: shin tu nga rgyal mchog tu gsung //
NK062(khu)001:11014: lta spyod dman la phrag dog cing //
NK062(khu)001:11015: dam ma 'dres rnams spong byed pa //
NK062(khu)001:11016: phrag dog dam tshig bsrung ba yin //
NK062(khu)001:11018: gnyis pa log pa'i dug lnga ni /
NK062(khu)001:11019: spyi'i mtshan nyid mi rtag pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11023: rang gi mtshan nyid sems kun nas blun zhing rmongs pa gti mug pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11025: nang sems can la rang dbang med par zhen cing sred pa 'dod chags dang /
NK062(khu)001:11026: kun nas mnar sems shing 'khrug pa zhe sdang dang /
NK062(khu)001:11027: khong nas 'gyings shing khengs pa nga rgyal dang /
NK062(khu)001:11028: gzhan gyi phun sum tshogs pa phrag tu mi shong ba phrag dog gi mtshan nyid yin la //
NK062(khu)001:11029: de ltar log pa'i dug lnga po de dag gi
NK062(khu)001:11030: rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid rtogs shing nyams su lon
NK062(khu)001:11031: na sku gsung thugs kho na las spang bya gang
NK062(khu)001:11032: yang mi dmigs pa'i phyir spang la de dag /
NK062(khu)001:11034: lta ba'i klungs las nyams nas nyan thos kyi theg par gol bar 'gyur ba'i phyir mi spang ngo //
NK062(khu)001:11036: gti mug ma 'dres kun nas rmongs //
NK062(khu)001:11038: zhe sdang ma 'dres mnar sems pa //
NK062(khu)001:11039: nga rgyal ma 'dres ri bo che //
NK062(khu)001:11042: skabs 'dir log pa'i dug lnga mi spong bar bshad pa 'di /
NK062(khu)001:11043: gsang ba yin nam bsgrags pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:11044: drang don yin nam nges don yin /
NK062(khu)001:11045: mi spang ba'i rgyu mtshan nam gtan tshigs gang yin /
NK062(khu)001:11046: ma spangs pa la dgos ched ci yod /
NK062(khu)001:11047: lam du byed tshul ji ltar du byed /
NK062(khu)001:11049: dri ba dang po gsang ba yin nam bsgrags pa yin zhes pa'i lan ni /
NK062(khu)001:11050: snod dang mi ldan pa'i gang zag blo chung gsang
NK062(khu)001:11051: sngags sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa la gsang zhing
NK062(khu)001:11052: / snod dang ldan pa'i gang zag blo chen dbang
NK062(khu)001:11053: po yang rab mchog tu gyur pa yang dag pa'i
NK062(khu)001:11054: lam du zhugs pa la bsgrags pa yin no //
NK062(khu)001:11055: dri ba gnyis pa drang don yin nam nges don yin zhes pa'i lan ni /
NK062(khu)001:11056: nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin can dang ye shes gnyis
NK062(khu)001:11057: spang gnyen du lta ba la drang don yin la
NK062(khu)001:11058: / gnyis med du lta ba la nges don yin te /
NK062(khu)001:11060: rnam rtog nyid na rang byung ye shes te //
NK062(khu)001:11061: rnam rtog mi skye ye shes brjod du med //
NK062(khu)001:11064: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug kyang //
NK062(khu)001:11065: byang chub chen po'i lam las byung //
NK062(khu)001:11067: dri ba gsum mi spong ba'i rgyu mtshan nam gtan tshigs gang yin zhes pa'i lan ni /
NK062(khu)001:11068: log pa'i dug lnga mi spong ba'i gtan tshigs lnga ste /
NK062(khu)001:11069: dug lnga spang bar bya ba'i gazhi'am rdzas ma grub pa'i phyir mi spang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11070: rnam par byang ba'i lam yin pa'i phyir mi spang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11071: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub yin pa'i phyir mi spang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11072: thabs shes rab kyi rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir mi spang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11073: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir mi spang ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:11075: dug lnga spa nga bar bya ba'i gazhi'am rdzas ma grub pa'i phyir mi spang ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11076: log pa'i dug lnga chos can /
NK062(khu)001:11077: spang bar bya ba'i gzhir ma grub ste /
NK062(khu)001:11078: shes bya'i gshis la dug lnga ye shes lnga tha
NK062(khu)001:11079: dad du ma grub pas nyon mongs pa rang kham
NK062(khu)001:11081: thag khra sbrul du snang yang gshis la sbrul med pa bzhin no //
NK062(khu)001:11083: ma rig pa nyid spang du med //
NK062(khu)001:11084: rig pa ye shes bsgrub tu med //
NK062(khu)001:11086: gnyis pa dug lnga rnam par byang ba'i lam yin pa'i phyir mi spang ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11087: log pa'i dug lnga chos can /
NK062(khu)001:11088: rnam par byang ba'i lam yin te /
NK062(khu)001:11089: dug lnga spyi'i mtshan nyid stong zhing bdag med du rtogs /
NK062(khu)001:11090: rang gi mtshan nyid ye shes lngar rtogs /
NK062(khu)001:11091: de yang gnyis med du rtogs pas /
NK062(khu)001:11092: dug lnga gang skyes chos nyid du 'char ba las gzhan pa'i 'bras bu bsgrub bya med pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:11094: dug gi sman mar gyis dug nad 'joms shing ro rtsa'i mchog tu 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK062(khu)001:11096: nyon mongs rang dang spyir bstan pa //
NK062(khu)001:11097: mtshan nyid ma nor don rtogs na //
NK062(khu)001:11098: rnam par byang ba'i lam du 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11101: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug kyang //
NK062(khu)001:11102: byang chub chen po'i lam las byung //
NK062(khu)001:11103: kun spyod yon tan lnga rnams kyang //
NK062(khu)001:11104: chos nyid dbyings kyi rgyan zhes gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:11106: de yang log pa'i dug lnga po lam du 'gro ba'i gnad ni /
NK062(khu)001:11107: zhe sdang med na rang gi ye shes gsal mi thebs /
NK062(khu)001:11108: 'dod chags med na rgyud dum bur 'gyur te 'bral med rgyud la mi skye /
NK062(khu)001:11109: gti mug med na bzang ngan du 'byed pa'i rtog med kyi shes pa rgyud la mi skye /
NK062(khu)001:11110: nga rgyal med na chos nyid du la mi zlos //
NK062(khu)001:11111: phrag dog med na chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du khod mi snyoms pa'i phyir ro //
NK062(khu)001:11113: gsal thebs 'bral ba med 'byed pa med chos nyid
NK062(khu)001:11114: du la zlos mnyam pa nyid du khod snyoms pas
NK062(khu)001:11116: rma bya dug la longs spyod pas spu mdangs legs shing skad snyan pa bzhin no //
NK062(khu)001:11117: gsum pa dug lnga sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub yin pa'i phyir mi spang ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11118: log pa'i dug lnga chos can /
NK062(khu)001:11119: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub tu 'gyur te /
NK062(khu)001:11120: dug lnga yi ge as mtshon nas sku /
NK062(khu)001:11122: +amo gyis mtshon nas thugs su brda sprad pas sgo
NK062(khu)001:11123: gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs las mi 'da' ba'i phyir
NK062(khu)001:11124: ro // dper na dug la sngags kyi btab pa bzhin no //
NK062(khu)001:11126: nyon mongs dug lngar snang grub kyang //
NK062(khu)001:11127: gang na'ang med de de nyid yin //
NK062(khu)001:11129: bzhi pa dug lnga thabs dang shes rab kyi rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir mi spang ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11130: log pa'i dug lnga chos can thabs dang shes rab kyi rang bzhin yin te /
NK062(khu)001:11131: dug lnga ye shes lngar ma 'gags par 'char ba thabs dang /
NK062(khu)001:11132: de la rang bzhin med par rtogs pa shes rab yin la /
NK062(khu)001:11133: de gnyis ye nas dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK062(khu)001:11134: dper na tshad nad can dang rlung nad can la /
NK062(khu)001:11135: ga bur sman dang dug tu snang yang /
NK062(khu)001:11136: ga bur la sman dug dbyer med pa bzhin no //
NK062(khu)001:11138: ma 'gag snang ba thabs yin te //
NK062(khu)001:11139: rang bzhin med pa shes rab yin //
NK062(khu)001:11141: lnga pa dug lnga rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i bdag
NK062(khu)001:11142: nyid chen po yin pa'i phyir mi spang ba ni
NK062(khu)001:11143: / log pa'i dug lnga chos can /
NK062(khu)001:11144: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid yin te /
NK062(khu)001:11145: zhe sngang mi bskyed pa rdo rje'i rigs dang stong pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK062(khu)001:11146: gti mug rnam par snang mdzad de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK062(khu)001:11147: nga rgyal rin chen 'byung ldan rin po che'i rigs dang mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK062(khu)001:11148: 'dod chags snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma'i rigs dang so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK062(khu)001:11149: phrag dog don yod grub pa las kyi rigs dang bya ba grub pa'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:11150: dper na 'khyags pa'i bdag nyid chu yin pa bzhin no //
NK062(khu)001:11152: zhe sdang rang byung ye shes chen po dang //
NK062(khu)001:11155: nyon mongs dug lngar snang ba'i rang bzhin rnams //
NK062(khu)001:11156: rnam grol ye shes lnga yi ngang du snang //
NK062(khu)001:11157: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK062(khu)001:11159: dug lnga ma spangs pa la dgos ched ci yod ces pa'i lan ni /
NK062(khu)001:11160: log pa'i dug lnga ma spangs pa'i dgos ched la yang lnga ste /
NK062(khu)001:11161: dngos po la mngon par zhen pa'i blo ldog pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK062(khu)001:11162: spros pa'i bag chags nye bar zhi ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK062(khu)001:11163: chos nyid zab mo'i don la blo myur ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK062(khu)001:11164: bka' zab mo la gus pa skye ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK062(khu)001:11165: spyod lam tshogs su 'gyur ba'i dgos ched do //
NK062(khu)001:11166: de la dang po dngos po la mngon par zhen pa'i blo ldog pa'i dgos ched ni /
NK062(khu)001:11167: dper na pha mes thams cad mes tshig nas shi ba'i mi zhig gi bsam pas /
NK062(khu)001:11168: me ni tsha zhing sreg ba kho na'o snyam du mngon par zhen pa cig /
NK062(khu)001:11169: dus nam zhig gi tshe 'brog dgon pa zhig tu phyin pas /
NK062(khu)001:11170: de na drang srong me'i gtsang sbra can bya ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11171: ri dwags me byi dkar po bya ba me la
NK062(khu)001:11172: gnas bcas nas 'tsho ba'i longs spyod thams cad me
NK062(khu)001:11174: mdog legs shing mdangs gsal bar mthong bas /
NK062(khu)001:11175: 'o na me 'di tsha zhing sreg pa kho nar 'dug snyam pa'i mngon par zhen pa log go //
NK062(khu)001:11176: dpe de bzhin du theg pa 'og ma pa nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i chos kho nar bzung ste /
NK062(khu)001:11177: spong 'gegs sbyong sgyur byed pa la /
NK062(khu)001:11179: nyon mongs pa nyid rang rig pa byang chub kyi
NK062(khu)001:11180: sems yin pas ma spangs bar lam du byas na
NK062(khu)001:11181: / 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas tshe gcig lus gcig la 'thob bo zhes brjod pas /
NK062(khu)001:11182: theg pa 'og ma ba dug lnga 'khor ba'i chos
NK062(khu)001:11183: kho na yin snyam ba'i mngon par zhen pa las
NK062(khu)001:11184: grol lo // gnyis pa spros pa'i bag chags nye bar zhi ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK062(khu)001:11185: spang blang la sogs pa gnyis byung phan chod spros
NK062(khu)001:11186: pa ste gnyis su zhen pa las log tsa na
NK062(khu)001:11187: spros pa'i bag chags zhi ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:11188: gsum pa chos nyid zab mo'i don la blo myur ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK062(khu)001:11189: nyon mongs nyid chos nyid yin pas de ltar rtogs na /
NK062(khu)001:11190: lam dang 'bras bu gzhan nas btsal mi dgos par
NK062(khu)001:11191: thag chod pas chos nyid zab mo'i don la blo
NK062(khu)001:11192: myur ba'o // bzhi pa bka' zab mo la gus pa skye ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK062(khu)001:11193: nyon mongs pa ma spang bar byang chub thob pa'i
NK062(khu)001:11194: thabs khyad par can dang ldan pa sngags kyi bka'
NK062(khu)001:11195: brgyud 'di ni / theg pa gzhan las khyad par
NK062(khu)001:11196: du 'phags pas shin tu zab pa'o snyam pa'i gus
NK062(khu)001:11197: brgyud 'di ni / pa skye ba'o // lnga pa spyod lam tshogs su 'gyur ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK062(khu)001:11198: sgo gsum gyi byed spyod thams cad ma 'gags par shes pas rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs /
NK062(khu)001:11199: de la rang bzhin med par shes bas ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs te /
NK062(khu)001:11200: de'i gnad kyis nyon mongs pa dang rnam rtog ye shes su 'char ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:11201: de yang rang gi sems nyid phyin ci ma log par rtogs tsa na /
NK062(khu)001:11202: nyon mongs pa lnga'i ro ma 'gag par skyes ba nyid chos nyid du 'char te /
NK062(khu)001:11203: de ltar shar tsa na rang rgyud du mi 'chor ro //
NK062(khu)001:11204: skye bo tha mal pa ltar nyon mongs pa'i mtha' la zhen pa yang med do //
NK062(khu)001:11207: stong pa bsgoms pas ye shes skye mi 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11208: snang ba 'di la zhen pa drag byas na //
NK062(khu)001:11209: nyon mongs shas che'i sa na ye shes 'bar //
NK062(khu)001:11210: dper na chu bo chen po 'bras bu bzhin //
NK062(khu)001:11212: nyon mongs pa gang skyes pa ye shes yin pas /
NK062(khu)001:11213: de ltar shes par bya la nyams su blang ngo //
NK062(khu)001:11214: yang nyon mongs pa chos can /
NK062(khu)001:11216: spang bar bya ba'i rdzas ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:11219: zhes kyang bsgrub tu rung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:11221: dug lnga lam du byed tshul ji ltar du byed /
NK062(khu)001:11223: dug lnga lam du byed tshul la brtag pa bzhi ste /
NK062(khu)001:11225: zhe sdang lta bu gcig la sbyar na /
NK062(khu)001:11226: rgyud la zhe sdang drag po skam gyis skyes pa'i rang dog de ka la lam du byed dam /
NK062(khu)001:11227: de gtan tshigs kyis gzhigs pas rang bzhin ma grub pa de la lam du byed dam /
NK062(khu)001:11228: zhe sdang la brten nas gnyen po byams pa bsgom pa lam du byed dam /
NK062(khu)001:11229: zhe sdang 'gags pa'i rjes thob kyi shes pa gsal la rtog med de la lam du byed /
NK062(khu)001:11230: dang po ltar na pha bsad kyi bu yang mtshams
NK062(khu)001:11231: med kyi las kyis mi gos par rnam grol thob
NK062(khu)001:11232: par thal / gnyis pa ltar na /
NK062(khu)001:11233: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang khyad par med par thal /
NK062(khu)001:11235: 'dod nyon mongs pa lam du byed 'dod kyang gnyen po lam byed du thal /
NK062(khu)001:11237: ma rig pa dang ye shes tha dad du thal /
NK062(khu)001:11238: de thams cad kyi rtags khas blangs /
NK062(khu)001:11240: 'dod par mi nus pa ma yin te /
NK062(khu)001:11241: lung rig gis gsal ba 'babs bo //
NK062(khu)001:11244: rje gong bu ba skyod ston sh+aakya ye shes kyi zhal nas /
NK062(khu)001:11245: skad cig ma dang po la nyon mongs pa thol gyis skyes pa la /
NK062(khu)001:11246: skad cig ma gnyis par de chos nyid du shes pa la lam du byed gsung ste /
NK062(khu)001:11247: des kyang brtag pa tha ma'i skyon mi spong ngo //
NK062(khu)001:11248: rje sgro phug pa'i bzhed kyis /
NK062(khu)001:11249: nyon mongs bskam skyes pa la lam du byed de /
NK062(khu)001:11250: de yang rtogs pa lta ba'i rtsis zin pa /
NK062(khu)001:11251: rang rgyud du ma shor ba /
NK062(khu)001:11252: nyon mongs pa rang gi mtha' la ma zhen pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11253: chos gsum ldan zhig la lam du byed gsung mod kyi /
NK062(khu)001:11255: gong gi chos gsum ldan dang /
NK062(khu)001:11256: nyon mongs pa skam skyes pa la khyad yod dam med /
NK062(khu)001:11257: yod na lam du bya rgyu de nyon mongs pa skam skyes pa ma yin par thal /
NK062(khu)001:11258: chos gsum ldan yin pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:11259: skam skyes yin kyang chos gsum ldan yin na /
NK062(khu)001:11262: brtag pa dang po'i skyon gyis gnod do //
NK062(khu)001:11263: des na mkhas grub chen po dag gi bzhed pas /
NK062(khu)001:11264: nyon mongs pa skam skyes pa lam du byed pa /
NK062(khu)001:11265: 'o na pha bsad kyi bu rang grol bar thal zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:11266: de brtag ste ma h+aa yo ga'i lam tshang la
NK062(khu)001:11267: ma nor ba lam du byed pa'i pha bsad kyi
NK062(khu)001:11269: de las gzhan pa'i pha bsad kyi bu la zer /
NK062(khu)001:11270: snga ma ltar na 'dod thog la /
NK062(khu)001:11271: phyi ma ltar na khyab pa med de /
NK062(khu)001:11272: pha bsad kyi bu de la zhe sdang skam skyes yod kyang /
NK062(khu)001:11273: ma h+aa yo ga'i lam pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK062(khu)001:11274: 'o na ma h+aa yo ga'i lam tshang la ma nor ba gang yin zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:11275: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba'i gdengs dang ldan pa /
NK062(khu)001:11276: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i
NK062(khu)001:11277: thabs kyis nyon mongs pa spyad kyang mi 'ching ba
NK062(khu)001:11278: / rma bya dug gis 'tsho ba lta bu'i rnal
NK062(khu)001:11279: 'byor pas nyon mongs pa skam gyis skyes pa'i dus
NK062(khu)001:11280: / na / skye bo tha mal pa ltar nyon mongs pa'i dbang du mi gtong /
NK062(khu)001:11283: byang chub sems dpa' ltar mi spyod /
NK062(khu)001:11284: sngags phyi rgyud ltar mi bsgyur bar /
NK062(khu)001:11285: dpe nya lam du chu bde ba lta bu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11286: ma h+aa yo ga'i lam pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa yin no //
NK062(khu)001:11287: de ltar ma yin pa'i gsang sngags par khas 'ches
NK062(khu)001:11288: pa gab pa'i gsang ba chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK062(khu)001:11290: sbas pa'i gsang ba ta na dang ga na la sogs pa la mngon par 'chel nas /
NK062(khu)001:11291: gsang sngags sgra ji bzhin pa ltar spyod pa rnams ni /
NK062(khu)001:11292: mnar med pa'i sems can dmyal ba chen por skye bar /
NK062(khu)001:11293: sngags gsar rnying gi rgyud sde du mar gsungs so //
NK062(khu)001:11294: gnyis pa mi dor ba'i dam tshig lnga bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:11295: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK062(khu)001:11296: dag pa'i snod bcud mi dor ro //
NK062(khu)001:11298: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK062(khu)001:11300: dkar rtsi byang chub kyi sems /
NK062(khu)001:11302: dri ni dri chen dri chu /
NK062(khu)001:11303: sha chen dang lnga po ni /
NK062(khu)001:11304: sngar le'u bco brgyad par bshad pa'i grub pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:11305: dag pa'i snod bcud mi dor ro //
NK062(khu)001:11306: zhes pas rigs lnga dang ye shes lngar ye nas
NK062(khu)001:11307: dag pa'i snod bcud 'di dag la longs spyad par
NK062(khu)001:11308: bya ste / gtsang rme'i rtog pa sbyangs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11309: thun mong gi yon tan gnyis gnyis 'byung ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11310: rigs lnga ye shes lnga bsgrub pa'i rdzas khyad par
NK062(khu)001:11311: can yin pa'i phyir dang du blang zhing mi dor
NK062(khu)001:11312: ro // de yang gsal bkra las /
NK062(khu)001:11313: grub pa bzhi yis brgyan pa'i phyir //
NK062(khu)001:11314: nad lnga sel phyir blang ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:11315: gtsang rme'i rtog pa sbyang phyir blang //
NK062(khu)001:11316: thun mong dgos pa lnga phyir dang //
NK062(khu)001:11317: rigs lnga bsgrub pa'i yon tan ni //
NK062(khu)001:11318: sdug bsngal las grol dngos grub thob //
NK062(khu)001:11320: nad lnga sel ba'i phyir dang du blang ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11321: byang sems dkar pos tsha ba'i nad sel /
NK062(khu)001:11322: dmar pos grang ba'i nad sel /
NK062(khu)001:11323: dri chen gyi dug nad sel /
NK062(khu)001:11324: dri chus gag pa'i nad sel /
NK062(khu)001:11325: sha chen gyis mdze nad sel lo //
NK062(khu)001:11326: gtsang rme'i rtog pa sbyang ba'i phyir dang du blang ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11327: kri yog man chad dkar gsum mngar gsum gtsang zhing /
NK062(khu)001:11328: dam rdzas lnga rme bar 'dzin pa'i rtogs pa las bzlog pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:11329: sems can rtogs pa bzlog phyir sman //
NK062(khu)001:11330: gtso rung dang du blang bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:11332: thun mong gi dgos pa lnga dang ldan pa'i phyir dang blang ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11333: byang sems dkar po zos pas tshe ring /
NK062(khu)001:11338: rigs lnga ye shes lnga bsgrub pa'i rdzas khyad par can yin phyir dang du blang ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11339: byang sems dkar pos mi bskyod pa dang stong nyid ye shes /
NK062(khu)001:11340: dmar pos mtha' yas dang sor rtogs ye shes /
NK062(khu)001:11341: dri chen gyis rnam snang dang me long ye shes /
NK062(khu)001:11342: dri chus don grub dang bya grub ye shes /
NK062(khu)001:11343: sha chen gyis rin 'byung dang mnyam nyid ye shes bsgrub pa'i rdzas khyad par can yin pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:11344: dam rdzas lnga po de dag dang du blang zhing mi dor bar rgyun du spyad par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:11345: gsum pa mjug bsdu ba yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:11346: yan lag bcu'i rtogs pas spyad //
NK062(khu)001:11348: yan lag bcu'i dam tshig ste //
NK062(khu)001:11350: rtsa ba la la dag ma nyams pa las byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK062(khu)001:11351: sgrub pa'i grogs cher byed pa'i phyir mi spang ba lnga dang /
NK062(khu)001:11352: mi dor ba ni yan lag bcu'i dam tshig ste /
NK062(khu)001:11353: ye nas dag mnyam rtogs pas spyad //
NK062(khu)001:11355: dngos po thams cad ye gdod ma nas dag pa
NK062(khu)001:11356: gsum dang mnyam pa bzhi'i ngo bor gnas pa de
NK062(khu)001:11357: dag gnas pa ltar rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas mi
NK062(khu)001:11358: spang ba nyon mongs pa dug lnga la spyad pa
NK062(khu)001:11359: dang / rtogs par 'dod pa'i rnal 'byor pas mi dor ba dam rdzas lnga la spyad par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:11360: gsum pa nyams na skyon yod pas 'da' bar dka' ba bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:11363: bsrung zhing bsgrub pa'i dam tshig lnga //
NK062(khu)001:11365: sngar bshad pa'i bsrung zhing bsdoms pa'i dam tshig gsum dang /
NK062(khu)001:11366: bsgrub cing blang pa'i dam tshig gnyis te dam tshig lnga po 'di ni /
NK062(khu)001:11367: rtsa ba yin te rigs med 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11369: lam dang 'bras bu'i chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba
NK062(khu)001:11370: yin te de'i phyir rtsa ba'i dam tshig ces bya'o
NK062(khu)001:11371: // de ltar rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po de nyams na /
NK062(khu)001:11372: mi dang lha'i rigs kyang med par 'gyur na /
NK062(khu)001:11373: theg pa chen po'i rigs lta smos kyang ci dgos te /
NK062(khu)001:11374: mkhar gyi 'gram zhig pa dang mtshungs par 'gyur pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:11375: mi spang mi dor lnga gnyis ni //
NK062(khu)001:11377: mi spang ba'i dam tshig dug lnga ste /
NK062(khu)001:11378: de yang log pa'i dug lnga spangs na nyan thos lta bur gyur te /
NK062(khu)001:11379: lam nor bas gsang sngags kyi lta ba las nyams so //
NK062(khu)001:11380: yang dag pa'i dug lnga spangs na bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis mi 'grub ste /
NK062(khu)001:11381: rgyud la byin rlabs mi 'jug par 'gyur ro //
NK062(khu)001:11382: mi dor ba'i dam tshig dam rdzas lnga spong ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11383: spyod pa kri yog tu gol bas na /
NK062(khu)001:11384: lta ba dang spyod pa ma 'brel bas gsang sngags kyi theg pa 'dir mi chud pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:11385: de ltar dam tshig lnga tshan gnyis bcu po de ni /
NK062(khu)001:11388: yan lag gi dam tshig yin yang /
NK062(khu)001:11389: de dag las 'da' na nyes skyon chen po 'dug pa'i phyir 'da' bar daka'o //
NK062(khu)001:11390: gsum pa mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig skyon yon dang bcas pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:11391: mnyam la mnyam par ma yin no //
NK062(khu)001:11393: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yi //
NK062(khu)001:11395: dngos po thams cad kyi rang bzhin bden gsum ris med du mnyam la mnyam pa ltar /
NK062(khu)001:11396: shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gyis mnyam par sbyor ba'i dus na /
NK062(khu)001:11397: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK062(khu)001:11399: gang yang bdag nyid chen po mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK062(khu)001:11400: don las mi 'da' ba ni mnyam pa'i dam tshig
NK062(khu)001:11401: yin la / de'i don la mi 'da' bar gnas na /
NK062(khu)001:11402: de'i 'bras bu ji lta bu 'thob ce na /
NK062(khu)001:11403: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob 'gyur pas //
NK062(khu)001:11405: gang yang ma spangs par 'bras bu mnyam rdzogs chen
NK062(khu)001:11406: po'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po dbye ba med
NK062(khu)001:11407: pa'i sa thob par 'gyur bas so //
NK062(khu)001:11408: 'das na sangs rgyas ma yin no //
NK062(khu)001:11410: gang zhig bdag nyid chen po'i dam tshig de las 'das shing /
NK062(khu)001:11411: mnyam pa'i dam tshig ma bsrung bas te mi mnyam par bzung na /
NK062(khu)001:11412: sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo las nyams pa yin pas /
NK062(khu)001:11413: thabs gzhan gyis 'bras bu mnyam rdzogs chen po'i sangs rgyas thob pa ma yin no //
NK062(khu)001:11414: bzhi pa dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:11415: nyams pa dang 'grogs pa'i skyon dang /
NK062(khu)001:11416: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon dang /
NK062(khu)001:11417: yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:11418: dang po nyams pa dang 'grogs pa'i skyon bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:11419: rtsa ba nyams pa'i brjod mi lang /
NK062(khu)001:11421: rtsa ba nyams pa'i 'chal pa dag /
NK062(khu)001:11423: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po yang sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig gsum du 'dus pas /
NK062(khu)001:11424: sku'i dam tshig slob dpon dang mched la nyams na gang nyams pa'i gnas su gso ste /
NK062(khu)001:11425: 'byor ba dang sri zhu la sogs pa kho nas zhi bar bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:11426: gsung gi dam tshig bla na med pa dang sngags
NK062(khu)001:11427: dang phyag rgya nyams na sgrub pa chen po lan
NK062(khu)001:11429: bzlas pa ldab kyis bsab bo //
NK062(khu)001:11430: thugs kyi dam tshig gsang bcu nyams na shes rab
NK062(khu)001:11431: dang ting nge 'dzin gyis gso bar byed dgos pa
NK062(khu)001:11432: la / gal te dam tshig nyams pa gso bar
NK062(khu)001:11433: mi byed pa'i 'chal ba ste 'bras bu 'grub pa'i
NK062(khu)001:11434: rten dam tshig med pa dag /
NK062(khu)001:11435: gso la nye bar mi brtson dang /
NK062(khu)001:11436: skad cig yud tsam smra ma byed //
NK062(khu)001:11438: dam tshig nyams pa gso ba'i cho ga la dus nye bar mi brtson pa de dang /
NK062(khu)001:11439: dus skad cig tsam mam yud tsam du yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK062(khu)001:11440: smras na nyes pa ci yod ce na /
NK062(khu)001:11441: dper na sbal pa rma can gcig gi zhor la sbal pa dong gang rmas par 'gyur ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11442: thu ru rngo can gcig gis rta khyu gang rngos 'khyer ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11443: 'o ma rul ba thig pa gcig gis 'o ma zangs gang rul bar byed pa bzhin du /
NK062(khu)001:11444: nyams gyur nyes pa brjod mi lang //
NK062(khu)001:11446: dam tshig nyams pa dang 'grogs par gyur pa'i nyes pa yang /
NK062(khu)001:11447: dam can thams cad kyi bar chad du 'gyur ba la sogs pa brjod kyis mi lang ste /
NK062(khu)001:11448: nyams pa gcig gi zhor la de dang dam 'dres
NK062(khu)001:11449: pa'i rnal 'byor pa kun kyang dmyal bar ltung ba'i
NK062(khu)001:11451: lung pa gcig pa'i chu la yang btung bar mi bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:11452: gnyis pa rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:11453: rtsa ba'i dam tshig bzhin du 'du //
NK062(khu)001:11455: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:11456: sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11458: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po nyams par gyur na /
NK062(khu)001:11459: tshe 'dir yang sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur te /
NK062(khu)001:11460: las ci brtsams pa la nus mthu med cing bar
NK062(khu)001:11461: chad mang bas mi 'grub cing gang yang don med
NK062(khu)001:11463: yid du mi 'ong sna tshogs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:11466: phyi mar yang yid du mi 'ong ba'i sdug bsngal
NK062(khu)001:11467: sna tshogs pa'i 'bras bu ngan song gsum mi 'dod
NK062(khu)001:11468: bzhin du khab len la lcags 'du ba ltar rang
NK062(khu)001:11470: gsum pa yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:11471: yan lag dam tshig ngan song ltung //
NK062(khu)001:11473: yan lag dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:11475: yan lag gi dam tshig mi spang ba lnga dang /
NK062(khu)001:11476: mi dor ba lnga ste bcu nyams na nyan rang dang kri yog tu gol bar gyur na /
NK062(khu)001:11477: 'bras bu med cing ngan song ltung //
NK062(khu)001:11479: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa nyams su blangs pa'i
NK062(khu)001:11480: 'bras bu thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub med
NK062(khu)001:11481: cing / lam mchog tu gyur pa spangs pa'i nyes
NK062(khu)001:11482: pas slar ngan song gi gnas su lhung bar 'gyur
NK062(khu)001:11483: cing / ro // de yang gsal bkra las /
NK062(khu)001:11484: nyams par gyur pa'i skyon bshad pa //
NK062(khu)001:11485: byang sems dam tshig spangs gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:11486: bskal par dge ba ci bsags kyang //
NK062(khu)001:11487: gzhi rten med par gyur pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:11489: sku yi dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:11490: ya nga'i nad sogs sdug bsngal che //
NK062(khu)001:11491: dus min tshe zad bar chad mang //
NK062(khu)001:11492: bskal par rdo rje dmyal bar ltung //
NK062(khu)001:11493: bde bas rab tu brel bar 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11494: gsung gi dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:11495: bgegs rnams thogs med 'ong ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:11496: rkyen dang ye 'drog mang ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:11497: chos la byin rlabs med 'gyur zhing //
NK062(khu)001:11498: bskal pa gnyis su dmyal bar lhung //
NK062(khu)001:11500: thugs kyi dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:11502: myong shing lkugs pa'i gnas su 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11503: yang dag bsgrubs la rtags med cing //
NK062(khu)001:11504: lce la zhing rmod la sogs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:11505: dmyal bar bskal pa gsum du gnas //
NK062(khu)001:11506: rtsa ba kun nyams 'chal pa dag /
NK062(khu)001:11507: gso la nye bar mi brtson na //
NK062(khu)001:11508: rdo rje dmyal bar de ltung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:11509: dmyal ba phal pa thams cad kyi //
NK062(khu)001:11510: sdug bsngal gcig tu bsdoms pas ni //
NK062(khu)001:11511: de yi 'bum gyi char mi phod //
NK062(khu)001:11512: sangs rgyas stong gi 'od zer dang //
NK062(khu)001:11513: byang chub sems dpa'i phrin las kun //
NK062(khu)001:11514: rgyun du mdzad kyang phan mi 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11515: bskal pa ther 'bum la sogs su //
NK062(khu)001:11518: se gol gcig gis phyin par byed //
NK062(khu)001:11519: de bas shin tu nan tan gyis //
NK062(khu)001:11520: yan lag dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:11521: longs spyod mang du 'phel ba med //
NK062(khu)001:11522: theg pa che la dpyad 'dogs shing //
NK062(khu)001:11523: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub rnams //
NK062(khu)001:11524: shin tu ring bar 'gyur ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:11525: gdul bya'i don rnams yal 'gyur zhing //
NK062(khu)001:11526: lta spyod ya chad gyur ba nyid //
NK062(khu)001:11527: theg pa phyi nang 'dres pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:11528: bka' yi byin rlabs bsgrub par dka' //
NK062(khu)001:11529: srung ba'i lha rnams g.yel ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:11530: zab mo'i chos las ring 'gyur zhing //
NK062(khu)001:11531: bskal par ngan song sdug bsngal myong //
NK062(khu)001:11534: dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes skyon dpag tu med pa gsungs nas gda' bas /
NK062(khu)001:11535: gsang sngags kyi sgor zhugs pa'i rnal 'byor pa kun gyis /
NK062(khu)001:11536: dam tshig ma nyams par bsrung ba la nan tan
NK062(khu)001:11537: chen po byed ba shin tu gal che lags so
NK062(khu)001:11538: gal che lags so gal che lags so //
NK062(khu)001:11539: lnga pa dam tshig gi rang bzhin bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:11540: dam tshig rnams ni bdag nyid yin //
NK062(khu)001:11542: dam tshig rnams ni rdo rje che //
NK062(khu)001:11544: gong du bshad pa'i rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig de dag rnams ni /
NK062(khu)001:11545: lta spyod gnyis dbyer mi phyed pas sam /
NK062(khu)001:11546: gzhi rang bzhin dang lam dang 'bras bu gsum dbyer me phyed pa'i phyir rdo rje zhes bya ste /
NK062(khu)001:11547: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin //
NK062(khu)001:11549: de dag dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi lam yang yin la ngo bo yang yin pas na /
NK062(khu)001:11550: bdag nyid ces brjod pa yin no //
NK062(khu)001:11551: drug pa dam tshig gi rnam grangs rgyas par bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:11552: sum brgya drug cur dbye ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:11553: gdul bya la dgongs nas dbye ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:11554: dang po sum brgya drug cur dbye ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11555: rtsa ba'i dam tshig gnyis su dbye //
NK062(khu)001:11558: phyi ma rtsa ba yan lag las //
NK062(khu)001:11559: lnga bcu'i brgya dang drug cu dang //
NK062(khu)001:11560: nyis brgya'i bsrung bya ma lus pa //
NK062(khu)001:11561: bka' lung gnyis kyi rjes su snyeg /
NK062(khu)001:11563: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig la rnam
NK062(khu)001:11564: grangs su phye bas sum brgya drug cu ston pa
NK062(khu)001:11565: las / dang po rtsa ba'i dam tshig brgya drug cu'i bsrung dmigs ni /
NK062(khu)001:11566: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni //
NK062(khu)001:11568: rtsa ba'i dam tshig bla na med pa byang chub kyi sems mi spang ba dang gcig /
NK062(khu)001:11569: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon bkur ba dang gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:11570: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad pa dang gsum /
NK062(khu)001:11571: yang dag pa'i lam du zhugs pa'i mched la byams pa dang bzhi /
NK062(khu)001:11572: gsang bcu po snod dang mi ldan pa la gsang
NK062(khu)001:11573: ba'i don phyir mi smra ba dang lnga po de
NK062(khu)001:11574: dag la nang tshegs su dbye ba'i grangs ni /
NK062(khu)001:11575: gcig la'ang gnyis dang bcu phrag gsum //
NK062(khu)001:11577: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po'i ya gyal gcig la'ang thabs kyis ma 'gags par spyod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11578: shes rab lta bas rtogs pa gnyis gnyis su phye bas rtsa ba la bcu dang /
NK062(khu)001:11579: de dag spyi ru bzhag nas /
NK062(khu)001:11580: bye brag tu rtsa ba lnga po re re la
NK062(khu)001:11581: yang bcu phrag gsum gsum du phye bas brgya drug
NK062(khu)001:11584: pany+tsa'i nying lag zhes pa yang //
NK062(khu)001:11585: dang po nyid nas thabs spyod dang //
NK062(khu)001:11586: shes rab nyid kyi nyis 'gyur yin //
NK062(khu)001:11587: re re'ang bsrung bya bcu gsum ste //
NK062(khu)001:11589: dang po bla na med pa byang chub kyi sems mi spang ba la bcu phrag gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:11590: yi dam gyi lha zhi khro gnyis re re la'ang
NK062(khu)001:11591: rtsa ba'i lha de la lhag pa'i lha dgu dgu
NK062(khu)001:11592: bkod pas lhag pa'i lha dgu nyid dang bcu ste
NK062(khu)001:11594: theg pa thun mong ba ltar /
NK062(khu)001:11595: byams pa snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms te /
NK062(khu)001:11596: thun mong gi tshad med pa bzhi dang /
NK062(khu)001:11597: khro bo rtog pa lha rgyud ltar /
NK062(khu)001:11598: khro gtum gyi tshul gyis gdug pa can rjes su 'dzin pa'i byams pa /
NK062(khu)001:11599: brtse ba chen pos myur du sgrol ba'i snying rjes
NK062(khu)001:11600: phung po tshogs su ston cing shes pa gnas spor
NK062(khu)001:11601: ba'i dga' ba / dug gsum rags par smin pa'i
NK062(khu)001:11602: gdul bya rnams yal bar mi 'dor ba'i btang snyoms
NK062(khu)001:11603: te thun mong ma yin pa'i tshad med pa bzhi
NK062(khu)001:11604: ba'i dga' ba / ste / don dam pa byang
NK062(khu)001:11605: chub sems kyi bden pa dkor bdun ngo bo nyid
NK062(khu)001:11606: du lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11607: kun rdzob byang chub sems kyi bden pa sku dang
NK062(khu)001:11608: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du mnyam par rdzogs pa
NK062(khu)001:11609: gnyis te / kun dril bas bla med mi spang ba la sum cu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11611: byang chub sems ni bla med lha //
NK062(khu)001:11612: zhi khro'i lha dgu nyid dang bcu //
NK062(khu)001:11613: bcu gnyis bsam las mi 'da' zhing //
NK062(khu)001:11614: thun mong mchog gi tshad med brgyad //
NK062(khu)001:11615: bden gnyis byang chub rnam pa bcu //
NK062(khu)001:11616: bla med gsal bas nyams mi bya //
NK062(khu)001:11617: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11618: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor na //
NK062(khu)001:11620: de phyir dus gsum 'da' mi bya //
NK062(khu)001:11622: gnyis pa bla ma bkur ba la sum cu ste /
NK062(khu)001:11624: bla ma bkur ba sgo gsum gyis //
NK062(khu)001:11626: lus kyi sgo nas bkur ba bcu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11627: brdeg bsad la sogs 'thing slad tsam du'ang mi bya ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11628: 'dod yon lnga'i mchod pa rgyun du mi bcad pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11629: gsang ba'i snod du dug mi spyod pa ste yum la mi spyad pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11630: drang po'i phyogs nas 'gro ba spang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11631: gdan sa gdan sogs mi barlama pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11634: rgyan 'dogs gzi ldir spang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11635: ma rabs kyi spyod pa kun spangs shing spyod lam bag zon dang ldan par bya ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11636: bkur sti'i gnas su bya ba dang bcu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11638: lus kyi bkur ba brdeg bsad sogs //
NK062(khu)001:11639: 'thing slad tsam du'ang bya ba min 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11640: gsang ba'i snod du dug mi spyod //
NK062(khu)001:11641: 'gro ba drang po'i phyogs spang dang //
NK062(khu)001:11642: gdan sa gdan sogs mi barlama dang //
NK062(khu)001:11644: rgyan 'dogs gzi ldir de bzhin te //
NK062(khu)001:11645: ma rabs spyod pa kun spangs la //
NK062(khu)001:11646: spyod lam zon chags bsti gnas bya //
NK062(khu)001:11648: ngag gi sgo nas bkur ba bcu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11655: lkog tu tshul ngan pa brjod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11656: ca co la sogs pa mi smra ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11657: skyon spangs shing yon tan brjod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11658: snyan par smra ba dang bcu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11660: rdzun dang phra ma tshig rtsub dang //
NK062(khu)001:11661: 'khyal pa nam yang mi bya ste //
NK062(khu)001:11662: be bogs ma yin rdabs skad dor //
NK062(khu)001:11663: lkog tu tshul brjod nyams par 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11664: yon tan brjod cing snyan par smra //
NK062(khu)001:11665: ca co la sogs ma yin par //
NK062(khu)001:11666: sangs rgyas rdo rjes gsung thos 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11668: sems kyi sgo nas bkur ba bcu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11669: bla ma'i rdzas la brkam zhing yum la chags pa ste 'dod chags dang /
NK062(khu)001:11670: bla ma dang bla ma'i 'khor gyi skyon la mnar sems pa ste zhe sdang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11671: yon tan la rmongs pa ste gti mug dang /
NK062(khu)001:11672: rang che'o snyam pa la sogs pa'i dregs pa ste nga rgyal dang /
NK062(khu)001:11673: bla ma'i phun sum tshogs pa phrag tu mi shong ba ste phrag dog dang /
NK062(khu)001:11674: ngan du sems pa rnams spang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11675: bla ma'i gsung gnyan cing lci bar sems pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11676: pha ma ltar sems pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11677: yi dam ltar sems pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11678: dus rtag tu gdung ba'i sems rgyun mi bcad pa dang bcu ste /
NK062(khu)001:11679: dril bas bla ma bkur tshul sum cu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11681: dam pa ston pa'i bla ma la //
NK062(khu)001:11682: chags dang gti mug nga rgyal dang //
NK062(khu)001:11683: phrag dog dug lnga'i sems mi bya //
NK062(khu)001:11684: ngan du mi sems lci bar sems //
NK062(khu)001:11685: pha ma yi dam 'dra bar sems //
NK062(khu)001:11686: rtag tu gdung ba rgyun mi gcad //
NK062(khu)001:11688: gsum pa sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad pa la sum cu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11689: phyogs mtshams bcing pa 'bar ba mtshams kyi sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:11690: rten dbang chen skyed pa'i sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:11691: gzhal yas khang skyed pa'i sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:11692: brten pa lha skyed pa la rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags dang /
NK062(khu)001:11693: skyed pa rkyen gyi sngags dang lnga /
NK062(khu)001:11694: bsnyen pa las bzhi'i sngags re rer bgrangs bas dgu /
NK062(khu)001:11701: mchod pa 'bul ba'i sngags dang bcu drug /
NK062(khu)001:11702: zhi khro gnyis po re re la yang dam tshig
NK062(khu)001:11703: dam las dang chos dang sku phyag rgya chen po
NK062(khu)001:11704: ste / de yang dam tshig gi phyag rgya la bca' ba dang bsam pa gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:11705: las kyi phyag rgya la'ang bca' ba dang bsam pa gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:11706: chos kyi phyag rgya la'ang bca' ba dang bsam pa gnyis so //
NK062(khu)001:11707: de ltar zhi khro gnyis la phyag rgya bdun bdun
NK062(khu)001:11708: te bcu bzhi'i steng du gong gi sngags bcu drug
NK062(khu)001:11709: bsnan pa ste / dril bas sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad pa sum cu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11711: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK062(khu)001:11712: zhi khro phyag rgya bdun gnyis gcig /
NK062(khu)001:11713: phyogs bcing rten dang khang pa'i sngags //
NK062(khu)001:11714: rtsa ba bskyed bsnyen las bzhi'i sngags //
NK062(khu)001:11715: dbang bskur byin bsdu'i gsang sngags dang //
NK062(khu)001:11716: spyan drangs bstim brtan phyag 'tshal mchod //
NK062(khu)001:11717: dus gsum rgyun du bzhi yi phyir //
NK062(khu)001:11718: nam yang rgyun cad yongs mi bya //
NK062(khu)001:11720: bzhi pa yang dag pa'i lam la zhugs pa'i mched la byams pa sum cu la /
NK062(khu)001:11721: lus kyi sgo nas bsrung ba bcu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11722: mtshon dbyug la sogs pas bsnun pa ste brdeg par mi bya ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11723: zas nor ma byin par mi blang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11724: mched kyis ma gnang bar gzungs ma la mi spyad pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11725: lta spyod mtho ba'i gong mi gcad pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11726: dbang thob pa snga ba dang rdzogs pa gong du bkur ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11727: dam tshig thob pa snga zhing bsrung ba la gus par bya ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11728: mched dang 'gal ba'i spyod lam kun la 'dzem bag bskyed pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11731: dus kun tu dga' zhing spro bar bya ba dang bcu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11733: yang dag lam du zhugs pa'i grogs //
NK062(khu)001:11734: bsnun dang ma byin blang mi bya //
NK062(khu)001:11735: zla zer ma yin gzungs mi spyad //
NK062(khu)001:11736: lta spyod mtho ba'i gong mi gcad //
NK062(khu)001:11737: dbang dang dam tshig de bzhin te //
NK062(khu)001:11738: kun tu ya bag zon 'grig can //
NK062(khu)001:11739: bkur sti mchod byed dga' bar spyod //
NK062(khu)001:11741: ngag gi sgo nas bsrung ba bcu ni //
NK062(khu)001:11746: dpag pa mi smra ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11747: ngan pa'i tshul mi brjod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11749: zhe sa dang bcas pas smra ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11751: ci smra yang bden pa'i tshig gi sri zhu'i sgra dang bcas te smra ba dang bcu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11752: rdzun sogs rnam bzhi spang ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:11753: dpag pa mi smra tshul mi brjod //
NK062(khu)001:11754: snyan smra zhe sa gsong por smra //
NK062(khu)001:11755: bden tshig sri zhu'i sgra byed pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:11757: sems kyi sgo nas bsrung ba bcu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11762: phrag dog gis kun nas blangs pa'i sems dang /
NK062(khu)001:11765: gnod sems rnams spang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:11767: gdung sems rgyun mi bcad pa dang bcu ste /
NK062(khu)001:11768: dril bas mched la bkur tshul sum cu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11770: sems kyi sngon bzhin dug lnga dor //
NK062(khu)001:11771: rngan dang dpag sems spang ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:11772: mig 'drar lta zhing gdung bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:11773: gnod sems spang dang rnam bcu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11775: lnga pa gsang ba'i don phyir mi smra ba la sum cu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11776: lta ba dang spyod pa zab mo dang gcig /
NK062(khu)001:11777: yi dam gyi lha dang gsang mtshan dang gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:11779: grub rtags dang bzhi ste spyir gsang bzhi dang /
NK062(khu)001:11783: rdzas dang bar gsang bzhi ste brgyad /
NK062(khu)001:11785: gsang bar gnyer gtan pa dang gnyis te bcu po
NK062(khu)001:11786: de dag gzhir byas nas yongs su ma smin pa
NK062(khu)001:11787: rnams la sems kyi bstan par mi bsam pa bcu
NK062(khu)001:11788: dang / ngag gi tshig tu mi brjod pa bcu dang /
NK062(khu)001:11789: lus kyi brdas mi mtshon pa bcu ste /
NK062(khu)001:11790: dril bas gsang ba mi bsgrag pa sum cu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11792: gsang ba'i phyir na mi smra ba //
NK062(khu)001:11793: spyi dang bar gsang bzhi bzhi dang //
NK062(khu)001:11794: 'os dang gnyer gtad rnam pa bcu //
NK062(khu)001:11795: sems kyi bstan par mi bsam zhing //
NK062(khu)001:11796: ngag gi brjod par yongs mi bya //
NK062(khu)001:11797: lus brdas bstan min sum cu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11799: de ltar sum cu pa phrag lnga la brgya lnga bcu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11800: de'i steng du gong gi spyir gsang bcu po bsnan pas brgya drug cu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11801: rtsa ba'i dam tshig gi bsrung dmigs so //
NK062(khu)001:11802: yan lag dam tshig lnga gnyis la //
NK062(khu)001:11804: yan lag gi dam tshig mi spang ba dang mi dor ba lnga tshan gnyis te bcu po la /
NK062(khu)001:11805: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su dbye //
NK062(khu)001:11807: gcig ni re re la'ang thabs dang shes rab gnyis
NK062(khu)001:11808: kyi sgo nas bcu phrag gnyis gnyis su ste nyis
NK062(khu)001:11811: mi spang lnga la bcu gnyis te //
NK062(khu)001:11813: dang po mi spang ba'i dam tshig lnga po re re la'ang nyi shu nyi shur dbye ste /
NK062(khu)001:11814: dang po zhe sdang gi nyi shu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11815: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu thabs kyi mdzad spyod kyi dngos su 'joms pa bcu dang /
NK062(khu)001:11816: shes rab lta bas rang bzhin med par shes nas
NK062(khu)001:11817: skye med kyi ngang du sgrol ba bcu ste nyi
NK062(khu)001:11819: zhing bcu thabs kyi mdzad pas 'joms //
NK062(khu)001:11820: shes rab rang bzhin med par sgrol //
NK062(khu)001:11821: thabs dang shes rab zhe sdang gis //
NK062(khu)001:11822: bdag gzhan don rnams rdzogs par byed //
NK062(khu)001:11824: gti mug gi nyi shu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11825: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu la thabs kyi mdzad
NK062(khu)001:11826: spyodakyi spang blang du mi 'byed par spyod pa bcu
NK062(khu)001:11827: dang / shes rab lta bas spang blang du mi 'byed pa bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11829: yan lag bcu yi dam tshig la //
NK062(khu)001:11830: thabs kyi mdzad pas mi 'byed cing //
NK062(khu)001:11831: shes rab gnyis med mi 'byed pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:11832: gti mug bcu gnyis 'da' mi bya //
NK062(khu)001:11834: nga rgyal gyi nyi shu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11835: gti mug gi dam tshig nyi shu las /
NK062(khu)001:11836: lhag par lta spyod shin tu brtan cing gdeng du gyur pa nyi shu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11838: de ltar thabs dang shes rab bcu //
NK062(khu)001:11839: gnyis ni gdeng du gyur pa yi //
NK062(khu)001:11840: lhag pa'i nga rgyal mi 'da' ba //
NK062(khu)001:11841: nga rgyal chen po'i dam tshig go //
NK062(khu)001:11843: zhing bcu la chags pas thugs rje mi gtong zhing yang dag pa'i sa la sbyor ba bcu /
NK062(khu)001:11844: rigs lnga'i yum la thabs kyis rol pa lnga ste bco lnga /
NK062(khu)001:11845: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor ba dang bcu drug /
NK062(khu)001:11846: thabs kyi sbyor ba dang bcu bdun /
NK062(khu)001:11847: dbang po dus kyi sbyor ba dang bco brgyad /
NK062(khu)001:11848: rang bzhin gyi thabs shes rab gnyis su med par sbyor ba dang bcu dgu /
NK062(khu)001:11849: shes rab lta ba'i don dang 'du 'bra la med par spyor ba dang nyi shu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11851: zhing bcu thugs rjes mi gtong zhing //
NK062(khu)001:11852: rig lnga'i yum la thabs kyi rol //
NK062(khu)001:11853: ting 'dzin thabs dbang rang bzhin sbyor //
NK062(khu)001:11856: phrag dog gi nyi shu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11857: ma rtogs pa phyal ba pa dang rgyang 'phen pa gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:11858: log par rtogs pa mu stegs rtag par lta ba dang chad par lta ba gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:11859: theg chung nyan thos dang rang rgyal gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:11860: theg chen byang chub sems dpa' dang sngags phyi rgyud
NK062(khu)001:11861: kyi theg pa kri ya u pa yo ga gsum
NK062(khu)001:11862: ste bcu po de rnam kyi lta spyod thabs kyi
NK062(khu)001:11863: spyod pa'i klong du mi chud pa bcu dang /
NK062(khu)001:11864: shes rab lta ba'i gor mi chud pa ste nyi shu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11866: ma rtogs gnyis dang log rtog gnyis //
NK062(khu)001:11867: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems //
NK062(khu)001:11868: gsang sngags phyi yi theg pa gsum //
NK062(khu)001:11869: gsang sgor mdzad pa mi chud cing //
NK062(khu)001:11870: shes rab ngan pas mi chud pa //
NK062(khu)001:11871: phrag dog chen po'i dam tshig go //
NK062(khu)001:11874: dang du blang ba'i dang grub rdzas //
NK062(khu)001:11875: sgrub rdzas rnam lnga'ang rtsa ba brgyad //
NK062(khu)001:11876: brgyad cha re zhing dwangs snyigs gnyis //
NK062(khu)001:11877: re re'ang rnam pa bcu ru 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:11878: zhing bcu'i bdud rtsi de bzhin pas //
NK062(khu)001:11879: rnam par dbye ba nyi shu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11880: bdag gzhan rang zhing dang ni gnyis //
NK062(khu)001:11881: rdzas bcu thabs spyod shes rab spyod //
NK062(khu)001:11882: bcu bcu nyi shur 'gyur ba'ang rigs //
NK062(khu)001:11884: mi dor ba'i dam tshig lnga po re re la yang nyi shu nyi shur dbye ste /
NK062(khu)001:11885: de yang byang sems kyi nyi shu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11886: byang sems mthar phyin pa mig /
NK062(khu)001:11887: chu rgyus mthar phyin pa sen mo //
NK062(khu)001:11888: khrag dang chu ser mthar phyin pa skra /
NK062(khu)001:11889: rus pa mthar phyin pa so ste mngon pa phyi'i bzhi dang /
NK062(khu)001:11892: gshegs bshul rdo rje chu ba /
NK062(khu)001:11893: pho brang snying rnams ni sbas pa nang gi bzhi ste brgyad dang /
NK062(khu)001:11894: de rnams la phyi nang gi dwangs snyigs gnyis te bcu /
NK062(khu)001:11895: zhing bcu'i byang sems la bcur phye bas nyi shu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11896: dri chen gyi nyi shu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11900: byis pa gtsang ma'i dri chen te mngon pa phyi'i bzhi dang /
NK062(khu)001:11904: bsgral pa'i dri chen rnams ni sbas pa nang gi bzhi ste brgyad dang /
NK062(khu)001:11906: zhing bcu'i dri chen dang nyi shu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11911: gshegs lam mkha' ma'i rtsa khrag ste mngon pa phyi'i bzhi dang /
NK062(khu)001:11912: gzungs ma la dang po 'dzag pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:11914: sbyar ba la 'dren pa'i khrag dang /
NK062(khu)001:11915: rgyud lnga bsgral ba'i khrag rnams ni sbas pa nang gi bzhi ste brgyad /
NK062(khu)001:11917: zhing bcu bsgral ba'i khrag bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11922: skye bo'i dri chu ste mngon pa phyi'i bzhi dang /
NK062(khu)001:11926: shi ba bam gyi dri chu rnams ni sbas pa nang gi bzhi ste brgyad dang /
NK062(khu)001:11928: zhing bcu'i dri chu dang nyi shu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11929: sha chen gyi nyi shu ni /
NK062(khu)001:11930: mngon pa phyi'i bzhi ni nu 'bur gnyis /
NK062(khu)001:11932: sbas pa nang gi bzhi ste brgyad /
NK062(khu)001:11934: zhing bcu bsgral ba'i sha chen bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK062(khu)001:11935: de ltar mi dor ba'i dam tshig lnga po la nyi shu nyi shur phye bas brgya /
NK062(khu)001:11936: de'i steng du gong gi mi spang ba'i dam tshig
NK062(khu)001:11937: lnga po la nyi shu nyi shur phye ba bsnan
NK062(khu)001:11938: pas nyis brgya po de rnams ni yan lag gi
NK062(khu)001:11940: mdor na rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig gi bsrung mtshams kyi rnam grangs ni /
NK062(khu)001:11941: rtsa ba'i dam tshig la brgya drug cu dang yan
NK062(khu)001:11942: lag gi dam tshig la nyis brgya ste sum brgya
NK062(khu)001:11944: rgyud gzhung 'di nyid kyi dbang du yin gyis gzhan du ni nges pa med par shes par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:11945: gnyis pa gdul bya la dgongs nas dbye ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:11946: dam tshig 'di ni de snyed spro //
NK062(khu)001:11948: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che //
NK062(khu)001:11950: theg pa chen po gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK062(khu)001:11951: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig 'di dag
NK062(khu)001:11952: ni 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i rgyal khrims chags
NK062(khu)001:11954: de yang rgya chad med par gdul bya'i blo dang
NK062(khu)001:11955: 'tshams par ji ltar 'dul ba'i thabs sna tshogs ston
NK062(khu)001:11956: pas na rmad po che zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:11957: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK062(khu)001:11958: srid gsum 'gro ba ji snyed pa //
NK062(khu)001:11959: rtog 'dul dam tshig de snyed spros //
NK062(khu)001:11961: de yang gnas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na
NK062(khu)001:11962: gnas pa'i gdul bya srid pa khams gsum gyis bsdus
NK062(khu)001:11963: pa'i 'gro ba sems can ji snyed gcig yod pa
NK062(khu)001:11964: de dag gi rnam par rtog pa ji snyed pa
NK062(khu)001:11965: 'dul ba'i gnyen por dam tshig gi rnam grangs kyang
NK062(khu)001:11969: ngo shes pas 'dul ba la sogs pa 'dul thabs
NK062(khu)001:11970: kyi bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa de snyed
NK062(khu)001:11971: cig spros nas sems can gyi don mdzad do //
NK062(khu)001:11972: bdun pa dam tshig gi yon tan bstan pa la drug ste /
NK062(khu)001:11973: mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob cing tshad las 'das pa'i yon tan dang /
NK062(khu)001:11974: rig 'dzin thob cing 'jig rten gyi gtso bos bkur 'os su mthong ba'i yon tan dang /
NK062(khu)001:11975: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpas byin gyis rlobs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK062(khu)001:11976: kun tu bzang po dang spyod yul gcig pa'i yon tan dang /
NK062(khu)001:11977: theg pa 'og ma'i 'dul sdom thams cad 'dir 'dus shing rnam par dag pa'i yon tan dang /
NK062(khu)001:11978: nyams kyang bskang du rung ba'i yon tan la sogs te yon tan tshad las 'das par bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:11979: dang po mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob cing tshad las 'das pa'i yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:11980: gzhan yang rgyal mchog mtha' yas mchog /
NK062(khu)001:11982: gzhan yang rgyal mchog kun bzang gi //
NK062(khu)001:11984: gong du bshad pa'i mnyam rdzogs chen po cig car
NK062(khu)001:11985: ba'i dam tshig las gzhan pa rim gyis pa'i yang
NK062(khu)001:11986: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams par
NK062(khu)001:11987: bsrungs pa'i 'bras bu rgyal ba kun gyi mchog rigs
NK062(khu)001:11988: thams cad kyi bdag po kun tu bzang po nyid
NK062(khu)001:11990: de dag gi ngo bo nyid ji ltar zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:11991: thams cad ma lus phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK062(khu)001:11993: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad dang mya ngan las 'das
NK062(khu)001:11994: pa'i chos lhag ma ma lus pa rgyal ba'i sku
NK062(khu)001:11995: gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'i ngo bor ye nas lhun
NK062(khu)001:11996: gyis grub pas na mchog ces bya ste /
NK062(khu)001:11997: bsgrub med dam pa ma lus 'grub //
NK062(khu)001:11999: de las gzhan pa'i 'bras bu bsgrub tu med de /
NK062(khu)001:12000: spang pa dang blang ba med pa ni 'bras bu'i
NK062(khu)001:12001: mchog dam pa ste kun tu bzang po'i yon tan
NK062(khu)001:12003: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK062(khu)001:12005: kun tu bzang po de'i yon tan brjod pa las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:12006: de la sogs pa'i yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab
NK062(khu)001:12007: cing brjod kyis mi lang bas na mtha' yas pa'i
NK062(khu)001:12008: mchog go // gnyis pa rig 'dzin thob cing 'jig
NK062(khu)001:12009: rten gyi gtso bos bkur 'os su mthong ba'i yon
NK062(khu)001:12010: mchog go // tan ni / rgyal ba rigs mchog 'khor gyis bkur //
NK062(khu)001:12012: rgyal ba rigs mchog 'dzin pa ste //
NK062(khu)001:12014: de lta bu'i dam tshig rnams dang ldan na /
NK062(khu)001:12015: sngar 'das pa dang da ltar bzhugs pa'i rgyal pa'i rigs kyi mchog 'dzin pa yin te /
NK062(khu)001:12016: de yang dam tshig 'di dag lta spyod tshang bar 'byor ba ni sar chud pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK062(khu)001:12017: de la rgyun du gnas pa ni sa la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK062(khu)001:12018: de stobs su gyur pa ni sar yongs su smin pa'i rig 'dzin yin no //
NK062(khu)001:12021: de lta bu'i rig 'dzin sgrub pa po de la
NK062(khu)001:12022: 'jig rten gyi gtso bo lha ma srin sde brgyad
NK062(khu)001:12023: dang de dag gi 'khor g.yog dang bcas pa kun
NK062(khu)001:12024: gyis kyang bskur sti byed cing de'i dgos pa sgrub
NK062(khu)001:12025: par byed do // gsum pa sangs rgyas dang byang
NK062(khu)001:12026: chub sems dpas byin gyis rlob pa'i yon tan ni
NK062(khu)001:12027: par byed do // / dam pa'i mchog dang byin gyis rlob //
NK062(khu)001:12029: dam pa'i mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK062(khu)001:12031: dam pa'i mchog sangs rgyas dang /
NK062(khu)001:12032: dam pa rig 'dzin dang byang chub sems dpa' ste de dag gi yis kyang /
NK062(khu)001:12033: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis rlob //
NK062(khu)001:12035: sangs rgyas rnams kyi sras dang rig 'dzin dang byang
NK062(khu)001:12036: chub sems dpa' rnams kyis spun du dgongs shing byin
NK062(khu)001:12037: gyis rlob bo // 'di na med kyang lung gra
NK062(khu)001:12038: chad la nyal ba blang ba bshad pa mkhan po'i
NK062(khu)001:12040: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams kyis ming por dgongs nas stong grogs byed do //
NK062(khu)001:12041: dam can chos skyong pa'i srung ma rnams kyis kyang
NK062(khu)001:12042: rje dpon dam par dgongs nas phrin las bsgrub bo
NK062(khu)001:12043: // zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsum ngo //
NK062(khu)001:12044: bzhi pa kun tu bzang po dang spyod yul gcig pa'i yon tan ni /
NK062(khu)001:12045: bde gshegs nyid kyi bzang por sbyor //
NK062(khu)001:12047: bde gshegs nyid kyi yul la zhugs //
NK062(khu)001:12049: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi bco lnga po la
NK062(khu)001:12050: sogs pa gzhung bzhin du ma nyams par bsrungs pa
NK062(khu)001:12051: de ni bde bar gshegs pa nyid kyi ngo bo
NK062(khu)001:12052: dang tha mid pas byed spyod thams cad kyang de
NK062(khu)001:12053: bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul la zhugs pa zhes bya'o
NK062(khu)001:12054: // 'jigs med kun tu bzang po sbyor //
NK062(khu)001:12056: de'i phyir dam tshig dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK062(khu)001:12057: byed spyod gang spyad kyang ltung bar 'gyur ba'i 'jigs
NK062(khu)001:12058: pa med pas / spyod yul yongs su dag pa kun tu bzang por sbyor pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12059: lnga pa theg pa 'og ma'i 'dul sdom thams cad
NK062(khu)001:12060: 'dir 'dus shing rnam par dag pa'i yon tan ni
NK062(khu)001:12061: / ji bzhin nyid dang lhun gyis grub //
NK062(khu)001:12063: ji bzhin nyid dang 'dul ba'i thabs //
NK062(khu)001:12065: chos thams cad kyi ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid mngon
NK062(khu)001:12066: du byed pa gsang sngags bla na med pa'i dam
NK062(khu)001:12067: tshig phan yon dang bcas pa 'di thun mong gi
NK062(khu)001:12068: gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs su bstan pa'i /
NK062(khu)001:12069: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK062(khu)001:12071: nyan thos kyis 'dul khrims ji snyed pa dang byang
NK062(khu)001:12072: chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang sngags phyi rgyud kyi
NK062(khu)001:12073: dam tshig la sogs pa bsam yas pa rnams 'dus
NK062(khu)001:12074: pa'i phyir / ma lus rnam dag lhun gyis grub //
NK062(khu)001:12076: 'dir rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams na /
NK062(khu)001:12077: theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyi dgag bya ma lus pa rnam par dag cing /
NK062(khu)001:12078: dgos pa ma lus pa ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12079: drug pa nyams kyang bskang rung pa'i yon tan la
NK062(khu)001:12080: sogs te yon tan tshad las 'das par bstan pa
NK062(khu)001:12081: ni / nyams na bskang pas mtha' yas mchog /
NK062(khu)001:12083: nyams na bskang pas rdzogs pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:12085: gal te sngags kyi dam tshig nyams par gyur na
NK062(khu)001:12086: yang nyan rang ltar bskang thabs med pa ma yin
NK062(khu)001:12087: te / bskang pas skong pa'i thabs khyad par can
NK062(khu)001:12088: yod pas nyams pa gso ba la rab tu brtson
NK062(khu)001:12089: na dam tshig gi yon tan thams cad yongs su
NK062(khu)001:12091: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK062(khu)001:12093: gong gi yon tan de la sogs pa dam tshig
NK062(khu)001:12094: bsrungs ba'i yon tan tshad las 'das shing mtha' yas
NK062(khu)001:12096: de yang dam tshig nyams pa rnams gso ba'i thabs ni /
NK062(khu)001:12098: nyams na bskang ba'i thabs rnams ni //
NK062(khu)001:12099: byang chub sems kyis dam nyams na //
NK062(khu)001:12100: mkhas la blangs te gnas par bya //
NK062(khu)001:12101: sku yi dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:12102: gang la nyams pa der song nas //
NK062(khu)001:12103: nor rdzas 'byor bas mnyes phul nas //
NK062(khu)001:12104: gang zhes tshig tu bshags byas la //
NK062(khu)001:12105: phyin chad sdom pa legs pa bcang //
NK062(khu)001:12106: gal te grongs chad gyur pa na //
NK062(khu)001:12107: de yi slob dpon bzhugs pa la //
NK062(khu)001:12108: de tshe gong ma bzhin du bshags //
NK062(khu)001:12109: med na mnyam pa brgya la bshags //
NK062(khu)001:12110: de yang rnyed bar ma gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:12111: de dang mnyam pa gsum bkug la //
NK062(khu)001:12112: byin sreg me thab rab brtsigs nas //
NK062(khu)001:12113: dkyil 'khor lha la mchod rjes su //
NK062(khu)001:12114: spyan drangs gsang mtshan la sogs mchod //
NK062(khu)001:12115: gong du smos pa'i yod byad rnams //
NK062(khu)001:12116: dbang po gsum la dbul bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:12117: gal te gus pas mi len na //
NK062(khu)001:12118: gnyis ka rdo rje dmyal bar ltung //
NK062(khu)001:12119: de bas myur du tshang bar bya //
NK062(khu)001:12120: gsung gi dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:12121: sgo gsum sku gsung thugs nyid du //
NK062(khu)001:12122: nges par shes na skong bar 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:12123: bzlas pa lngab kyi bsab pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:12124: sgrub pa chen po gsum gyis skong //
NK062(khu)001:12125: thugs kyi dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:12126: 'gro drug sems su gsal rtogs na //
NK062(khu)001:12127: bdag nyid bdag la gsang ba med //
NK062(khu)001:12128: mi rtog ting 'dzin rlung zhugs te //
NK062(khu)001:12130: yan lag dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK062(khu)001:12131: gang nyams de ni gsor bcug la //
NK062(khu)001:12132: brgya rtsa brgyad kyi tshogs kyis bskang //
NK062(khu)001:12133: de ltar nyams su long la skong //
NK062(khu)001:12136: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig nyams na rdo rje'i dmyal
NK062(khu)001:12137: bar skye bas de'i sdug bsngal bsams te shin tu
NK062(khu)001:12138: 'jigs par byas la dam tshig nyams pa skong ba'i
NK062(khu)001:12139: cho ga la shin tu brtson par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:12140: gnyis pa gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12143: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la 'dul bar gyur to //
NK062(khu)001:12145: zhes le'u'i gzhung don de dag brjod pas dam tshig gi rang bzhin ni /
NK062(khu)001:12146: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK062(khu)001:12147: rgyal ba de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyang dam tshig gi rang bzhin las mi 'da' la /
NK062(khu)001:12148: gdul bya gzhan dam tshig gi 'dul bar gyur ba lta ci smos zhes pa'i don no //
NK062(khu)001:12149: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12150: gsang ba'i snying po bcu dgu pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12152: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK062(khu)001:12154: gsang ba'i zhes rtogs dka' ba /
NK062(khu)001:12156: de kho na nyid gzhan sel pa /
NK062(khu)001:12157: nges pa the tshom dang bral ba /
NK062(khu)001:12158: las zhes pa de mtshan gyi gzhir gda' /
NK062(khu)001:12159: dam tshig gi le'u ste bcu dgu pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12161: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig gi rnam
NK062(khu)001:12162: par gzhag pa bstan pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams
NK062(khu)001:12163: tshoms dang ris su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed
NK062(khu)001:12164: pa'i don gyis na le'u ste de'i grangs nyi shu
NK062(khu)001:12165: rtsa gnyis su yod pa las yas bgrangs bcu dgu
NK062(khu)001:12167: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK062(khu)001:12168: rgyud kyi 'grel bshad rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i
NK062(khu)001:12169: sgron me yid bzhin gyi nor bu zhes bya ba
NK062(khu)001:12170: las le'u bcu dgu pa'i gzhung don rnam par bshad
NK062(khu)001:12172: da ni le'u nyi shu pa 'chad par byed pa 'di la /
NK062(khu)001:12173: chos tshoms ngos bzung ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK062(khu)001:12174: blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam ston /
NK062(khu)001:12175: lam la thabs lam grol lam gnyis las gnyis ka ston /
NK062(khu)001:12176: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston /
NK062(khu)001:12177: mtshan nyid gsum las rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ston /
NK062(khu)001:12178: snang ba bzhi las lam snang ston /
NK062(khu)001:12179: blo 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don ston /
NK062(khu)001:12180: de la bcu las gzhung hril bos phrin las ston /
NK062(khu)001:12184: dug gsum gyi mchod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12185: phrin las bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin ston /
NK062(khu)001:12186: blo tha ma'i chos tshoms bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu las rang bzhin lta ba /
NK062(khu)001:12189: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK062(khu)001:12190: de lta ston par byed pa'i le'u nyi shu ba 'di la don gsum ste /
NK062(khu)001:12191: gsungs pa lo rgyus su barjooda pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12194: dang po gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12195: de nas de bzhin 'di brjod do //
NK062(khu)001:12197: de nas zhes pas le'u bcu dgu par dam tshig
NK062(khu)001:12198: bstan pa la de nyi shu par dam tshig dang
NK062(khu)001:12199: ldan pa'i sgrub pa pos phrin las bya ba ston
NK062(khu)001:12200: pas na nas / de bzhin gshegs pa bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po ni /
NK062(khu)001:12202: lhun gyis grub pa'i dam tshig byin gyis rlob pa
NK062(khu)001:12203: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK062(khu)001:12204: nas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK062(khu)001:12206: byang chub sems nyid la phrin las rnam pa bzhi
NK062(khu)001:12207: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub par gnas pa las mi
NK062(khu)001:12208: 'da' ba'i dam tshig de cho ga bzhis bskul bas
NK062(khu)001:12209: mngon sum du snang bar byed pas na byin gyis
NK062(khu)001:12210: rlob pa zhes bya ba'i dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin
NK062(khu)001:12211: la mngon du bzhag pa ste snyoms par zhugs nas
NK062(khu)001:12212: / 'og nas 'byung ba'i don ched du brjod pa 'di dag brjod do //
NK062(khu)001:12213: gnyis pa le'u'i gzhung la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:12215: phrin las kyi yon tan no //
NK062(khu)001:12216: dang po phrin las dngos la bzhi ste /
NK062(khu)001:12217: rdzas dang lu gu rgyud kyi sgo nas phrin las bya ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:12219: bro gar glu tshig gi yon tan dang /
NK062(khu)001:12221: dang po rdzas dang lu gu rgyud kyi sgo nas phrin las bya ba la bzhi ste /
NK062(khu)001:12226: dang po drag po'i phrin las la'ang lnga ste /
NK062(khu)001:12227: drag po'i lid+ga bca' ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:12228: drag po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12229: drag po'i bsgrub bya'i las dang /
NK062(khu)001:12230: mchod sbyin bya ba yon tan dang bcas pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12231: lu gu rgyud kyi yon tan dang cas pa bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12232: dang po drag po'i ling+ga bca' ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:12233: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK062(khu)001:12234: mtshan ma ming du bcas par bya //
NK062(khu)001:12239: sngags 'chang drag po'i cha byad can gyi kha byang
NK062(khu)001:12240: du phyogs nas khros pa'i sems kyi rang gi grib
NK062(khu)001:12241: ma dang kha chus mi 'gos shing grib ma mi
NK062(khu)001:12242: 'phog pa'i thabs dang ldan par byas la /
NK062(khu)001:12243: dgra bgegs gang yin gyi bdud rtsi lnga'am yang na
NK062(khu)001:12244: sha gang gi nya sha bu ram sbrang rtsi til
NK062(khu)001:12245: dang zas lnga la rgyu byas pa'i lid+ga pho mo
NK062(khu)001:12246: gang yin gyi mtshan ma can /
NK062(khu)001:12247: dpral bar rus dang snying khar srog gang yin ming du bcas par bya ste /
NK062(khu)001:12248: de yang gro shog la bris nas rlan pa'am /
NK062(khu)001:12249: yang na gro shog gi lid+ga la rjes kyi sa'am
NK062(khu)001:12250: zag rdzas rnams kyis byugs pa yang rung bas lte
NK062(khu)001:12252: 'doms su ch+gee mo m+aa ra ya phata bya ba bris /
NK062(khu)001:12253: mtha' ma dzahs bskor la thod pa mtshan ngan gyi
NK062(khu)001:12254: nang du bcug la mgo bo lho nub dang rkang
NK062(khu)001:12255: pa byang shar du bstan te /
NK062(khu)001:12256: dkyil 'khor gyi byang phyogs kyi brub khung gru gsum du gzhug go //
NK062(khu)001:12257: gnyis pa drag po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12258: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK062(khu)001:12260: sngags 'chang rnams drag po'i cha byad dang 'dug stangs kyis /
NK062(khu)001:12262: dz+wa la ram la sogs pa'i sngags brjod pas /
NK062(khu)001:12263: phyi drag po e'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mthing nag gru gsum me 'bar ba bskyed la /
NK062(khu)001:12264: +amo badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK062(khu)001:12265: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK062(khu)001:12267: nang drag po lha'i tshogs badz+ra he ru kas gtso
NK062(khu)001:12268: byas pa'i khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kun kyang
NK062(khu)001:12270: mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs pa /
NK062(khu)001:12271: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa /
NK062(khu)001:12272: sprul pa dang yang sprul du bcas grangs med pa bskyed do //
NK062(khu)001:12273: gsum pa drag po'i bsgrub bya'i las ni /
NK062(khu)001:12274: bkug nas rdo rje phur pas gdab //
NK062(khu)001:12275: rdul du byas nas tshogs la 'bul //
NK062(khu)001:12277: de yang gu gul la sogs pa lha dbye'i rdzas
NK062(khu)001:12278: kyi dud pas ling+ga bdug cing 'go ba'i lha lnga
NK062(khu)001:12279: dang dbyer / de nas ba hu'i sngags kyis lha las la gzud /
NK062(khu)001:12280: pho nya drug skor btang la /
NK062(khu)001:12281: bi shwa badz+ra'i sngags kyis sprul pa spros nas gzas
NK062(khu)001:12282: pa po gang yin rang dbang med par mdun du
NK062(khu)001:12285: bgegs yin na tri dzahzhesa brjod cing /
NK062(khu)001:12286: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya lan gsum mam bdun gyis bkug nas /
NK062(khu)001:12287: dzahh+aumhbam hohs ling+ga dang gnyis su med pa byas la /
NK062(khu)001:12288: lcags sam shing nag po la byas pa'i rdo rje phur pa mgo la rgya mdud dang /
NK062(khu)001:12289: dbal zur gsum pa gsum brub khung gi zur gsum
NK062(khu)001:12290: la bskor ba der sras mchog badz+ra k+ai la ya
NK062(khu)001:12292: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab pa la sogs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12293: lag sor byin gyis brlab pa la sogs pa byas nas /
NK062(khu)001:12294: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u lnga bcu rtsa bdun pa nas byung ba'i phur bskul gyi tshig dang /
NK062(khu)001:12295: g+ha ta'i sngags kyis ling+ga'i dpral mgrin snying ga ste
NK062(khu)001:12296: lus ngag yid gsum gyi gnas gsum du gdab bar
NK062(khu)001:12297: bya'o // de nas sh+aish+ti'i sngags kyis gris gtubs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12298: +amo b+h+rum la sogs pa'i sngags kyis tshon cha'i char phab pas /
NK062(khu)001:12299: ling ro rnams rdul phra rab tsam du byas par bsams nas tsho gsum du byas la /
NK062(khu)001:12300: tsho gcig bstab zhal du blug la dkyil 'khor gyi lha rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK062(khu)001:12301: badz+ra he ru kas gtso byas pa'i drag po'i lha tshogs rnams la gtor mar dbul /
NK062(khu)001:12302: tsho gcig gtubs la sbyin sreg gi bsregs rdzas dang basre'o //
NK062(khu)001:12303: tsho gcig la bro brdungs lam rgya gram du dong
NK062(khu)001:12304: gru gsum brus la ro g.yam la ro sol gyis
NK062(khu)001:12305: rdo rje rgya gram bris la mnan par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:12306: bzhi pa mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12309: 'bar ba gtum chen rngam pa la //
NK062(khu)001:12311: bcom ldan 'das badz+ra he ru kas gtso byas pa'i
NK062(khu)001:12312: khrag 'thung 'bar ba drag po'i dkyil 'khor gtum chen
NK062(khu)001:12314: khros pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK062(khu)001:12316: stong gi sems rnal 'byor zhe sdang khros pa'i yid kyis ye shes kyi lha mchod cing /
NK062(khu)001:12317: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro la sbyin pa'i las byas pa'i yon tan ni /
NK062(khu)001:12318: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK062(khu)001:12320: sangs rgyas rnams kyi bsod nams kyi tshogs las grub pa'i gzugs sku gnyis kyang 'jig bar nus na /
NK062(khu)001:12321: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu la sogs pa brlag par nus pa lta smos kyang ci dgos so //
NK062(khu)001:12322: lnga pa lu gu rgyud kyi yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12325: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK062(khu)001:12328: phyi drag po'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba 'byams klas pa bskyed la /
NK062(khu)001:12329: +amo badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK062(khu)001:12330: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK062(khu)001:12332: badz+ra he ru kas gtso byas pa'i drag po khro
NK062(khu)001:12333: bo'i lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor khrag 'thung lnga bcu
NK062(khu)001:12334: rtsa brgyad mchog tu gsal ba'i sgrub pa po pho
NK062(khu)001:12335: mo rnams kyis bro ra gru gsum du byas pa'i
NK062(khu)001:12336: dbus su ling ro rnams bzhag cing /
NK062(khu)001:12337: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams nas //
NK062(khu)001:12339: lag pa g.yas pa steng dang g.yon pa 'og tu
NK062(khu)001:12340: byas nas bsnol nas mathe'u chung lu gu rgyud du
NK062(khu)001:12342: bcings 'gyur bskyod nas phyogs bcur g.yos //
NK062(khu)001:12344: de ltar lu gu rgyud kyi phyag rgya bcings te /
NK062(khu)001:12346: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas kyi //
NK062(khu)001:12347: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig dang /
NK062(khu)001:12348: sum+b+ha na'i sngags kyi bskul zhing mig 'gyur ba dang bcas pas rkang stabs bskyod nas bro brdungs pas /
NK062(khu)001:12349: rdo rje rigs kyi sprul pa mthing nag dpag tu med pa phyogs bcur g.yos nas /
NK062(khu)001:12350: gang la bya brdul du brlag par bsams la /
NK062(khu)001:12351: che ge mo m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK062(khu)001:12352: ces pa'i sngags brjod cing phyag rgya sprugs nas bshig pas /
NK062(khu)001:12354: zhes pas gzas pa po gang yin pa de'i rnam
NK062(khu)001:12355: shes myos nas lus gas te snying 'tshig par 'gyur
NK062(khu)001:12356: ro // gnyis pa dbang gi phrin las la yang lnga ste /
NK062(khu)001:12357: dbang gi lad+gi bcas pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12358: dbang gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:12359: dbang gi bsgrub bya'i las dang /
NK062(khu)001:12360: mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan dang /
NK062(khu)001:12361: lu gu rgyud kyi las yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12362: dang po dbang gi lid+ga bca' ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:12363: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK062(khu)001:12364: mtshan ma ming du bcas par bya //
NK062(khu)001:12366: de yang lid+ga'i rgyu bdud rtsi lnga'am yang na zas lnga la byas pa /
NK062(khu)001:12367: gang dbang du bya bar 'dod pa'i pho mo gang yin gyi mtshan ma can /
NK062(khu)001:12369: snying gar srog gang yin gyi mtha' ming gi yi
NK062(khu)001:12370: ges skor ba la sogs pa sngar bzhin du bcas
NK062(khu)001:12371: la / dkyil 'khor gyi nub tu brub khung zla gam du bcug la bzhag par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:12372: gnyis pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12373: bam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK062(khu)001:12375: sngags 'chang rnams dbang gi cha byad dang 'dug stangs kyis /
NK062(khu)001:12376: bam ram la sogs pa'i sngags brjod pas /
NK062(khu)001:12377: phyi dbang mchog bam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor zla gam me 'bar ba bskyed la /
NK062(khu)001:12378: +amo pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK062(khu)001:12379: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK062(khu)001:12381: nang dbang gi lha'i mchog pad+ma he ru kas gtso
NK062(khu)001:12382: byas pa'i khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kun kyang
NK062(khu)001:12383: dmar nag rngams pa'i gzugs can lcags kyu thogs pa
NK062(khu)001:12384: / me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa sprul
NK062(khu)001:12385: pa yang sprul dang bcas pa grangs med pa bskyed
NK062(khu)001:12386: / do // gsum pa dbang gi bsgrub bya'i las ni /
NK062(khu)001:12387: rdo rje chags pa'i phung pas gdab //
NK062(khu)001:12388: chags pa'i tshogs la thim par dbul //
NK062(khu)001:12390: de yang sngar bzhin bsgrub bya dgug gzhug bstim pa
NK062(khu)001:12391: la sogs pa'i lid+ga la zangs sam shing dmar po
NK062(khu)001:12392: la mgo la rgya mdud dang /
NK062(khu)001:12393: dbal zla gam du byas pa rdo rje chags pa
NK062(khu)001:12394: ste sras mchog pad+ma k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i phur
NK062(khu)001:12395: pa lnga brub khung gi kha khyer la bkod pa
NK062(khu)001:12396: rnams la / dbang bskur byin rlabs la sogs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12397: lag sor byin gyis brlabs pa la sogs pa byas
NK062(khu)001:12398: nas phur bskul gyi tshig dang g+ha ta ya'i sngags
NK062(khu)001:12399: kyi rjes la / che ge mo bdag gi dbang du bsdus shig /
NK062(khu)001:12400: p+aa sham ma na ye hoh zhes pa'i lid+ga'i dbang po lnga'i gnas su gdab cing chags pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:12401: dbang dkyil 'khor gyi lha snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK062(khu)001:12402: pad+ma he ru kas gtso byas pa'i dbang gi lha
NK062(khu)001:12403: tshogs rnams la sngar drag po'i skabs su bshad pa'i
NK062(khu)001:12404: cho ga rnam dang tshul mthun par thim par dbul
NK062(khu)001:12405: lo // bzhi pa mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12408: 'bar ba gzi brjid lhun chen la //
NK062(khu)001:12410: bcom ldan 'das pad+ma he ru kas gtso byas pa'i
NK062(khu)001:12411: khrag 'thung dbang gi dkyil 'khor gzi brjid lhun chen
NK062(khu)001:12412: lta bu dang ldan pa'i tshogs rnams la /
NK062(khu)001:12413: chags pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK062(khu)001:12415: stong gi sems rnal 'byor pa chags shing zhen pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan ni /
NK062(khu)001:12416: rdo rje gsung yang dbang du 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:12418: rdo rje gsung gi lha pad+ma dbang chen yang sgrub
NK062(khu)001:12419: pa po bdag gis dbang du 'dus par 'gyur na
NK062(khu)001:12420: bsgrub bya gzhan lta smos kyang ci dgos so //
NK062(khu)001:12421: lnga pa lu gu rgyud kyi las yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12424: bam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK062(khu)001:12425: zhes pas bam ram zhes brjod pas /
NK062(khu)001:12426: phyi dbang gi dkyil 'khor zla gam dmar nag 'bar ba 'byams klas pa bskyed la /
NK062(khu)001:12427: +amo pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK062(khu)001:12428: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK062(khu)001:12429: zhes pas pad+ma he ru kas gtso byas pa'i dbang
NK062(khu)001:12430: gi khro bo'i lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor khrag 'thung
NK062(khu)001:12431: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad mchog tu gsal ba'i sgrub pa
NK062(khu)001:12433: bro ra zla gam du bcas pa'i dbus su ling ro rnams bzhag cing /
NK062(khu)001:12434: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams nas //
NK062(khu)001:12436: lag pa sngar ltar bsnol ba'i srin lag lu gu rgyud du sbrel cing bsdams nas /
NK062(khu)001:12439: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig dang sum b+ha ni'i ni sngags kyi bskul zhing /
NK062(khu)001:12441: pad+ma rigs kyi sprul pa dmar nag dpag tu med pa rnams kyi gang la bya ba /
NK062(khu)001:12442: sgrub po po'i dbang du bsdus par bsams la /
NK062(khu)001:12443: bsgrub bya che ge mo bdag gi dbang du gyur cig /
NK062(khu)001:12444: p+aa sham ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK062(khu)001:12445: zhes pa'i sngags brjod cing phyag rgya sprugs nas shig pas /
NK062(khu)001:12448: zhes pas bdag la mi mos pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12449: mi mdza' ba rnams 'gug par 'gyur ba lta smos kyang ci dgos te /
NK062(khu)001:12450: phyag na rdo rje'ang khyi la zan byin pa bzhin
NK062(khu)001:12451: du 'brangs shing rang ci 'dod pa de bzhin du
NK062(khu)001:12453: gsum pa rgyas pa'i phrin las la yang lnga ste /
NK062(khu)001:12454: rgyas pa'i lid+ga bca' ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:12455: rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12456: rgyas pa'i bsgrub bya'i las dang /
NK062(khu)001:12457: mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan dang /
NK062(khu)001:12458: lu gu rgyud kyi las yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12459: dang po rgyas pa'i lid+ga bca' ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:12460: bdud rtsi lnga'am yon tan yid bzhin gter du brtag /
NK062(khu)001:12462: de yang lid+ga'i rgyu bsgrub bya'i bdud rtsi lnga'am yang
NK062(khu)001:12463: na zas lnga la 'jig rten gang tshe dang bsod
NK062(khu)001:12464: nams rgyas pa mi dang mi ma yin pa'ang rung
NK062(khu)001:12465: ste / de dag gi lid+ga bcas tshul rnams sngar
NK062(khu)001:12466: bzhin du byas pa la yon tan dpag tu med
NK062(khu)001:12467: pas na yid bzhin gyi gter du brtag cing dkyil
NK062(khu)001:12468: 'khor gyi lho phyogs su brub khung gru bzhi bcug
NK062(khu)001:12470: gnyis pa rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12471: ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK062(khu)001:12473: sngags 'chang rnams rgyas pa'i cha byad dang 'dug stangs kyis /
NK062(khu)001:12474: ma ram la sogs pa'i sngags brjod pas /
NK062(khu)001:12475: phyi rgyas pa ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ser nag gru bzhi me 'bar ba bskyed la /
NK062(khu)001:12476: +amo rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK062(khu)001:12477: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK062(khu)001:12479: nang rgyas pa lha'i mchog rat+na he ru kas gtso
NK062(khu)001:12480: byas pa'i khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kun kyang
NK062(khu)001:12481: / ser nag rgyas pa'i gzugs can rin po che zur brgyad pa thogs pa /
NK062(khu)001:12482: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa /
NK062(khu)001:12483: sprul pa yang sprul dang bcas pa grangs med pa bskyed do //
NK062(khu)001:12484: gsum pa rgyas pa'i bsgrub bya'i las ni /
NK062(khu)001:12485: nga rgyal dga' 'phro phur pas gdab //
NK062(khu)001:12488: de yang sngar bzhin bsgrub bya dgug gzhug bstim pa
NK062(khu)001:12489: la sogs ba byas pa'i lid+ga la gser ram shing
NK062(khu)001:12490: ser po la mgo la brgya mdud dang /
NK062(khu)001:12491: dbal zur bzhir byas pa nga rgyal dga' 'phro ste
NK062(khu)001:12492: sras mchog rat+na k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i phur pa
NK062(khu)001:12493: bzhi / brub khung gi zur bzhir bkod pa rnams la dbang bskur byin rlabs la sogs pa dang /
