NK062(khu)001:12494: lag sor byin gyis brlabs pa la sogs pa byas
NK062(khu)001:12495: nas phur bskul gyi tshig dang g+ha ta ya'i rjes
NK062(khu)001:12496: la / bdag che ge mo'i tshe dang bsod nams
NK062(khu)001:12497: dang dbang thang dang longs spyod thams cad push+tim ku
NK062(khu)001:12499: zhes lid+ga'i yan lag bzhi la gdab cing /
NK062(khu)001:12500: rdo rje tshe dang bsod nams gzi byin rnams 'phel bar 'gyur ba rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK062(khu)001:12501: rat+na he ru kas gtso byas pa'i rgyas pa'i dkyil
NK062(khu)001:12502: 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la dbul ba'i tshul ni
NK062(khu)001:12503: sngar dang rjes su mthun no //
NK062(khu)001:12504: bzhi pa mchod sbyin bya ba yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12508: zhes pas bcom ldan 'das rat+na he ru kas gtso
NK062(khu)001:12509: byas pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar ba rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK062(khu)001:12510: gyi lha tshogs sprul pa yang sprul dang bcas pa
NK062(khu)001:12511: nang du 'du zhing phyir 'phro ba gzi brjid chen
NK062(khu)001:12512: po dang ldan pa rnams la /
NK062(khu)001:12513: dga' ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK062(khu)001:12514: zhes pas stong gi sems rnal 'byor dga' zhing spro
NK062(khu)001:12515: ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan ni
NK062(khu)001:12516: / yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK062(khu)001:12517: zhes pas tshad las 'das pa'i yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK062(khu)001:12518: lnga pa lu gu rgyud kyi las yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12519: ma yi tshogs kyi gang bar 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:12521: ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK062(khu)001:12523: ma ram zhes brjod pas phyi rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK062(khu)001:12524: gru bzhi ser nag 'bar ba 'byams klas pa bskyed
NK062(khu)001:12525: la / +amo rat+na he ru ka rat+na ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK062(khu)001:12526: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK062(khu)001:12528: rat+na he ru kas gtso byas pa'i rgyas pa'i khro
NK062(khu)001:12529: bo lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor khrag 'thung lnga bcu
NK062(khu)001:12530: rtsa brgyad mchog tu gsal ba'i sgrub pa po pho
NK062(khu)001:12531: mo rnams kyis bro ra gru bzhir byas pa'i dbus
NK062(khu)001:12532: su ling ro rnams bzhag cing /
NK062(khu)001:12533: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams bskyod //
NK062(khu)001:12535: lag pa sngar bzhin bsnol ba'i gung mo lu gu
NK062(khu)001:12536: rgyud du sbrel zhing bsdams nas rkang thabs bskyod la
NK062(khu)001:12538: nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK062(khu)001:12539: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig dang /
NK062(khu)001:12540: sum+b+ha ni'i sngags kyis bskul zhing sngar bzhin bro brdungs pas /
NK062(khu)001:12543: gzi brjid 'bar ba rin po che'i rigs kyi sprul
NK062(khu)001:12544: pa ser nag dpag tu med pa'i cho 'phrul chen
NK062(khu)001:12545: po spros pas / yid bzhin nam mkha' gang bar 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:12547: tshe dang bsod nams dang dbang thang dang longs spyod
NK062(khu)001:12548: la sogs pa dgos 'dod 'byung ba yid bzhin gyi
NK062(khu)001:12549: nor bu rin po che ltar bsams la /
NK062(khu)001:12550: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa'i tshe dang bsod nams
NK062(khu)001:12551: dang dbang thang dang longs spyod thams cad rgyas par
NK062(khu)001:12552: gyur cig / push+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK062(khu)001:12554: phyag rgya sprugs nas bshig pa'i yon tan ni /
NK062(khu)001:12555: nam mkha'i khams gang ba dang mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK062(khu)001:12556: bzhi pa zhi ba'i phrin las la yang lnga ste /
NK062(khu)001:12557: zhi ba'i lid+ga bcas ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:12558: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12559: zhi ba'i bsgrub bya'i las dang /
NK062(khu)001:12560: mchod sbyin bya ba'i yon tan dang bcas pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12561: lu gu rgyud kyi las yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12562: dang po zhi ba'i ling+ga bca' ba ni /
NK062(khu)001:12563: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la /
NK062(khu)001:12564: gtum rngam 'khrug pa'i ngo bor brtag /
NK062(khu)001:12566: de yang lid+ga'i rgyu bsgrub bya'i bdud rtsi lnga'am yang
NK062(khu)001:12567: na zas lnga la 'jig rten na gang rgyud ma
NK062(khu)001:12568: rungs pa lus gdug cing gtum pa ngag rngam zhing
NK062(khu)001:12569: sems 'khrug pa mi dang mi ma yin pa gang
NK062(khu)001:12570: yang rung ba'i lid+ga bca' tshul rnams sngar bzhin byas
NK062(khu)001:12571: la / de dag gi ngo bor brtag cing dkyil
NK062(khu)001:12572: 'khor gyi shar phyogs kyi brub khung zlum por gzhug
NK062(khu)001:12573: la / go // gnyis pa zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12574: ya yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK062(khu)001:12576: sngags 'chang rnams zhi ba'i cha byad dang 'dug stangs kyis /
NK062(khu)001:12577: ya ram ra la sogs pa'i sngags brjod pas /
NK062(khu)001:12578: phyi zhi ba ya'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dkar zhing zlum pa me 'bar ba bskyed la /
NK062(khu)001:12579: +amo bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+ha ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK062(khu)001:12580: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram zhes brjod pas /
NK062(khu)001:12581: nang zhi ba'i lha'i mchog bud+ha he ru kas gtso
NK062(khu)001:12582: byas pa'i khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kun kyang
NK062(khu)001:12583: sku mdog dkar po zhi ba'i tshul can 'khor lo
NK062(khu)001:12584: bsnams pa me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa
NK062(khu)001:12585: / sprul pa yang sprul dang bcas pa grangs med pa bskyed do //
NK062(khu)001:12586: gsum pa zhi ba'i bsgrub bya'i las ni /
NK062(khu)001:12587: lhan ner gsal ba'i phur bus gdab //
NK062(khu)001:12588: 'bar ba lhan ne'i tshogs la dbul //
NK062(khu)001:12590: de yang sngar bzhin bsgrub bya dgug gzhug bstim pa la sogs pa byas pa'i lid+ga la /
NK062(khu)001:12591: dngul lam shing dkar po la mgo la rgya mdud dang dbal zlum por byas la /
NK062(khu)001:12592: lhan ner gsal ba'i sras mchog bung+ng+ha k+ai la yar
NK062(khu)001:12593: bskyed pa'i phur pa drug brub khung gi kha khyer
NK062(khu)001:12595: dbang bskur byin brlab la sogs pa dang lag sor byin gyis rlob pa la sogs pa byas nas /
NK062(khu)001:12596: phur bskul gyi tshig dang g+ha ta ya'i sngags kyi rjes la /
NK062(khu)001:12597: gdug cig gtum pa rngams zhing 'khrug pa'i sems can thams cad sh+aan+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK062(khu)001:12598: zhes lid+ga'i yan lag bzhi mgo dang lnga snying ga
NK062(khu)001:12599: dang drug tu gdab cing 'bar ba lhan ne ste
NK062(khu)001:12600: rnam par snang mdzad bud+d+ha he ru kas gtso byas
NK062(khu)001:12601: pa'i zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la
NK062(khu)001:12602: dbul ba'i tshul ni snga ma dang rjes su mthun
NK062(khu)001:12603: no // bzhi pa mchod sbyin bya ba'i yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12606: gsal ba'i gzi brjid 'tsher ba la //
NK062(khu)001:12608: bcom ldan 'das bud+d+ha he ru kas gtso byas pa'i
NK062(khu)001:12609: dang zhing gsal bzhi pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK062(khu)001:12610: gzi brjid 'bar zhing 'od zer 'tsher ba rnams la
NK062(khu)001:12611: / dang ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK062(khu)001:12613: stong gi sems rnal 'byor pa zhi zhing dang ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan ni /
NK062(khu)001:12614: gtum chen rngam pa'ang lhan ner 'gyur //
NK062(khu)001:12616: lus gtum chen ngag rngam po sems khro ba las kyi sbyor ba'ang zhi nas lhan ner 'gyur ro //
NK062(khu)001:12617: lnga pa lu gu rgyud kyi las yon tan dang bcas pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12618: ya yi tshogs kyi med par byed //
NK062(khu)001:12620: ya yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK062(khu)001:12623: phyi zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor zlum po dkar po 'byams klas pa bskyed la /
NK062(khu)001:12624: +amo bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK062(khu)001:12625: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK062(khu)001:12626: zhes pas bud+d+ha he ru kas gtso byas pa'i zhi
NK062(khu)001:12627: ba'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs khrag 'thung
NK062(khu)001:12628: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad mchog tu gsal ba'i sgrub pa
NK062(khu)001:12629: po pho mo rnams kyis bro ra zlum por byas
NK062(khu)001:12630: pa'i dbus su ling ro rnams bzhag cing /
NK062(khu)001:12631: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams nas //
NK062(khu)001:12633: lag pa sngar ltar bsnol ba'i mdzub mo lu gu rgyud du sprel cing bsdams nas /
NK062(khu)001:12635: gti mug rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK062(khu)001:12636: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig dang sum+b+ha ni'i sngags kyis bskul zhing /
NK062(khu)001:12638: 'bar ba lhan ne'i byin gyis khyab //
NK062(khu)001:12640: 'bar ba lhan ne'i zhi ba'i rigs kyi sprul pa
NK062(khu)001:12641: dkar po dpag tu med pa'i gzi byin gyis khyab
NK062(khu)001:12642: nas / phyi dang nang gi gdug rtsub thams cad zhi bar bsams nas /
NK062(khu)001:12643: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa la sdang ba'i dgra
NK062(khu)001:12644: gnod pa'i bgegs bar du gcod pa'i bdud thams cad
NK062(khu)001:12645: kyi gdug rtsub thams cad zhi bar gyur cig sh+ain+tam
NK062(khu)001:12647: zhes pa'i sngags brjod cing phyag rgya sprugs nas bshig bas /
NK062(khu)001:12648: thams cad g.yo ba med par byed //
NK062(khu)001:12650: zhe sdang gi kun nas blangs pa'i phyi nang gi
NK062(khu)001:12651: gdug rtsub khro gtum thams cad zhi nas g.yo ba
NK062(khu)001:12653: las bzhi po 'di dag skabs 'dir gzhung gi 'bru bsnan pa tsam du zad kyi /
NK062(khu)001:12654: rgyas par sbyin sreg rtsa ba dang lag len gyi skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:12655: gnyis pa lhag ma'i las bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:12656: dbang phyug ma lhag mas mchod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12657: dam tshig bsgrag cing las bcol ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:12658: dang po dbang phyug ma lhag mas mchod pa bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12659: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK062(khu)001:12660: lhag ma'i mchod sbyin 'dod pa sbyin //
NK062(khu)001:12662: de yang las bzhi gang byed kyi phrin las ling
NK062(khu)001:12663: ro mnan pa yan chad tshar ba'i rjes la rtsa
NK062(khu)001:12666: dbang mo rnams sngags dang phyag rgyas spyan drangs la
NK062(khu)001:12667: sngar bsdus pa'i lhag gtor rnams kha chus bran la
NK062(khu)001:12668: gtor mar bsres shing so sor mchod nas phrin las
NK062(khu)001:12669: bcol ba ni / slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK062(khu)001:12670: lhag ma'i mchod sbyin 'dod pa sbyin //
NK062(khu)001:12672: dpal gyi pho brang gi slas te btsun mo'i 'khor dang /
NK062(khu)001:12673: gzhan yang mdza' mo'i ngos nas byi mo //
NK062(khu)001:12674: las byed pa'i ngos nas bran mo'i tshogs te /
NK062(khu)001:12675: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad la lhag ma'i
NK062(khu)001:12676: mchod sbyin ji ltar 'dod pa ltar gzhung bzhin du
NK062(khu)001:12677: sbyin no // gnyis pa dam tshig bsgrag cing las bcol ba la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:12680: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12681: rang gi dam tshig rab bsgrags nas //
NK062(khu)001:12682: gang 'dod las de byed par bsgom //
NK062(khu)001:12684: dpal gyi spyan sngar dam bcas pa'i rang rang gi
NK062(khu)001:12685: dam tshig rnams rab tu bsgrags nas phrin las rnam
NK062(khu)001:12686: bzhis gang 'dod kyi las de dag byed par bka'
NK062(khu)001:12687: basgo'o // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:12690: dang po dam tshig bsgrag pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12693: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru ka /
NK062(khu)001:12694: shin tu gdug cing gtum bag can //
NK062(khu)001:12696: sngon ru dra 'dul ba'i tshe dpal chen po badz+ra
NK062(khu)001:12697: he ru ka sku shin tu gdug cig gsung rngam
NK062(khu)001:12699: thams cad ma lus 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:12700: dbang dang byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK062(khu)001:12702: dregs pa can gyi tshogs thams cad lhag ma ma
NK062(khu)001:12703: lus pa 'dul bar mdzad pa'i dbang dang byin rlabs
NK062(khu)001:12704: khyad par can mnga' bas na rmad po che ste
NK062(khu)001:12705: / lha chen la sogs dbang bsdus nas //
NK062(khu)001:12706: 'khor rnams dbang phyug slas su byas //
NK062(khu)001:12708: de ltar dpal chen po de nyid kyis 'jig rten
NK062(khu)001:12709: gyi gtso bo lha chen po nyi shu rtsa brgyad
NK062(khu)001:12710: la sogs pa dbang du bsdus te bsgral nas /
NK062(khu)001:12711: de dag gi 'khor na gnas pa'i dbang phyug ma
NK062(khu)001:12712: nyi shu rtsa brgyad rnams dpa' chen po badz+ra he
NK062(khu)001:12713: ru ka'i slas su te btsun mo'i 'khor du byas
NK062(khu)001:12714: nas / so so'i las rnams bskos pa de //
NK062(khu)001:12715: ji ltar dam bcas khas blangs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:12716: ma thogs myur su mngon par phyung //
NK062(khu)001:12718: zhi rgyas dbang drag so so'i las rnams la bskos
NK062(khu)001:12719: pa de dag gis dpal gyi spyan sngar ji ltar
NK062(khu)001:12720: dam bcas shing khas blangs pa'i tshig /
NK062(khu)001:12722: ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa yang //
NK062(khu)001:12723: zhes pa la sogs pa'i las rnams dus ring por
NK062(khu)001:12724: ma thog par myur du mngon sum du 'grub par
NK062(khu)001:12725: rtags phyung zhig / dam bcas bzhin du ma byas na //
NK062(khu)001:12726: ji ltar dam bcas mna' bor ba'i //
NK062(khu)001:12727: sdom bcas de las 'da' ma byed //
NK062(khu)001:12729: gal te sngon dpal chen po'i spyan sngar dam bcas pa bzhin du las rnams ma byas na /
NK062(khu)001:12732: dpa' bo chen po'i spyan snga 'dir //
NK062(khu)001:12733: zhes pa la sogs pa rang gis dam bcas mana'ang
NK062(khu)001:12734: bor ba'i tshad srog la bzhag nas sdom pa bcas
NK062(khu)001:12735: pa de las khyed rnams 'da' bar ma byed cig
NK062(khu)001:12736: / dam tshig de las 'das gyur nas //
NK062(khu)001:12737: mgo lus snying yang tshal pa bdun //
NK062(khu)001:12740: gal te dam tshig de las 'das shing nyams par gyur na /
NK062(khu)001:12741: khyed rnams kyi mgo bo tshal pa brgya /
NK062(khu)001:12743: snying yang tshal pa bdun du lce la dam chu
NK062(khu)001:12744: bzhag pa de yak+sha khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin
NK062(khu)001:12745: du gyur nas gtubs par 'gyur ro //
NK062(khu)001:12746: gnyis pa las bcol ba bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12750: ji ltar bcol ba bzhin du byos //
NK062(khu)001:12752: dam bcas pa bazha na du ma byas na nyen chen po 'dug pa de bas na /
NK062(khu)001:12753: rnal 'byor pa sngags 'chang bdag gis phrin las bzhi
NK062(khu)001:12754: ji ltar bcol ba bzhin du mngon sum du 'grub
NK062(khu)001:12755: par byos shig / las de mngon du ma byas na //
NK062(khu)001:12756: rang gis mna' bor khas blangs ba'i //
NK062(khu)001:12757: rul myags tshig nas dmyal bar 'gro //
NK062(khu)001:12759: bcol ba'i las de dag mngon sum du 'grub par ma byas na /
NK062(khu)001:12760: rang rang gis dpal chen po'i spyan sngar mna' bor
NK062(khu)001:12761: zhing khas blangs pa'i dam bca' bzhin du 'jig rten
NK062(khu)001:12764: snying tshig nas phyi ma rdo rje'i dmyal bar 'gro dgos pas de 'dra'i nyen la ma bdo bar /
NK062(khu)001:12765: rnal 'byor dam la gnas gyur pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:12766: las rnams yongs su bya ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:12767: 'khor rnams bu gcig bzhin du skyong //
NK062(khu)001:12769: gsang sngags kyi rnal 'byor pa dam la gnas par
NK062(khu)001:12770: gyur pa'i bcol ba'i las bzhi po rnams yongs su
NK062(khu)001:12771: rdzogs par bsgrub par bya ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:12772: de'i 'khor rnams kyang bu gcig po la mas byams shing gdung ba bzhin du skyongs shig /
NK062(khu)001:12773: phra men ma yang dngos grub thob //
NK062(khu)001:12774: bcol ba'i las rnams mngon du byos //
NK062(khu)001:12777: phra men ni don rtags dpe gsum las /
NK062(khu)001:12778: don gyi phra men dbyings la ye shes kyis spras pa yin la /
NK062(khu)001:12779: rtags kyi phra men khro mo'i lus la dud 'gro'i mgo bo can /
NK062(khu)001:12780: dpe'i phra men gser yol dngul gyis spras pa lta bu yin /
NK062(khu)001:12781: 'dir rtags sam las kyi phra men rnams kyis kyang mchog gi dngos grub thob par 'gyur bas /
NK062(khu)001:12782: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi bcol ba'i las rnams mngon
NK062(khu)001:12783: sum du 'grub bar byos shig ces lhag ma'i lha
NK062(khu)001:12785: gsum pa bro gar glu tshig gi yon tan bstan pa la drug ste /
NK062(khu)001:12786: khrag 'thung yab yum gyi glu tshig gis phrin las bzhi ka 'grub par bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12787: go r+ai la sogs pa phyogs kyi khro mo bzhis dbang rgyas 'grub par bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12788: puk+ka s+ai la sogs pa mtshams kyi khro mo bzhis zhi drag 'grub par bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12789: sid+ha ma la sogs pa phyogs kyi phra men ma bzhis drag po 'grub par bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12790: kri ta ma la sogs pa mtshams kyi phra men ma bzhis drag po 'grub par bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12791: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis pho nya mngag gzhug gi las 'grub bar bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12792: dang po khrag 'thung yab yum gyi glu tshig gis phrin las bzhi ka 'grub par bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12793: khro bo bsgrub pa'i byed pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:12795: khro bo bsgrub pa'i las kyi gtso bo ni 'di yin no zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:12796: khro bo tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i dus su
NK062(khu)001:12797: phrin las bzhi po kun gyi gtso bo ni bro
NK062(khu)001:12798: gar glu tshig 'di yis 'grub ba yin no //
NK062(khu)001:12799: khrag 'thung chen po la sogs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:12800: bro gar glu tshig chen pos ni //
NK062(khu)001:12802: khrag 'thung chen po rigs lnga yab yum la sogs
NK062(khu)001:12803: par gsal ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal
NK062(khu)001:12804: 'byor pas / rkang pa'i bro dang lag pa'i gar dang ngag gi glu tshig ni /
NK062(khu)001:12805: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten du //
NK062(khu)001:12806: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:12808: las bzhi so so'i sngags smon lam dang bcas pas
NK062(khu)001:12809: bro chen po brdungs pa 'dis ni yon tan gang
NK062(khu)001:12810: 'byung zhe na / thams cad thams cad ci 'dod par //
NK062(khu)001:12811: thams cad thams cad byed pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:12813: las thams cad dang dngos grub thams cad ci 'dod
NK062(khu)001:12814: par las thams cad dang dngos grub thams cad 'grub
NK062(khu)001:12815: cing thob par byed pa yin no //
NK062(khu)001:12816: gnyis pa goo r+ai la sogs pa phyogs kyi khro mo bzhis dbang rgyas 'grub bar bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12819: mdzod ldan chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:12820: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK062(khu)001:12822: khro mo goo r+ai ma yon tan gyi mdzod ldan
NK062(khu)001:12823: pas na chen mo yin pa la sogs pa'i sogs
NK062(khu)001:12826: be ta li ste phyogs kyi khro mo bzhir gsal
NK062(khu)001:12827: ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK062(khu)001:12829: bro gar dang glu tshig chen mos bro brdungs pas ni yon tan gang 'byung zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:12833: dbang du 'du bar 'dod na dbang du 'du bar
NK062(khu)001:12834: byed la tshe dang bsod nams la sogs pa rgyas
NK062(khu)001:12835: shing 'phel bar 'dod yang rgyas shing 'phel bar byed
NK062(khu)001:12836: do // gsum pa puk+ka s+ai la sogs pa mtshams
NK062(khu)001:12837: kyi khro mo bzhis zhi drag 'grub par bstan pa
NK062(khu)001:12838: do // ni / spos mo rmugs par byed //
NK062(khu)001:12840: spos mo chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:12841: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK062(khu)001:12843: yon tan gyi mngon par mtho ba'i spos mo chen
NK062(khu)001:12844: mo puk+ka s+ai dang la sogs pa'i sogs khong nas
NK062(khu)001:12847: tsan+t+ra l+ai ste mtshams kyi khro mo bzhir gsal ba'i
NK062(khu)001:12848: ting 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas sngar bshad
NK062(khu)001:12849: pa bzhin bro gar dang glu tshig chen mos bro
NK062(khu)001:12850: brdungs pas ni yon tan gang 'byung zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:12851: lhan ner 'dod na lhan ner byed //
NK062(khu)001:12852: rmugs par 'dod na smugs par byed //
NK062(khu)001:12854: phyi nang gi gdug rtsub thams cad zhi nas lhan ner 'dod na ni lhan ner byed la /
NK062(khu)001:12855: drag po mngon spyod kyi las kyis gdul bya dran
NK062(khu)001:12856: pa nyams shing blo rmugs par 'dod na ni smugs
NK062(khu)001:12857: par byed do // bzhi pa sid+ha ma la sogs
NK062(khu)001:12858: pa phyogs kyi phra men bzhis drag po 'grub par
NK062(khu)001:12859: par byed do // bstan pa ni / seng gdong med bar byed //
NK062(khu)001:12861: seng gdong chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:12862: bro gar glu tshig chen mo ni //
NK062(khu)001:12864: phra men ma seng ge'i gdong ba can gyi sing+ha
NK062(khu)001:12865: ma chen mo dang la sogs pa'i sogs khong nas
NK062(khu)001:12868: shwa na ma ste phyogs kyi phra men ma mche
NK062(khu)001:12869: ba can bzhir gsal ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan
NK062(khu)001:12870: pa'i rnal 'byor pas sngar bshad pa bzhin bro gar
NK062(khu)001:12871: dang glu tshig chen mos bro brdungs pas ni yon
NK062(khu)001:12873: thams cad kun la za bar byed //
NK062(khu)001:12874: rdul cha tsam yang med par byed //
NK062(khu)001:12876: drag po sgrol ba'i las kyis gdul bya gdug pa
NK062(khu)001:12877: can thams cad kun la sha rus za zhing khrag
NK062(khu)001:12879: sha khrag rus gsum gyi lhag ma rdul phra rab
NK062(khu)001:12880: kyi cha tsam yang med par brlag cing stongs par
NK062(khu)001:12881: byed do // lnga pa kri ta ma la sogs
NK062(khu)001:12882: pa mtshams kyi phra men bzhis drag po 'grub par
NK062(khu)001:12883: byed do // bstan pa ni / bzhad gdong nyams par byed //
NK062(khu)001:12885: bzhad gdong chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK062(khu)001:12886: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK062(khu)001:12888: phra men bzhad kyi gdong ba can g+h+ri ta ma chen mo dang la sogs pa'i sogs khongs nas /
NK062(khu)001:12891: hu lu ma ste mtshams kyi phra men ma gshog
NK062(khu)001:12892: pa can bzhir gsal ba'i ting 'dzin dang ldan pa'i
NK062(khu)001:12893: rnal 'byor pas sngar bshad pa bzhin bro gar dang
NK062(khu)001:12894: glu tshig chen mos bro brdungs pas ni yon tan
NK062(khu)001:12896: thams cad ma lus 'byin par byed //
NK062(khu)001:12897: kun la rab tu nyams par byed //
NK062(khu)001:12899: drag po'i phrin las kyis gdul bya gdug pa can
NK062(khu)001:12900: rnams kyi mthu rtsal thams cad lhag ma ma lus
NK062(khu)001:12902: dgra bgegs kun la yod pa'i mthu rtsal rab tu nyams par byed do //
NK062(khu)001:12903: drug pa dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis
NK062(khu)001:12904: pho nya mngag gzhug gi las 'grub par bstan pa
NK062(khu)001:12905: ni / slas dang byed pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:12907: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK062(khu)001:12908: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK062(khu)001:12910: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs dbang phyug ma
NK062(khu)001:12911: nyi shu rtsa brgyad du gsal ba'i ting 'dzin dang
NK062(khu)001:12912: ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas sngar bshad pa bzhin bro
NK062(khu)001:12913: gar dang glu tshig chen mos bro brdungs pas ni
NK062(khu)001:12914: yon tan gang byung zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:12915: rbad cing btang bar bya ba ste //
NK062(khu)001:12916: thams cad thams cad byed pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:12918: rbad cing las la btang bar bya ba ni pho
NK062(khu)001:12919: nya ste de dag thams cad kyis mngag gzhug dang
NK062(khu)001:12920: pho nya'i las thams cad 'grub par byed pa yin
NK062(khu)001:12921: no // bzhi pa gzungs sems bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:12924: dang po gzungs ma bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12925: ljon pa dang ni lcug phran tshal //
NK062(khu)001:12926: sdong gcig dang ni mes reg dang //
NK062(khu)001:12928: phrin las bzhi 'grub pa'i cha rkyen gyi gtso bo gzungs ma dang gtso bo'i sems yin la /
NK062(khu)001:12929: de yang gzungs ma'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK062(khu)001:12930: shing dang chos mtshungs sbyor te /
NK062(khu)001:12931: ljon pa dang ni zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:12932: shing ljon pa la 'dzar 'dzer dang thag thug med pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12933: de dang chos mthun par zhi ba'i gzungs ma ni /
NK062(khu)001:12934: byad lus shin tu mdzes shing rnal 'byor pa'i yid du 'ong ba la bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:12935: de yang sgyu 'phrul rda rje las /
NK062(khu)001:12936: dkar mo bong chung skad che la //
NK062(khu)001:12937: bzhin lus gtsug phud g.yas su 'khyil //
NK062(khu)001:12938: yan lag phra 'jam skad gsal zhing //
NK062(khu)001:12939: glu gar lci bas zhi ba bya //
NK062(khu)001:12942: zhes pas shing lcug phran tshal la yal 'dab mang po yod pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12943: de dang chos mthun par rgyas pa'i gzungs ma'ang spun
NK062(khu)001:12944: zla dang bu tsha mang po yod pa la bya
NK062(khu)001:12945: ba ste / zla dang yan lag mang ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:12946: phra zhing shad la gzabs su ring //
NK062(khu)001:12947: bzhin lus ser zhing gru bzhir gnas //
NK062(khu)001:12948: rna 'phyang sha dang nu ma rgyas //
NK062(khu)001:12951: sdong gcig dang ni zhes bas /
NK062(khu)001:12952: shing sdong po gcig pa ni gcig pur skyes pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12953: de dang chos mthun par dbang gi gzungs ma ni
NK062(khu)001:12954: spun zla dang bu tsha med par gcig pur skyes
NK062(khu)001:12956: bzhin mdog pad 'dra sog kha la //
NK062(khu)001:12957: smin dkyus ring zhing stod smad phyed //
NK062(khu)001:12958: lus la chu klung dri zhim zhing //
NK062(khu)001:12959: bde ba ldan zhing yal ga med //
NK062(khu)001:12964: shing mes reg pa ni mes tshig pa ste sma phab pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:12965: de dang chos mthun par drag po'i gzungs ma'ang yug
NK062(khu)001:12966: sa mo la sogs pa sma phab pa sdug bsngal
NK062(khu)001:12967: gyi nyen pa la bya ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:12968: nag mo gru gsum rtsi mgo ma //
NK062(khu)001:12969: khro gnyen byis pa'i lus ldan zhing //
NK062(khu)001:12970: gtum zhing barlanga tshig mdzem bag med //
NK062(khu)001:12971: gtsang rme'i rtog bral gsod par bshad //
NK062(khu)001:12973: 'di la 'grel chung pin tar tha ltar na /
NK062(khu)001:12974: phrin las bzhi sgrub pa sbyin sreg bya ba phyi'i gnas su bshad de /
NK062(khu)001:12976: zhi rgyas dbang drag phyi nang gsang ba'i gnas //
NK062(khu)001:12977: ljon shing can dang lcug phran rgyas pa'i tshal //
NK062(khu)001:12978: shing gcig drung dang mes tshig phyi yi yin //
NK062(khu)001:12979: ma smas pa dang pu ta mang 'phel dang //
NK062(khu)001:12980: skye brgyud med dang bkra mi shis gsang ba //
NK062(khu)001:12981: ting 'dzin rnam pa bzhi ni nang gir gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:12983: 'o na las bzhi bsgrub pa'i cha rkyen du gzungs ma mi dgos sam zhe na ma yin te /
NK062(khu)001:12984: sbyin sreg bya ba'i gnas de nyid du gzungs ma'i mtshan nyid kyang bshad ma thag pa'i /
NK062(khu)001:12985: ma smas pa dang pu tra mang 'phel dang //
NK062(khu)001:12986: zhes pa la sogs pa'am sgyu 'phrul rdo rje nas
NK062(khu)001:12987: bshad pa'i gzungs ma rnams dang snyoms par 'jug pa
NK062(khu)001:12989: gnyis pa gtso bo'i sems bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:12990: dang bas dga' bas chags pas dang //
NK062(khu)001:12991: khros pas k+aa li rab tu bya //
NK062(khu)001:12993: phrin las bzhi po de dag bsgrub pa'i tshe /
NK062(khu)001:12994: gtso bo'i sems ni don gyi sems snang stong dbyer
NK062(khu)001:12995: med 'ching grol dang bral ba la las bzhi lhun
NK062(khu)001:12996: grub tu gnas pa mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu yin la
NK062(khu)001:12997: / stongs kyi sems las bzhi kun slong gi bsam
NK062(khu)001:12998: pa bzhi ni mthun pa'i grogs byed pas lhan cig
NK062(khu)001:13000: de yang las bzhi re re la yang don gyi sems dang stongs kyi sems gnyis gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:13002: chos thams cad yid du mi 'ong ba'i dngos po
NK062(khu)001:13003: rnams rang bzhin gyi mi gnas te dang bas na
NK062(khu)001:13004: zhi ba'i don gyi sems yin la /
NK062(khu)001:13005: zhi ba'i phrin las kyis las la sbyar bas gnod
NK062(khu)001:13006: pa dang gdug rtsub thams cad zhi bar bsam pa
NK062(khu)001:13007: ni stong kyi sems yin no //
NK062(khu)001:13009: yon tan gyi dngos po rnams rang bzhin gyis gnas
NK062(khu)001:13010: pa'i dga' ba chen po ni rgyas pa'i don gyi
NK062(khu)001:13011: sems yin la / rgyas pa'i phrin las kyi las
NK062(khu)001:13012: la sbyor bas yon tan thams cad mngon sum du
NK062(khu)001:13013: 'phel bar bsam pa ni stongs kyi sems yin no
NK062(khu)001:13014: sems yin la / // chags pas dang /
NK062(khu)001:13016: bdag la mi gus pa dang mi 'dza' ba la
NK062(khu)001:13017: sogs pa'i gdul bya rang gi sems nyid las mi
NK062(khu)001:13018: gzhan par chags pa ni dbang gi don gyi sems
NK062(khu)001:13019: yin la / de dang rjes su mthun par mngon
NK062(khu)001:13020: sum du zhen cing chags pa'i sgo nas dbang gi
NK062(khu)001:13021: phrin las kyi las la sbyar bas bsgrub bya dbang
NK062(khu)001:13022: du bsdu bar bsam pa ni stongs kyi sems yin
NK062(khu)001:13023: yin la / no // khros pas k+aa li rab tu bya //
NK062(khu)001:13025: dngos po'i rang bzhin dngos med du 'jig bar byed pa ni drag po'i don gyi sems yin la /
NK062(khu)001:13026: sems rab tu 'khrug cing zhe sdang khros pas k+aa
NK062(khu)001:13027: li sgrol ba drag po'i phrin las kyi las la
NK062(khu)001:13028: rab tu sbyar bar bya ba ste bsgral ba'i zhing
NK062(khu)001:13029: bcu'i srog 'jig par mos pa'i bsam pa ni stongs
NK062(khu)001:13031: gnyis pa phrin las kyi yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13033: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis sbyong bar gyur to //
NK062(khu)001:13035: zhes ston pas brjod pas ma 'ongs pa dang 'byung
NK062(khu)001:13036: bar ma nges pa ste dus phyi ma gnyis kyi
NK062(khu)001:13037: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de /
NK062(khu)001:13038: sems can rnams la 'das pa dang da ltar te
NK062(khu)001:13039: dus snga ma gnyis kyi de bzhin gshegs pa rtogs
NK062(khu)001:13040: pa mngon gyur gyi sangs rgyas nyid kyis brtse ba'i
NK062(khu)001:13041: thugs rje mdzad pa'i phrin las rnam bzhi'i sgo nas
NK062(khu)001:13042: rgyud dag par sbyong bar gyur to //
NK062(khu)001:13044: yang na ston pas debazhina gshegs pa nyid kyang phrin las bzhi'i sgo nas rgyud sbyong la /
NK062(khu)001:13045: 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyang phrin las bzhi'i sgo nas rgyud sbyong bar gyur to //
NK062(khu)001:13046: de'i phyir gdul bya gzhan dag phrin las kyis rgyud
NK062(khu)001:13047: sbyong dgos pa lta ci smos zhes pa'i tha tshig
NK062(khu)001:13048: go // gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13051: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK062(khu)001:13052: zhes bas gsang ba'i rtogs dka' ba /
NK062(khu)001:13054: de kho na nyid gzhan sel ba /
NK062(khu)001:13055: nges pa the tshom dang bral ba /
NK062(khu)001:13056: las zhes pa de mtshan gyi gzhir gda' /
NK062(khu)001:13057: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las byin gyis rlob pa zhes bya ba'i le'u ste nyi shu pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13058: zhes pas sems nyid la ye gdon ma nas lhun
NK062(khu)001:13059: gyis grub pa'i phrin las bzhi thabs 'dis mngon du
NK062(khu)001:13060: snang bar byed pas na byin gyis rlob pa zhes
NK062(khu)001:13061: bya ba'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams tshoms dang ris
NK062(khu)001:13062: su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa 'i don
NK062(khu)001:13064: de'i grangs nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las yas bgrangs nyi shu ba'i don du gada'o //
NK062(khu)001:13065: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13066: rgyud kyi 'grel bshad rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13067: sgron me yid bzhin gyi nor bu zhes bya ba
NK062(khu)001:13068: las le'u nyi shu pa'i gzhung don rnam par bshad
NK062(khu)001:13070: da ni le'u nyi shu rtsa gcig pa 'chad par byed pa 'di la /
NK062(khu)001:13071: chos tshoms ngos bzung ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK062(khu)001:13072: blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam dang 'bras bu ston /
NK062(khu)001:13073: lam la thabs lam grol lam gnyis las grol lam ston /
NK062(khu)001:13074: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston /
NK062(khu)001:13075: mtshan nyid gsum las 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid ston /
NK062(khu)001:13076: snang ba bzhi las lam dang 'bras bu'i snang ba ston /
NK062(khu)001:13077: blo 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don ston /
NK062(khu)001:13078: de la dngos po bcu yod pa las bstod pa'i mchod pa ston /
NK062(khu)001:13079: de'i zhor la dkyil 'khor dang phrin las zur tsam ston /
NK062(khu)001:13080: blo tha ma'i tshos tshoms bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig
NK062(khu)001:13081: bcu las mtshon pa dpe dang spyi 'gro gsum gyis
NK062(khu)001:13082: ston no // de ltar ston par byed pa le'u
NK062(khu)001:13083: nyi shu rtsa gcig pa 'di la don gsum ste
NK062(khu)001:13084: ston no // / gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13087: dang po gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13088: de nas bcom ldan 'das glu 'di blangs so //
NK062(khu)001:13090: de nas zhes pas rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin
NK062(khu)001:13091: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang lhag pa ting 'dzin sku
NK062(khu)001:13092: gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor rnams rdzogs par bstan pa
NK062(khu)001:13093: la de de la bstod pas na nas zhes bya'o
NK062(khu)001:13094: // bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po ni 'bru mthun la /
NK062(khu)001:13095: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyis shin tu rngam pa'i mdangs kyis glu 'di blangs so //
NK062(khu)001:13096: zhes pas khro bo rab tu mang po'i tshogs kyi
NK062(khu)001:13097: dkyil 'khor de dag kun gyi zhal khro tshul dang
NK062(khu)001:13098: ldan pa'i 'dzum pa dang bcas pas shin tu rngams
NK062(khu)001:13099: pa'i mdangs kyis dbyangs ngo ro dang bcas pas bstod
NK062(khu)001:13100: pa'i glu drug po 'og nas 'byung ba 'di dag
NK062(khu)001:13102: gnyis pa le'u'i gzhung bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:13104: gzhung gsungs pa'i tshul bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13105: dang po gzhung dngos la drug ste /
NK062(khu)001:13109: yon tan la bstod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13110: phrin las la bstod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13111: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las spyir bstod pa'ang dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13112: dang po sku la bstod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13114: gtum chen za byed che hoh zhes pa der gda' zhing /
NK062(khu)001:13115: h+aum ni glu nyid ye shes kyi rgyan gyi phyir te glu'i 'go drangs pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13116: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK062(khu)001:13118: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag kun kyang gsum dang ldan te /
NK062(khu)001:13119: rngam pa'i tshems gtum pa mche ba gtsigs pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13120: 'bar ba'i sku gtum pa 'jigs pa'i cha byad can dang /
NK062(khu)001:13121: phrin las drag shul mdzad pa'i phyag gtum pa 'jigs pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs bsnams pa /
NK062(khu)001:13122: bdud dang gnod sbyin la sogs pa las khyad par du gyur ba'i phyir chen po ste /
NK062(khu)001:13123: khro bo de lta bu'i sku la bzod par dka'
NK062(khu)001:13124: ba'i me dpung dus kyi tha ma bskal pa 'jig
NK062(khu)001:13125: pa'i me chen ser lhag 'bar bltar me ri dang
NK062(khu)001:13129: mun pa sel ba'i 'od zer gsal ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13130: thabs la mkhas pa'i 'od zer mang ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13131: thugs rje chen po'i 'od zer gyis thams cad khyab pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:13132: de dag kyang dper na nyi ma 'bum dus gcig
NK062(khu)001:13133: tu shar ba lta bu'i 'od zer byin gyis thams
NK062(khu)001:13135: khro gnyen glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK062(khu)001:13137: dbang du sdud pa'i khro gnyer dpral bar bsdus pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13138: zil gyis gnon pa'i khro gnyen 'bri gu ta rtse gsum du gyen du 'greng ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13139: thabs la mkhas pa'i khro gnyer lus sna tshogs su g.yo ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13140: de dag kyang dper na glog stong dus gcig tu 'gyu ba bzhin du 'khyug pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13141: mche ba zangs yag za byed che //
NK062(khu)001:13143: skye shi rtsad gcod kyi mche ba dkar la zangs ring ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13144: gdug pa za byed kyi mche ba rtsa ba dmar ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13145: rngam pa'i mche ba rab tu rno ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13146: de lta bu'i mche ba zangs yag 'bar ba gtsigs
NK062(khu)001:13147: pas gdug pa can za bar byed pa la 'gran
NK062(khu)001:13148: gyi zla med pas na che ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:13149: ho ni de dag gi bstod pa'i don la mnyes pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13150: gnyis pa gsung la bstod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13152: rngam pa'i g.yeng ba che hoh zhes pa der gda' zhing /
NK062(khu)001:13153: h+aum ni glu nyid rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir //
NK062(khu)001:13155: stong pa chen po'i zhal rngam /
NK062(khu)001:13157: sgrol ba chen po'i tshems rngam pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13158: gsung rngam par sgrog pa'i nga ro //
NK062(khu)001:13159: drag po dbyangs kyi nga ro //
NK062(khu)001:13160: 'jigs pa'i nga ro a a dang phata phata la sogs pa /
NK062(khu)001:13161: de dag kyang dper na 'brug stong dus gcig tu
NK062(khu)001:13162: ldir ba lta bu'i skad ltar drag po'i dbyangs 'jigs
NK062(khu)001:13163: par grags pa'o // gtum chem ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK062(khu)001:13165: spyan 'dren pa'i tshe lha gshegs pa'i gtum chem che ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13166: ru tra 'dul ba'i tshe phrin las mdzad pa'i gtum chem drag pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13167: sprul pa spros pa'i tshe sprul pa 'khrug pa'i gtum chem mang ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:13168: de dag kyang dper na ri rab 'bum dus gcig tu bsnyil ba'i skad tsam du grags pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13169: a a ha la'i gad rgyangs che //
NK062(khu)001:13171: gdug pa can la rngam pa'i gad mo a a /
NK062(khu)001:13172: gtum pa'i gad mo ha la /
NK062(khu)001:13173: dgyes pa'i gad mo ha ha ste gad rgyangs de dag kyang rab tu sgra che bar bzhad pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13174: spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yeng ba che //
NK062(khu)001:13176: 'khor sdud pa'i spyugs pa snyan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13177: gdug pa 'dul ba'i spyugs pa drag pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13178: byin 'bebs pa'i spyugs pa gdangs 'tsher la yun ring
NK062(khu)001:13179: bas te spyugs pa'i sgra de dag gi dbugs las
NK062(khu)001:13181: khams gsum thams cad g.yeng bar byed pa la 'gran zla med pas che ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:13182: ho ni bstod pa'i don la mnyes pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13183: gsum pa thugs la bstod pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:13185: khro bo thig le che hoh zhes pa der gda' zhing /
NK062(khu)001:13186: h+aum ni glu nyid khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK062(khu)001:13188: shes rab chen po'i khro bo /
NK062(khu)001:13189: ye shes chen po'i khro bo /
NK062(khu)001:13190: phyag rgya chen po'i khro bo dang gsum las /
NK062(khu)001:13191: 'dir khro bo nyid shes rab kyi ngo bor gyur bas na shes rab chen po'i khro bo ste /
NK062(khu)001:13192: des lta ngan thams cad mi dmigs par 'joms par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK062(khu)001:13193: de nyid cis kyang mi sgrib par gsal bas na 'od po che zhes pas so //
NK062(khu)001:13194: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal //
NK062(khu)001:13196: shes byed ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyis shes bya
NK062(khu)001:13197: ma lus pa kun dus gcig tu yul med rang
NK062(khu)001:13198: gsal gyi tshul gyis mkhyen pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13201: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin du 'bar ba'i ye
NK062(khu)001:13202: shes kyis snang ba thams cad kyang nyid las mi
NK062(khu)001:13203: gzhan par sbyong ba'i phyir kun tu 'joms zhes gsungs
NK062(khu)001:13204: so // sna tshogs ye shes thig le che //
NK062(khu)001:13206: ye shes chen po bco brgyad la sogs pa rtsis
NK062(khu)001:13207: las 'das pas na sna tshogs pa'i ye shes rnam
NK062(khu)001:13208: pa tha dad du gsal ba kun kyang mi gnas
NK062(khu)001:13209: pa'i ye shes chen pos ro gcig pas na thig
NK062(khu)001:13211: ho ni bstod pa'i don la mnyes pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13212: de yang ye shes bco brgyad ni /
NK062(khu)001:13231: mi rtog pa'i ye shes zhes gsungs shing /
NK062(khu)001:13232: yang nang pa'i ye shes lnga /
NK062(khu)001:13234: de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes /
NK062(khu)001:13236: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes lnga /
NK062(khu)001:13237: kri yog gi ye shes lnga /
NK062(khu)001:13238: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i ye shes bzhi ste bco brgyad ces pa'am /
NK062(khu)001:13239: yang na yul stong pa bco brgyad mkhyen pa'i ye
NK062(khu)001:13240: shes bco brgyad yin zhes bla ma gong ma rnams
NK062(khu)001:13241: gsung ngo // bzhi pa yon tan la bstod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13243: khro ba'i che hoh zhes pa der gda' zhing /
NK062(khu)001:13244: h+aum ni glu nyid khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK062(khu)001:13246: khro bo'i rgyal po'i dkyil 'khor 'di dag gi yon
NK062(khu)001:13247: tan gyi tshogs rab tu mang po'i tshad sprin chen
NK062(khu)001:13248: po 'khrigs pa tsam du snang ba las /
NK062(khu)001:13251: khros pa khro bo'i dkyil 'khor so so'i sprul pa
NK062(khu)001:13252: dang bcas pa bsam yas pa gdul bya tha dad
NK062(khu)001:13253: la char chen po ltar du 'bebs shing snang bar
NK062(khu)001:13254: mdzad pa'o // dkyil 'khor yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK062(khu)001:13256: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha de dag kyang yid
NK062(khu)001:13257: bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta bu la
NK062(khu)001:13258: dgos 'dod zad mi shes pa 'byung ba'i gter du
NK062(khu)001:13259: gyur pas gdul bya so so'i re ba skor ba
NK062(khu)001:13260: byed pa'o // sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che //
NK062(khu)001:13262: de ltar yon tan sna tshogs dang bcas khros pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13263: tshul ston pa'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyang
NK062(khu)001:13264: ye shes chen po'i khro bor ro gcig pas na
NK062(khu)001:13266: ho ni bstod pa'i don la mnyes pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13267: lnga pa phrin las la bstod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13269: bdud thig le che hoh zhes pa der gda' zhing /
NK062(khu)001:13270: h+aum ni glu nyid bdud kun gyi ni bdag chen po //
NK062(khu)001:13272: nyon mongs pa la sogs pa'i bdud bzhi po ma
NK062(khu)001:13273: lus pa kun gyi rang bzhin ma spangs par dbang
NK062(khu)001:13274: du byed pa ni bdag nyid chen po badz+ra he
NK062(khu)001:13275: ru ka'o // bdud kyi bdud sde bdud rnams 'joms //
NK062(khu)001:13277: don de'i phyir bdud ru dra sde dang bcas pas
NK062(khu)001:13278: pho rnams kyi phung po bsgral zhing shes pa gnas
NK062(khu)001:13279: spar mo rnams sbyar zhing byin gyis brlabs pas na
NK062(khu)001:13280: / bdud ru dra 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi kyang bdud ltar snang ba yin te /
NK062(khu)001:13281: phyi rol gzhan snang du pham par byas pa na bdud rnams 'joms pa zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:13284: de'i phyir 'jigs pa'i tshogs ru dra 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyang bsdigs shing 'jigs par byed pa /
NK062(khu)001:13285: 'jigs byed chen po thig le che //
NK062(khu)001:13287: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i lha tshogs
NK062(khu)001:13288: thams cad kyang ye shes kyi mdzad pa nyid las
NK062(khu)001:13289: ma g.yos par rang snang ba'i phyir thig le che
NK062(khu)001:13290: zhes bya'o // ho ni bstod pa'i don la mnyes pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13291: drug pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las spyir
NK062(khu)001:13292: bstod pa'am dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa
NK062(khu)001:13294: rdo rje 'thor rlung che hoh zhes pa der gda' zhing /
NK062(khu)001:13295: h+aum ni glu nyid ye shes kyi rgyan gyi phyir te glu'i 'go 'dren pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13296: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK062(khu)001:13298: rdo rje ni khro bo'i tshogs rnams ngo bo snang
NK062(khu)001:13299: stong dbyer mi phyed pa dang phrin las bdud bzhi
NK062(khu)001:13301: tshul des 'og ma rnams kyang shes par bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:13303: zhes pa ni dpe yin la /
NK062(khu)001:13304: don rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes de mtshan
NK062(khu)001:13305: ma'i rnam par rtog pas mi gzhigs pa'i rtags su
NK062(khu)001:13306: khro bo rnams kyi sku rdo rje'i brag chen sra
NK062(khu)001:13307: ba po dang 'dra ste sra zhing mkhregs pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13308: rdo rje chu bo sdud chen po //
NK062(khu)001:13309: zhes pa ni dpe yin la /
NK062(khu)001:13310: don 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid
NK062(khu)001:13311: du sdud cing ma rtogs pa'i sems can la thugs
NK062(khu)001:13312: rjes chags pa'i rtags su khrag gi rgya mtsho zhal
NK062(khu)001:13314: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK062(khu)001:13315: zhes pa ni dpe yin la /
NK062(khu)001:13316: don ye shes kyi mes mtshan ma'i bag chags mi
NK062(khu)001:13317: gnas pa sreg pa'i rtags su sku me dpung 'bar
NK062(khu)001:13319: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che hoh zhes pa ni dpe yin la /
NK062(khu)001:13320: don ye shes kyi rlung gis rnam par rtog pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13321: rgyu 'bras skye med kyi dbyings su 'thor bar byed
NK062(khu)001:13322: pa'i rtags su zhal dang shangs nas bshugs rlung drag
NK062(khu)001:13325: de las dur khrod kyi 'byung ba bzhi po yang
NK062(khu)001:13326: ye shes rdo rje'i ngo bo bstod pa yang zhar
NK062(khu)001:13327: la bshad pa'o zhes gsungs pas /
NK062(khu)001:13328: 'byung ba bzhi la bstod kyang rung ste /
NK062(khu)001:13329: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK062(khu)001:13330: zhes pas keng rus kyi ri rab dang /
NK062(khu)001:13331: rdo rje chu bo sdud chen po //
NK062(khu)001:13332: zhes pas rak+ta'i rgya mtsho dang /
NK062(khu)001:13333: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK062(khu)001:13334: zhes pas bskal pa'i me dang /
NK062(khu)001:13335: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che //
NK062(khu)001:13336: zhes pas rlung rdo rje rgya gram la bstod pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13337: ho ni bstod pa'i don la mnyes pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13338: de yang bstod pa de dag ni bu ngan pa
NK062(khu)001:13339: la mas bstod pa lta bu ni ma yin te
NK062(khu)001:13340: / yon tan yod pa la yod pa ltar nyid
NK062(khu)001:13341: kyis nyid la bstod pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13343: de'i rjes su lam pa'i rnal 'byor bas bstod pa
NK062(khu)001:13344: ni bstod pa'i mchod par shes bar bya'o zhes bla
NK062(khu)001:13345: ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK062(khu)001:13346: gnyis pa gzhung gsungs ba'i tshul ni /
NK062(khu)001:13347: zhes ched du glu blangs so //
NK062(khu)001:13349: zhes khro bo'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK062(khu)001:13350: la bstod pa'i glu 'di dag 'khor rnams kyi ched
NK062(khu)001:13351: du bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po nyid kyis
NK062(khu)001:13353: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13354: gsang ba'i nyi shu gcig pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13356: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK062(khu)001:13357: zhes pa gsang ba'i rtogs dka' ba /
NK062(khu)001:13359: de kho na nyid gzhan sel ba /
NK062(khu)001:13360: nges pa the tshom dang bral ba /
NK062(khu)001:13361: las zhes pa de mtshan gyi gzhir gda' /
NK062(khu)001:13362: khro bo la bstod pa'i le'u ste nyi shu gcig pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13364: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK062(khu)001:13365: phrin las dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa
NK062(khu)001:13366: la bstod pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams tshoms dang
NK062(khu)001:13367: ris su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don
NK062(khu)001:13368: gyis na le'u ste de'i grangs nyi shu rtsa gnyis
NK062(khu)001:13369: su yod pa las yas bgrangs nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK062(khu)001:13371: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13372: rgyud kyi 'grel bshad rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13373: sgron me yid bzhin gyi nor bu zhes bya ba
NK062(khu)001:13374: las le'u nyi shu rtsa gcig pa'i gzhung don rnam
NK062(khu)001:13376: da ni le'u tha ma 'chad par byed pa 'di la /
NK062(khu)001:13377: chos tshoms ngos bzung ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK062(khu)001:13378: blo rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las gsum ka ston /
NK062(khu)001:13379: lam la thabs lam grol lam gnyis las grol lam ston /
NK062(khu)001:13380: mtshan nyid gsum las rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta
NK062(khu)001:13381: ba dang 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid ston
NK062(khu)001:13382: / rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston /
NK062(khu)001:13383: snang ba bzhi las bzhi ka ston /
NK062(khu)001:13384: blo 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las gdams gtad ston /
NK062(khu)001:13385: blo tha ma'i chos tshoms bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu las rang bzhin lta ba /
NK062(khu)001:13388: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK062(khu)001:13389: de ltar ston pa'i le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa
NK062(khu)001:13390: 'di la rnam par dbye ba'i tshig stag gis mchongs
NK062(khu)001:13393: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13396: dang po gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13397: de nas bcom ldan 'das brjod do //
NK062(khu)001:13400: de yang 'brel mtshams sbyor ba'i tshig bya ngang mo'i 'gros ltar bshad na /
NK062(khu)001:13401: le'u gsum pa'i smad nas nyi shu rtsa gcig pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13402: bar gyi le'u phyed dang bcu dgus rgyud don rdzogs
NK062(khu)001:13403: par bstan pa la de gdams shing gtad pa ston
NK062(khu)001:13404: pas na nas zhes bya ste /
NK062(khu)001:13405: de yang gang gis gdams shing gtad na /
NK062(khu)001:13406: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:13407: bcom ldan 'das bsam gyi mi khyab pa'i dgyes pa
NK062(khu)001:13408: chen po kun tu bzang pos gdams shing gtad pa'o
NK062(khu)001:13409: // gang la gdams shing gtad na /
NK062(khu)001:13410: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:13411: 'khor thams cad kyang ston pa'i rang bzhin nyid las mi gzhan pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:13412: de yang lhan cig pa'i 'khor dbang yongs su rdzogs
NK062(khu)001:13413: par thob pa rnams de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du
NK062(khu)001:13414: gyur pa dang / go phye ba'i 'khor gang zag
NK062(khu)001:13415: chos kyi mig can rnams kyang ma 'ongs pa'i dus
NK062(khu)001:13416: su de bzhin gshegs nyid du 'gyur pa la dgongs
NK062(khu)001:13419: gsang sngags kyi rgyal po zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:13420: gsang sngags kyi mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud rang
NK062(khu)001:13421: bzhin gsang ba'i snying po zhes bya ba shes bya
NK062(khu)001:13422: thun mong ba rnams las khyad par du gyur pa
NK062(khu)001:13423: dang / de mtshon byed lam rkyen gyi rgyud ye
NK062(khu)001:13424: ger bkod pa lta spyod gzhan las khyad par du
NK062(khu)001:13426: ngo bo dang yon tan le'u gsum pa dang bcu
NK062(khu)001:13427: gsum par bshad pa rnams kyi don gyis na rgyal
NK062(khu)001:13428: po ste de lta bu'i rgyud 'di gdams shing gtad
NK062(khu)001:13429: do // dgos ched ci'i phyir gdams shing gtad na /
NK062(khu)001:13430: brtan par bzung ba 'di ched du brjod do //
NK062(khu)001:13432: rang bzhin gyi rgyud gzhan du mi 'gyur bar bya ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13433: lam gyi rgyud brtan zhing mi nub par gzung ba'i
NK062(khu)001:13434: phyir gdams shing gtad pa'i don 'og nas 'byung ba'i
NK062(khu)001:13435: de dag 'khor rnams kyi ched du tshig tu brjod
NK062(khu)001:13436: pa dang 'dra bar gsal ba 'di ston pas brjod
NK062(khu)001:13437: do // gnyis pa le'u'i gzhung bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:13440: dang po gdams pa bstan pa la bzhi ste /
NK062(khu)001:13441: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba rtogs byar gdams pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13442: log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba dag byar gdams pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13443: gdul bya lam gyis snang ba bgrod byar gdams pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13444: 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba thob byar gdams pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13445: dang po gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba rtogs byar gdams pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13448: de yang gzhi ni chos thams cad kyi 'byung gzhi /
NK062(khu)001:13449: rang bzhin ni bcos slad dang bral ba /
NK062(khu)001:13450: snang ba ni rang rig pa thams cad du rtsal ma 'gag par snang ba ste /
NK062(khu)001:13451: de'i don 'khor rnams la gdams tshul ni /
NK062(khu)001:13452: kye kye zhes lhan cig pa'i 'khor dang go phye ba'i 'khor gnyis la bos nas /
NK062(khu)001:13453: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK062(khu)001:13455: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das gnyis kyi rang bzhin 'di nyid ni /
NK062(khu)001:13456: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK062(khu)001:13458: de bzhin gshegs pa bud+d+ha bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i sku
NK062(khu)001:13459: dang ye shes su gdod nas gnas pa ni gzhi
NK062(khu)001:13460: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i ngo bo nyid nges
NK062(khu)001:13462: de ni sems can thams cad la rang bzhin gyi
NK062(khu)001:13463: gnas pa ste 'di nyid kyi don la dus gsum
NK062(khu)001:13464: du mi 'gyur bar gnas par bya'o zhes gdams pa'o
NK062(khu)001:13465: // gnyis pa log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba dag byar gdams pa ni gzung 'dzin 'dzin //
NK062(khu)001:13467: de yang gnyis med las log cing gnyis su rtog pas na log rtog /
NK062(khu)001:13468: de ma yin la der bzung bas 'khrul pa las dang log rtog gi blor snang ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:13469: 'o na chos thams cad rang bzhin bden pa dbyer
NK062(khu)001:13470: med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por ye nas sangs
NK062(khu)001:13471: rgyas pa ma yin nam zhe na /
NK062(khu)001:13473: zhes pas rang bzhin de ltar yin mod kyi de ltar ma rtogs te /
NK062(khu)001:13474: ma rig pa'i bdag gnyis las byung ba'i gzung 'dzin
NK062(khu)001:13475: gyi kun brtags gnyis kyi spros pa la thog ma
NK062(khu)001:13476: med pa'i dus nas bden zhen du mngon par 'chel
NK062(khu)001:13478: rnam rtog zhags pas so sor 'dzin //
NK062(khu)001:13480: gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa zhags pa dang
NK062(khu)001:13481: 'dra bas 'khor 'gro ba drug gi gnas so sor
NK062(khu)001:13482: 'dzin cing las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis sdug
NK062(khu)001:13483: bsngal bar gyur pas na de las grol bar gdams
NK062(khu)001:13484: pa'am / thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i bdag
NK062(khu)001:13485: nyid ngo ma shes pa dag btags pa'i zhen pa
NK062(khu)001:13486: dgrol ba'i phyir rkyen lam gyi rgyud rnams gsungs so
NK062(khu)001:13487: pa'am / // gsum pa gdul bya lam gyi snang ba bgrod byar gdams pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13490: de yang thun mong gi sems lnga skyes sam skye
NK062(khu)001:13491: rung ba zhig gdul bya 'jug cing bgrod par byed
NK062(khu)001:13492: pas na lam bstan ba blo dang 'tshams par snang
NK062(khu)001:13493: ba'o // 'khrul snang de las dgrol bar bya ba'i phyir lam gyi rgyud rnams gsungs la /
NK062(khu)001:13494: 'o na nye lam gsang ba'i snying po gcig pus chog mod /
NK062(khu)001:13495: thun mong gi lam du ma gsungs ba la dgos pa med do bar dogs pa gsal ba'i phyir /
NK062(khu)001:13496: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK062(khu)001:13498: gong 'og gi sa dang lam gyi rim pa rnams
NK062(khu)001:13499: kyi khyad par ma 'dres par bkod pa nges 'byung
NK062(khu)001:13501: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK062(khu)001:13503: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam stegs
NK062(khu)001:13504: yin pas na mthar thug gi lam 'di nyams su
NK062(khu)001:13506: bzhi pa 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba thob byar gdams pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13509: de yang gang zhig smin pa zhig 'bras bu de
NK062(khu)001:13510: bzhin nyid du nar son pa zhig bde gshegs rtog
NK062(khu)001:13511: tshogs sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang
NK062(khu)001:13512: snang ba'o // ye shes ngo mtshar rab 'byams kyis //
NK062(khu)001:13514: lam nyams su blangs pa'i 'bras bu sku dang ye
NK062(khu)001:13515: shes mngon du byas pa ni ngo mtshar ba ste
NK062(khu)001:13516: de'i yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa sku gsung
NK062(khu)001:13517: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo rab 'byams
NK062(khu)001:13518: kyis / don du mi 'gyur yongs ma gsungs //
NK062(khu)001:13520: gdul bya 'gro ba'i don du mi 'gyur ba'i lam
NK062(khu)001:13521: ni yongs ye ma gsungs pa ste lam du ma
NK062(khu)001:13522: yang gsang sngags kyi lam stegs su dgos pas don
NK062(khu)001:13523: 'gyur du gsungs pa ltar nyams su blangs pas 'bras
NK062(khu)001:13524: bu de dag thob byar gdams pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13525: mdor na snang ba bzhi yang gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rgyud gsum du 'dus la /
NK062(khu)001:13526: de gsum yang rang bzhin gyi rgyud rang bzhin bden
NK062(khu)001:13527: pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por ye
NK062(khu)001:13528: nas sangs rgyas pa las mi 'gyur bar gdams pa'o
NK062(khu)001:13529: // gnyis pa gtad pa la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:13530: sdud pa po la rgyud kyi mtshan nyid brjod nas gtad de rgyal tshab tu dbyung ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13531: gang zag chos kyi mig can la rgyud kyi yon
NK062(khu)001:13532: tan brjod nas gtad de mi nub par bya ba'o
NK062(khu)001:13533: // dang po sdud pa po la rgyud kyi mtshan
NK062(khu)001:13534: nyid brjod nas gtad de rgyal tshab tu dbyung ba
NK062(khu)001:13537: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK062(khu)001:13538: gsang ba 'di las gzhan mi mnga' //
NK062(khu)001:13540: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK062(khu)001:13541: cad la rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di las
NK062(khu)001:13542: lhag pa'i dgongs pa'am thugs kyi brnag byar bya ba
NK062(khu)001:13544: rgyal ba thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid dang dgongs
NK062(khu)001:13545: pa phyin ci ma log par mngon du bstan pa
NK062(khu)001:13546: ni rang bzhin gyi rgyud gsang ba'i snying po 'di
NK062(khu)001:13548: sgro dang skur pa zhi ba yi //
NK062(khu)001:13550: de lta bu'i rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud
NK062(khu)001:13551: kyi ngo bo nyid ci 'dra bar sgro 'dogs pa
NK062(khu)001:13552: dang skur pa 'debs pa zhi ba ste med pa
NK062(khu)001:13553: yi don phyin ci ma log par ston pa ni
NK062(khu)001:13554: / gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK062(khu)001:13555: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK062(khu)001:13557: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid de nges
NK062(khu)001:13558: pa'i rgyud zhes bya ba lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud
NK062(khu)001:13560: shes bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi ming shes byed lam gyi rgyud la btags pa'i phyir ro //
NK062(khu)001:13561: de ltar rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud ni
NK062(khu)001:13562: lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud kyi 'byung khungs su gyur
NK062(khu)001:13563: pas dbyings nas 'di nyid mngon du snang ba ni
NK062(khu)001:13565: nges pa'i lung las byung ba'i phyir mngon du phyung
NK062(khu)001:13566: ba'i lung 'di'i bka' bsdu ba phyag na rdo rje
NK062(khu)001:13567: khyod kyis gyis shig ces gtad nas rgyal tshab tu
NK062(khu)001:13568: dbang bskur ba'o // gnyis pa gang zag chos kyi
NK062(khu)001:13569: mig can la rgyud kyi yon tan brjod nas gtad
NK062(khu)001:13570: de mi nub par bya ba bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13575: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK062(khu)001:13576: phyag rgya gsang chen snying po 'di //
NK062(khu)001:13578: rgyud 'di ni dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13579: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po drug pa kun tu
NK062(khu)001:13580: bzang po'i gsung du phyung ba ni gsung gi phyag
NK062(khu)001:13581: rgya ste / lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud 'dis rang
NK062(khu)001:13582: bzhin gyi rgyud don mtshon pa las mi 'da' ba
NK062(khu)001:13583: rgya ste / dang / 'di rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid las kyang mi 'da' ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13584: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis kyang lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud 'di las ma 'das /
NK062(khu)001:13585: da ltar ba rnams kyang mi 'da' /
NK062(khu)001:13586: ma 'ongs pa rnams kyang 'da' bar mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK062(khu)001:13587: de na gsang chen snying po lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud 'di yi /
NK062(khu)001:13588: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK062(khu)001:13590: tshig don phyin ci ma log par rtogs nas mi
NK062(khu)001:13591: nub par bya ba'i phyir snod du gyur ba'i gdul
NK062(khu)001:13592: bya rnams la blo dang 'tshams par smra bar gang
NK062(khu)001:13593: byed pa / de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK062(khu)001:13595: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor pa de nyid ni kun
NK062(khu)001:13596: tu bzang po nga nyid dang khyad par med pa
NK062(khu)001:13597: yin te / phan nus zab gsum gyi dbang lnga
NK062(khu)001:13598: yang ma bskur bar yongs su rdzogs pas nus pa
NK062(khu)001:13599: chen po dang ldan pas na rig pa rtsal gyi
NK062(khu)001:13601: de ni nges par lung bstan te //
NK062(khu)001:13603: de lta bu rtogs pa'i rten gyi gang zag de
NK062(khu)001:13604: ni sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpar nges
NK062(khu)001:13605: par lung bstan pa yin te /
NK062(khu)001:13606: sras ni thugs las skyes pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:13608: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi sras zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:13609: de ni kun tu bzang po'i thugs kyi dgongs pa
NK062(khu)001:13610: phyin ci ma log par rtogs pa las skyes pa
NK062(khu)001:13611: yin pas na / sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK062(khu)001:13613: rgyu'i theg pa'i sa las mchog tu gyur pa sa
NK062(khu)001:13614: rab rig pa 'dzin pa gsang sngags kyi sa la
NK062(khu)001:13617: rang rig ye shes rgyud don phyir //
NK062(khu)001:13618: rang snang rig pa mngon byas pas //
NK062(khu)001:13619: rig 'dzin mchog ste lhun grub pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13620: ting 'dzin nus pa'i mthu med kyang //
NK062(khu)001:13621: sa sbyong sems dpas bskyod du med //
NK062(khu)001:13622: bde gshegs nyid dang spyod yul gcig /
NK062(khu)001:13623: rig pa'i skyes bur lung thob pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13626: de lta bu yi rang bzhin de //
NK062(khu)001:13627: gzhan la ma brten mi 'gal bar //
NK062(khu)001:13628: mngon sum rig pa'i thag chod na //
NK062(khu)001:13629: rnal 'byor sa la sleb pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:13632: rnam dag lam chen kun sgrol 'dir //
NK062(khu)001:13633: skal ldan gang zhig su zhugs pa //
NK062(khu)001:13635: nges par 'char gyis brtson par gyis //
NK062(khu)001:13636: de nyid sems kyi me long ste //
NK062(khu)001:13637: mngon sum gsal bar rtogs ma thag /
NK062(khu)001:13638: 'gro ba'i lus la sangs rgyas yin //
NK062(khu)001:13640: de lta bas na 'di'i don ji ltar rtogs par
NK062(khu)001:13641: gyis la snod dang ldan pa la mi nub par
NK062(khu)001:13642: bya ba'i phyir snod ldan rnams la sgrogs shig bar
NK062(khu)001:13643: gtad pa'o // zhor la rgyud 'di phyogs bcur 'phel
NK062(khu)001:13644: zhing byin che bar bya ba'i phyir ma mo dang
NK062(khu)001:13645: mkha' 'gro la gtad pa yang 'dir ma gsungs kyang
NK062(khu)001:13646: gtad pa'o // / sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u lnga bcu pa las /
NK062(khu)001:13647: gsang ba'i snying por nges pa 'di //
NK062(khu)001:13648: gsang sngags kun gyi rgyal po yin //
NK062(khu)001:13649: thabs chen mtshon pa'i shes rab yin //
NK062(khu)001:13650: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i snying po dang //
NK062(khu)001:13651: gsang ba'i rgyud chen mang po rnams //
NK062(khu)001:13652: nga yi thugs las sprul pa yin //
NK062(khu)001:13653: tshangs pa dang ni brgya byin dang //
NK062(khu)001:13654: 'jig rten skyong ba rnams dang ni //
NK062(khu)001:13655: dbang phyug chen po la sogs dang //
NK062(khu)001:13656: ded dpon 'phrog ma'i bu rnams dang //
NK062(khu)001:13657: lus dang ba glang spyod pa dang //
NK062(khu)001:13658: sgra mi snyan dang 'dzam gling du //
NK062(khu)001:13659: nga yi thugs kyi snying po 'di //
NK062(khu)001:13660: phyogs bcu kun tu 'phel ba dang //
NK062(khu)001:13661: de yi gzungs la gtad pa ni //
NK062(khu)001:13662: yid bzhin mdzod 'byor bka' yi gnas //
NK062(khu)001:13663: bstan pa 'dzin par nus pa la //
NK062(khu)001:13664: gsang ba'i snying po mchog tu gtad //
NK062(khu)001:13666: gsum pa le'u'i mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13667: gsang ba'i nyi shu gnyis pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13669: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:13672: de kho na nyid gzhan sel ba /
NK062(khu)001:13673: nges pa the tshom dang bral ba /
NK062(khu)001:13674: las zhes pa de mtshan gyi gzhir gda' /
NK062(khu)001:13675: mnyes pa dang yongs su bzung ba'i le'u ste nyi shu gnyis pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13677: rang gzhan gyi mdzad pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs
NK062(khu)001:13678: pas ston 'khor thams cad dbyer med par dgyes pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13680: rgyud brtan cing mi nub par bya ba'i phyir yongs
NK062(khu)001:13681: su bzung ba ste rgyud gdams pa dang gtad pa
NK062(khu)001:13682: ston pa'i gzhung gi tshig don rnams tshoms dang ris
NK062(khu)001:13683: su gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pa'i don gyis
NK062(khu)001:13685: de'i grangs nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las
NK062(khu)001:13686: yas bgrangs nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa'i don du gada'o
NK062(khu)001:13687: // gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK062(khu)001:13688: pa'i rgyud kyi 'grel bshad rgyud don gsal bar byed
NK062(khu)001:13689: pa'i sgron me yid bzhin gyi nor bu zhes bya
NK062(khu)001:13690: la las le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa'i gzhung don
NK062(khu)001:13693: // spyi don gsum pa mjug gi don la gnyis te /
NK062(khu)001:13694: rgyud rdzogs nas mdzad pa chos nyid du grol bar bzhugs tshul bstan pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13695: 'di las stan pa dang theg pa thams cad 'phros pas rgyud kyi che ba bstan pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13696: dang po rgyud rdzogs nas mdzad pa chos nyid du grol bar bzhugs tshul bstan pa ni /
NK062(khu)001:13700: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dbyer med par dgyes nas zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:13701: zhes ston pas brjod pas dus gsum gyi de bzhin
NK062(khu)001:13702: gshegs pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa yang bde ba
NK062(khu)001:13703: chen por ro gcig pas dbyer med par snang ba
NK062(khu)001:13704: ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dgyes pa zhes bya'o
NK062(khu)001:13705: // nas zhes pa 'brel ba ston pa'i sgra'o //
NK062(khu)001:13706: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings /
NK062(khu)001:13708: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa thams cad rang
NK062(khu)001:13709: rig pa kho na las gzhan pa med pas mnyam
NK062(khu)001:13711: sku gsung thugs lhun stug po bkod pa'i rgyan nyid du bzhugs so //
NK062(khu)001:13713: de nyid thams cad du ma 'gags par rang snang
NK062(khu)001:13714: bas sku ngo bo ma sgrub brda sprod pas gsung
NK062(khu)001:13715: snang stong gnyis su mi phyed pas thugs su ma
NK062(khu)001:13716: btsal bar sku gsung thugs su lhun gyis grub pa
NK062(khu)001:13717: kho na'o // de dag gi ngo bo nyid ni
NK062(khu)001:13718: tshig tu brjod pa las 'das pas mtha' yas pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13719: sku dang ye shes kyi phyag rgya de las gzhan
NK062(khu)001:13720: pa'i sel med pa sha stag gis yongs su gang
NK062(khu)001:13721: ba ni dper na til gyi gang bu ltar chos
NK062(khu)001:13722: kyi dbyings mtha' klas par sku dang ye shes kyi
NK062(khu)001:13723: khyab par gdal bas na stug po bkod pa ste
NK062(khu)001:13724: kho na'o // / de dag kyang shin tu mdzes
NK062(khu)001:13725: pa dang ngo bo nyid brjod par dka' bas blta
NK062(khu)001:13726: bas mi ngom pa dang thams cad du cir yang
NK062(khu)001:13727: kho na'o // / snang ba'i phyir / rang rig
NK062(khu)001:13728: pa'i rgyan nyid du rgyal ba thams cad kyang de
NK062(khu)001:13729: lta bu'i ngo bor gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyi
NK062(khu)001:13730: gnas pa ni bzhugs pa ste /
NK062(khu)001:13731: 'di dag gi ngo bo nyid dang dgongs pa ni bzhengs pa ste rjes thob dang /
NK062(khu)001:13732: bzhugs pa ste mnyam gzhag gnyis su mi mnga' bar gnas shing rtag par bzhugs so //
NK062(khu)001:13733: de yang ther zug dang rgyun gyi rtag pa ni ma yin te ngo bo nyid kyi rtag pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13734: gnyis pa 'di las bstan pa dang theg pa thams
NK062(khu)001:13735: cad 'phros pas rgyud kyi che ba bstan pa ni
NK062(khu)001:13740: shes bya dang thabs dang dus dang 'bras bu la
NK062(khu)001:13741: sogs pa lugs gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'o
NK062(khu)001:13742: zhes pas / rgyud 'di ni theg pa gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa yin te /
NK062(khu)001:13743: de yang gzhi shes bya'i gnas lugs bden pa dbyer
NK062(khu)001:13744: med de nyid bden pa bya bral dang tha dad
NK062(khu)001:13746: lam thabs shes zung 'jug de nyid rgyu lam du byed pa las 'phags /
NK062(khu)001:13747: dus tshe gcig lus gcig de nyid skye ba bcu
NK062(khu)001:13748: drug gam bskal ba grangs med gsum la sogs pa
NK062(khu)001:13749: la 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa las 'phags /
NK062(khu)001:13750: 'bras bu pad+ma can dang yi ge 'khor lo tshogs
NK062(khu)001:13751: chen gyi sa nyid bcu gcig pa kun tu 'od
NK062(khu)001:13752: las 'phags pa'o // rtog pa'i rgyal po zhes pa la /
NK062(khu)001:13758: yang dag pa'i rtog pa la sogs pa las zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:13759: ngo bo nyid kyi rtog pa chos nyid du zhen pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13760: 'khrul ba'i rtog pa so so'i skye bo la zhen pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13761: log pa'i rtog pa mu stegs pas btags pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13762: rnam pa'i rtog pa yul gyi rnam pa dang zhes pa'am /
NK062(khu)001:13763: yang na ngo bo nyid kyi rtog pa rgyu lhan skyes kyi rtog pa ma rig pa /
NK062(khu)001:13764: 'khrul ba'i rtog pa rkyen kun brtags kyi ma rig pa /
NK062(khu)001:13765: log pa'i rtog pa smig rgyu la chur 'dzin pa la sogs pa /
NK062(khu)001:13766: rnam pa'i rtogs pa yid 'das ma 'ongs kyi rjes su 'jug pa /
NK062(khu)001:13767: yang dag pa'i rtog pa chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid rnam par 'byed pa dang lnga las /
NK062(khu)001:13768: 'di dag ni yang dag pa'i don blo la nges par byed pa'i phyir yang dag pa'i rtog pa'o //
NK062(khu)001:13769: de'i phyir rtog pa gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas na rgyal po zhes bya'o //
NK062(khu)001:13770: 'di la zur thams cad mkhyen pa chos rje chen po byams pa seng ge'i bzhed kyis /
NK062(khu)001:13771: rtog pa'i rgyal po zhes pas cho ga'i rnam grangs
NK062(khu)001:13772: zhib mo rgyas par ston pas na rtog pa'i rgyal
NK062(khu)001:13773: po ste / sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud kyi mtshan gyi rnam grangs su bzhed do //
NK062(khu)001:13774: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i le'u stong phrag brgya pa las zhes bas /
NK062(khu)001:13775: de lta bu'i rgyud mchog 'di ni rdo rje sems
NK062(khu)001:13776: dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13777: rgyud las bsdus pa'i snying por 'dug pas na rgyud
NK062(khu)001:13778: thams cad kyi rgyal po yin pa'i phyir nges par
NK062(khu)001:13779: che ba'o // mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:13780: rgyud sde zab mo 'di nyid du mtshan nyid kyi sde gsum dang /
NK062(khu)001:13781: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde drug po rnams kyi don
NK062(khu)001:13782: dang 'bras bu thams cad 'dir 'dus shing 'dir gtan
NK062(khu)001:13783: la 'bebs par byed pas na lung gi spyi'i 'grel
NK062(khu)001:13784: pa yin pa'i phyir nges par che ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:13785: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba zhes bas /
NK062(khu)001:13786: dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK062(khu)001:13787: thugs kyi gsang ba dam pa'i mthar thug 'di las
NK062(khu)001:13788: mi 'da' bas na dgongs pa thams cad kyi zhe
NK062(khu)001:13789: phug yin pa'i phyir nges par che ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:13790: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:13791: nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi'i mthar thug gi bsgrub
NK062(khu)001:13792: bya gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK062(khu)001:13793: pa las ma 'das pas na theg pa thams cad
NK062(khu)001:13794: kyi yang rtse yin pa'i phyir nges par che ba'o
NK062(khu)001:13795: // thams cad ma lus par 'phros te zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:13796: rgyud 'di nyid kyi byin rlabs las /
NK062(khu)001:13797: bstan pa dang theg pa rim pa dgu po thams
NK062(khu)001:13798: cad lhag ma ma lus par 'phros pa ste de
NK062(khu)001:13799: las gzhan pa'i sel med pas na bstan pa thams
NK062(khu)001:13800: cad kyi 'byung gnas yin pa'i phyir nges par che
NK062(khu)001:13801: ba'o // 'khor lo bskor ba zhes pas /
NK062(khu)001:13802: yongs su shes par bya ba gsung gi bstan pa rnams ni bskor ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13805: de yang rgyud 'di'i byin rlabs las bka' dang po
NK062(khu)001:13806: bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bas nyon
NK062(khu)001:13807: mongs pa dang srid pa'i zag pa gnyis kyi d+r+wa
NK062(khu)001:13808: ba / bka' bar pa mtshan nyid med pa dang /
NK062(khu)001:13809: tha ma nges pa don gyi chos kyi 'khor los lta ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13810: ma rig pa'i zag pa gnyis kyi d+r+wa ba ma
NK062(khu)001:13811: lus pa gcod par byed pas na sngar 'das pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13812: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gshegs bshul yin pa'i phyir nges
NK062(khu)001:13813: par che la / ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK062(khu)001:13814: rnams kyi lam yang yin pa'i phyir nges par che
NK062(khu)001:13815: par che la / ba'o // de dag gi 'bras bu'i mchog ces pas /
NK062(khu)001:13816: bstan pa dang theg pa mang por spros pa de
NK062(khu)001:13817: dag gi mthar thug gi 'bras bu ni 'dir 'du
NK062(khu)001:13818: ba ste theg pa 'og ma'i 'bras bu rnams las
NK062(khu)001:13819: kyang theg pa 'di'i 'bras bur bgrod dgos pa'i phyir
NK062(khu)001:13820: na / 'bras bu rnams kyi nang nas kyang mchog
NK062(khu)001:13821: tu gyur pa ni rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying por
NK062(khu)001:13822: 'dug pas 'bras bu thams cad kyi thug sa yin
NK062(khu)001:13823: pa'i phyir nges par che ba'o //
NK062(khu)001:13826: tshig dang don la lhag ma ma lus pa'i tha
NK062(khu)001:13827: tshig gam gnas skabs re zhig rdzogs nas bshad du
NK062(khu)001:13828: ma mchis pa'i don du gada'o //
NK062(khu)001:13830: // bdag gi rjes 'brangs rnams kyi don gyi phyir //
NK062(khu)001:13831: bla ma rnams gsung rten bcas nas //
NK062(khu)001:13832: rtsa rgyud gsal byed gsal sgron bya //
NK062(khu)001:13833: nongs gyur dam pa rnams la bshags //
NK062(khu)001:13834: gsang sngags theg pa'i sgor zhugs nas //
NK062(khu)001:13835: yang dag don la mi 'dud par //
NK062(khu)001:13836: mi chos zang zing las byed cing //
NK062(khu)001:13837: rang dbang yod bzhin dbang med ces //
NK062(khu)001:13838: smra zhing gsang don yal 'jog pa //
NK062(khu)001:13839: phyi ma gar 'gro gtol med par //
NK062(khu)001:13840: gal te le lo'i las byed pa //
NK062(khu)001:13841: kye ma'o rang 'joms dpa' bo ste //
NK062(khu)001:13842: rgya mtsho'i mjing gi pha bong ltar //
NK062(khu)001:13843: thugs rjes zhags pa'i dpyang thag yin //
NK062(khu)001:13844: rang gis rang bslus snying re rje //
NK062(khu)001:13845: le lo can la thar lam med //
NK062(khu)001:13846: 'gro ba lhan cig ling tog gis //
NK062(khu)001:13847: ldongs pas rgyud don ma mthong ba //
NK062(khu)001:13848: bdag gis ye ger 'di bkod bas //
NK062(khu)001:13849: sems kyi dmus long mig bye shog /
NK062(khu)001:13851: bstan pa rgya cher spel ba yis //
NK062(khu)001:13852: kun la yang dag mig ldan nas //
NK062(khu)001:13853: log lta ma lus tshar gcod shog /
NK062(khu)001:13854: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13855: rgyud kyi 'grel bshad rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13856: sgron me yid bzhin gyi nor bu zhes bya ba
NK062(khu)001:13857: 'di ni / rigs gzugs la sogs pa yon tan
NK062(khu)001:13858: du ma'i dpal gyis mngon par mtho ba'i zur gyi
NK062(khu)001:13859: sngags 'chang seng ge dpal bzang po dang /
NK062(khu)001:13860: rdo rje 'chang gnyis kyis las dang po pa dgung
NK062(khu)001:13861: lo bcu pa dang bdun pa'i dus su bskul ba'i
NK062(khu)001:13862: ngor / sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho la sogs pa'i bshad rgyud chen po sde bzhi dang /
NK062(khu)001:13863: gzhan yang sngags kyi rgyud sde du ma dang /
NK062(khu)001:13867: spyan 'grel la sogs pa'i rgya 'grel rnams dang /
NK062(khu)001:13868: mngon rtogs 'grel la sogs pa'i bod kyi 'grel ba rnams dang /
NK062(khu)001:13869: sngon gyi bla ma dam pa mkhas shing grub pa thob pa chen po rnams kyi gsung sgros dang /
NK062(khu)001:13870: gsang bdag chen po sgro phug pa'i bshad srol gyi
NK062(khu)001:13871: gsung sgros ma nor ba rim pa nas rim par
NK062(khu)001:13872: brgyud pa zur thams cad mkhyen pa chos kyi rje
NK062(khu)001:13873: chen po byams pa seng ge'i gsung la brten nas
NK062(khu)001:13874: dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rdo rje 'dzin pa
NK062(khu)001:13875: chen po bsam grub rdo rjes lcags pho rta'i lo
NK062(khu)001:13876: la sgrub gnas dam pa dpal 'ug pa lung gi
NK062(khu)001:13877: gtsugs lag khang du legs par bkod pa'i 'grel bshad
NK062(khu)001:13878: gzhir bzhag pa la bla ma rgya gab gong pas
NK062(khu)001:13879: mdzad pa'i t+ai ka rin cen phreng ba dang /
NK062(khu)001:13880: mkhas grub chen po badz+ra sh+r+ai b+ha dras mdzad pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13881: 'grel bshad kyang khong du chud par byas te las
NK062(khu)001:13882: dang po pa'i don du t+ai ka bklag chog gu
NK062(khu)001:13883: ru lugs su bris pa 'di ni bstan pa dang
NK062(khu)001:13884: sems can gyi don rgya chen po bsgrub par bya
NK062(khu)001:13885: ba'i phyir du / chos smra ba'i sngags pa d+harma k+airti dang /
NK062(khu)001:13886: sh+aakya'i btsun pa rat+na ku m+aa ra sh+r+ai b+ha dra la sogs pas bskul ba'i ngor /
NK062(khu)001:13887: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bor
NK062(khu)001:13888: gyur pa mtshungs med chos kyi rje rin po che
NK062(khu)001:13889: 'jam pa'i dbyangs chen po bsam 'grub rdo rje zhes
NK062(khu)001:13890: mtshan yongs su grags pa de nyid kyi zhabs kyi
NK062(khu)001:13891: pad+ma dri ma med pa la gtugs shing /
NK062(khu)001:13892: gsung gi bdud rtsi'i rgyun myang bar gyur pa'i sngags
NK062(khu)001:13893: pa nam mkha' rin cen dpa' bzang pos chu mo
NK062(khu)001:13894: sprul gyi lo chu smad kyi zla ba'i dkar phyogs
NK062(khu)001:13895: kyi tshes brgyad la gtsang bye ma seng ge'i dben
NK062(khu)001:13896: gnas bde chen sgrol mar yongs su rdzogs par sbyar
NK062(khu)001:13897: ba 'dis 'gro ba dpag tu med pa rdo rje
NK062(khu)001:13898: 'dzin pa'i go 'phang la 'god par gyur cig //
NK062(khu)001:13899: bla med rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud mchog mchog tu
NK062(khu)001:13900: rab zab zab don mthar thug phun tshogs ston pa'i
NK062(khu)001:13901: rgyud // rgyud rgyal gsang ba'i snying po'i 'grel bshad
NK062(khu)001:13902: bshad sgros rab gsal gsal ba'i sgron me yidabazhina nor
NK062(khu)001:13903: rgyud // bu'i mchog / mchog gyur 'di ni 'jam
NK062(khu)001:13904: dbyangs chos rje rje btsun nyid gsungs gsung bzhin ma
NK062(khu)001:13905: nor legs par bkod pa'i tshul //
NK062(khu)001:13906: tshul lugs rnam dag phun tshogs 'di yang yang dag
NK062(khu)001:13907: don zab zab mo 'chad 'dod blo ldan 'ga' yi
NK062(khu)001:13908: don // don chen ma lus myur bar rab bsgrub
NK062(khu)001:13909: bsgrub dang bshad 'dod 'dod pa dri med bsam pas
NK062(khu)001:13910: don // kun blangs sems // sems rab dge ba
NK062(khu)001:13911: bzang pos legs bris bris pa gang de de las
NK062(khu)001:13912: byung ba'i rab dkar dge ba'i tshogs //
NK062(khu)001:13913: tshogs gnyis de yis mkha' mnyam 'gro kun kun gyi
NK062(khu)001:13914: sdig sgrib sgrib gnyis bag chags bcom nas rgyal ba'i
NK062(khu)001:13915: sku // sku gnyis mchog gyur myur ba nyid du
NK062(khu)001:13916: du mas legs thob thob pa gang des don gnyis
NK062(khu)001:13917: sku // phun tshogs shog / 'dis kyang bstan pa
NK062(khu)001:13918: dang sems can la phan pa rgya chen po thogs
NK062(khu)001:13919: sku // phun tshogs shog / par gyur cig / mad+ga lam //
NK062(khu)001:13921: // mdo sngags chos tshul tshang la ma nor ba //
NK062(khu)001:13922: mkhas shing grub brnyes rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i srol //
NK062(khu)001:13923: thub bstan snying po gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba'i //
NK062(khu)001:13924: bstan pa 'phel rgyas 'dzam gling khyab gyur cig /
